\toc1 Israelia ko Judabar Atriviba, Men Ak…®nafarir Namba 2
\mt1 Israelia ko Judabar Atriviba, // Men Ak…®nafarir Namba 2
\mt2 O
\mt1 2 Atriviba
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim
\ip Atrivibar Ak…®nafarir Namba 2, a bizir Atrivibar Ak…®nafarir Faragha Zuim…®n eghaghanibar g…®n otivizibagh eghari. Ak…®nafarir kamning, bar fom…®ra ak…®nafarir vam…®ran ike. Atrivibar Ak…®nafarir Namba 2, a Israelian kantrin pumuning…®n atrivibagh eghari. Kar Judabar kantrin saut…®n amadaghan itim, ko Israelian kantrin not…®n amadaghan itir atrivibar eghaghaniba. A bizir otivizibagh eghara ghua, kantrin kamning…®n apaniba aning gas…®ghas…®ghizir dughiam…®n tu. Not…®n amadaghan itir kantri Israel, kantri Asiria, faragha iza a gas…®ghas…®ki. Ez…® g…®n, saut…®n amadaghan itir kantri Juda, kantri Babilon…®n Atrivim Nebukatnesar a gas…®ghas…®ki.
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam, an Atrivibar Ak…®nafarir Faragha Zuim…®n m…®n ghu, egha an atriviba amizir araziba tuis…®si. Me God…®n apengan iti, o puvat…®? Bizir ekiam ak…®nafarir kam aneka, a kamak…®n. Bizir Israel…®n ik…®zimning v…®rara aning batoz…®, apaniba me gas…®ghas…®gh…®zim, kar me uan atriviba ko men os…®mt…®zim. Judabar atriviba ko Israelian atriviba ko men gumazamiziba, me bar mogh…®ra ak…®rim God gasaragha dughiar av…®ribar an Araziba batogha, an akam barazir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me os…®mt…®zir ekiar kam bato.
\ip Gumazamizibar n…®ghn…®zim…®n aven, Jerusalem ko God…®n D…®penir an itim, kar bizir bar ekiamning, egha kamagh…®n men aka, God me ko iti. Ez…® me kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, God me ko ik…®t…®, bizir kuratam me batoghan kogham. Ez…® ak…®nafarir kam, a Jerusalem ikuvizir bizim, ko apaniba God…®n D…®penim gas…®ghas…®ghizir bizim geghari. Bizir kam, a Israelian gumazamizibar n…®ghn…®ziba bar dagh as…®ghas…®ki. Bizir kam bang…®n, g…®n men ik…®r…®m…®rim…®n araziba, ko God…®n ziam fer araziba bar igharaghavram oto.
\c 1
\ms1 Elaija ko Elisan eghaghanim
\mr (Sapta 1:1--8:15)
\s1 Elaija ghaze, // Atrivim Ahasia aremegham
\p 
\v 1 Israelian Atrivim Ahap aremezir dughiam…®n g…®n, Moapia, Israelia me gativagh men ganan me aghuagha me batoke.
\p 
\v 2 Dughiar mam…®n, Israelian Atrivim Ahasia, uan d…®penim…®n azuarim p…®n aperaghav iti. Azuarir kam…®n b…®rim akariagh…®r…®z…®, Ahasia nguazim gir…®gha bar kufi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a gumazir maba amada, eght…® me Filistian kantrin itir nguibar ekiam Ekron…®n mang…® Ekron…®n asem Balsebup, an azangs…®gh fogh suam, a ua deragh otogham, o puvat…®gham.
\v 3 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ensel, kamagh…®n Tisben nguibar ekiam…®n itir God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Elaija m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® d…®kavigh mang…® gumazir Samarian atrivim Ekron…®n nguibar ekiam…®n amadaziba batogh. Egh n…® kamagh…®n me m…®kemegh, ‚ÄòIa manmaghsua Ekron…®n asem Balsebup…®n azangasa? God…®n tam ti Israel…®n kantrin aven itir puvat…®, ez…® ia mangasa?
\v 4 Ia oragh. Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam Atrivim Ahasia gami: N…® ua deraghan kogham. Bar puvat…®. N…® kamagh…®ra uan dakozim…®n ir…®gh…®v k…® mang…® aremegham.‚Äô ‚Äù Ez…® Elaija akar kam baregha, d…®kavigha ghua gumazir kabav gei.
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® gumaziba Elaijan akam baregha g…®vagha, uam atrivim bagha ghuz…®, atrivim kamagh…®n men azara, ‚ÄúIa tizimsua zuam…®ra ua ize?‚Äù
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® me kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir mam tuavim…®n e batogha ghaze, ‚ÄòIa uamategh mang…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akar kam…®n gun atrivim m…®kemegh. Akar kam kamak…®n: Ia manmaghsua Ekron…®n asem Balsebup…®n azangs…®ghasa? Ia ti God…®n tam Israel…®n kantrin aven itir puvat…®, egha ia mangasa? Bar guizbang…®ra, n…® ua deraghan kogham. Bar puvat…®. N…® kamagh…®ra uan dakozim…®n ir…®gh…®v k…® mang…® aremegham.‚Äô ‚Äù
\p 
\v 7 Atrivim akar kam baregha kamagh…®n men azara, ‚ÄúGumazir akar kam ia gan…®ngizim, a manmagh…®n garir gumazim?‚Äù
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Matyu 3:4; Mak 1:6\x*Ez…® me kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúA korotiar me as…®zir ar…®zibar ingarizim aru, egha let…®n me as…®zir inim…®n ingarizim…®n uab…® am…®gh…®r…®.‚Äù
\p Atrivim oregha ghaze, ‚ÄúMar, Tisben gumazim, Elaija.‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 Egha atrivim, m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanir mam ko an m…®dorozir gumazir 50pla sara, me amangiz…®, me Elaija inigh izasa zui. Me ghua danganir Elaija itim…®n otivigha gumazir dapanir kam Elaijan garima, a m…®ghs…®ar mam gis…®n aperaghav iti. Ez…® gumazir dapanir kam kamagh…®n Elaija m…®gei, ‚ÄúO God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim, atrivim ghaze: N…® izighir…® mang…® an ganigh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10-12 \xt Luk 9:54\x*Ez…® Elaija kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim, eght…® avim God…®n Nguibam…®n ikegh izighir…® n…® ko n…®n 50plan m…®dorozir gumaziba sara bar ian isigham.‚Äù Ez…® zuam…®ra avim izaghira gumazir dapanir kam ko an m…®dorozir gumazibar isiz…®, me ariaghire.
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® g…®n atrivim, ua m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanir igharazim ko an m…®dorozir gumazir 50pla amadaz…®, me Elaija bagha ua ghue. Me ghua otivigha, gumazir dapanir kam kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúO God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim, atrivim akar gavgavim n…® gan…®ga ghaze: N…® zuam…®ra izighir…®, egh mang…® an ganigh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® Elaija kamagh…®n an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim, eght…® avim God…®n Nguibam…®n ikegh izighir…® n…® ko n…®n 50plan m…®dorozir gumaziba sara bar ian isigham.‚Äù Ez…® zuam…®ra avim izaghira gumazir dapanir kam ko an m…®dorozir gumazibar isiz…®, me ariaghire.
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® g…®n atrivim ua m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanir igharazir mam ko an m…®dorozir gumazir 50pla amangiz…®, me Elaija bagha ua ghu. Egha namba 3…®n gumazir dapanir kam ghua m…®ghs…®am…®n ghuavanaga, Elaijan borogh…®ra tevimning ap…®righa, kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúO God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim, ga uaning, n…® nan ik…®r…®m…®rim ko nan m…®dorozir gumazibar ik…®r…®m…®ribar apangkuvight…®, e n…®n damazim…®n bizir aghuim…®n m…®n otoght…®, n…® e gas…®ghas…®ghan mark…®.
\v 14 K…® fo, avim God…®n Nguibam…®n ikegha izaghir…®gha gumazir dapanir faragha izezimning…®n isiava aning…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba sara isi. Ez…® ga uaning, n…® nan apangkuvighasa k…® ifonge, egh na gas…®ghas…®ghan mark…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 15 Gumazir dapanir kam m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ensel, kamagh…®n Elaija m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® d…®kavigh gumazir kam ko mag…®r…®. N…® an atiatingan mark…®.‚Äù Ez…® Elaija d…®kavigha a ko atrivim bagha zui.
\p 
\v 16 Elaija ghua otogha akar kam…®n gun atrivim m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®keme: N…® ghaze, Israel…®n kantrin aven Godba ti puvat…®, egha n…® gumaziba amangiz…®, me Ekron…®n asem Balsebup…®n azangasa ghue. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® ua deraghan kogham. Bar puvat…®. N…® kamagh…®ra uan dakozim…®n ir…®gh…®v ik…® mang…® aremegham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 17 Ez…® g…®n Ahasia areme, ez…® bizir kam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Elaijan akam garugha m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, an otogha g…®fa. Ahasia otariba puvat…®, ez…® an aveghbuam, Joram, an danganim inigha, Israelian atrivim…®n oto. Dughiar kam…®n, Judan kantrin aven, Jehosafat…®n otarim Jehoram atrivim…®n iti. Jehoram atrivim…®n itir azenir namba 2…®n aven, Joram Israelian atrivim…®n oto.
\v 18 Atrivim Ahasia amizir bizir igharazibar eghaghaniba, da ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti, me a d…®bora ghaze, Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghaniba.
\c 2
\s1 God Elaija inigha uan Nguibam…®n ghu
\p 
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God am…®nir ighuagharuim…®n Elaija inigh uan Nguibam…®n mangasa n…®ghn…®si. Bizir kam otivasa rogh…®ra izez…®, Elaija ko Elisa Gilgal ategha zui.
\v 2 Egha Elaija kamagh…®n Elisa m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God mang…® Betel…®n otivasa na m…®keme. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ga uaning, n…® kagh ik…®.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Elisa kamagh…®n an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam…®n, k…® bar guizbang…®ra m…®gei, k…® n…® ko mangam.‚Äù Kamagh…®n amiz…®, aning v…®rara Betel…®n nguibam…®n ghu.
\p 
\v 3 Dughiar kam…®n, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar okoruar ekiar mam Betel…®n iti. Egha me bar d…®kavigha nguibam…®n azenan iza aning batogha, kamagh…®n Elisa m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God dat…®r…®gh…®n, n…®n gumazir ekiam inigh mangam. N…® ti kamagh…®n foz, o puvat…®?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Elisa kamagh…®n men akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® fogha g…®fa. Ia ua bizir kam…®n m…®k…®man mark…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® aning ikia, egha Elaija kamagh…®n Elisa m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God Jerikon nguibam…®n mangasa na amada, kamagh…®n amiz…®, ga uaning, n…® kagh ik…®.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Elisa ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam…®n, k…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei, k…® n…® ko mangam.‚Äù Egha aning v…®rara Jerikon nguibam…®n ghu.
\v 5 Dughiar kam…®n, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar okoruar mam Jerikon iti. Egha me Elisa bagha iza kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God dat…®r…®gh…®n n…®n gumazir ekiam inigh mangam. N…® kamagh…®n foz, o puvat…®?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Elisa kamagh…®n men akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® fogha g…®fa. Ia ua bizir kam m…®k…®man mark…®.‚Äù
