\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt God…®n Araziba 21:17\x*Aning ghua Elaija kamagh…®n Elisa m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God na iniamin dughiam rogh…®ra ize, ez…® k…® n…® ategham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® faragh bizir tizimra, n…® bagh a damu n…®n akuragham, n…® bizir tizim gifonge?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Elisa kamagh…®n an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® fo, n…® God…®n gavgavim inigha akam inigha izir ingangarim gami. Ga uaning, n…® gavgavir kam na dan…®ngasa k…® ifonge, mati afeziam bizir av…®riba uan otarir ivariam gan…®di. Egh k…® n…®n danganim inigh, God…®n akam inigha izir ingangarim damuam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® Elaija kamagh…®n an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúBizir n…® nan azarazir kam, a bizir ekiam, k…® a damuan ibura. Eght…® n…® nan gant…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God na inigh mang…®t…®, n…® guizbang…®ra gavgavir kam iniam. K…® zuir dughiam…®n, n…® nan ganighan kogh…®va, n…® gavgavir kam inighan kogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 11 Aning ghua m…®g…®a zuima, Ame! Avir mam zuam…®ra aning…®n torim…®n oto. Avir kam…®n aven, aning garima, hoziaba karis…®n mam kurvasi. Ez…® am…®nir ighuagharuim Elaija inigha God…®n Nguibam…®n ghu.
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt 2 Atriviba 13:14\x*Ez…® Elisa Elaijan gari a zuima a kamagh…®n d…®a m…®g…®av…®ra iti, ‚ÄúNan afeziam! Nan afeziam! N…® Israelian akurvazir gumazir bar gavgavim, mati m…®dorozir hoziaba ko m…®dorozir karisba.‚Äù Ez…® Elaija ghugha g…®vaz…®, Elisa uam an gari puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Elisa bar oseme, egha uan korotiar ruarim…®n suiragha aneb…®ghiz…®, an akuar pumuning…®n ir…®, kar a uan os…®mt…®zim akakagha amizir arazim.
\v 13 Elaija ghuavanadir dughiar kam…®n, an korotiar ruarim nguazim gir…®. Ez…® Elisa a inigha uamategha Jordan…®n Fanem…®n ghua an m…®riam…®n tughav iti.
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt 2 Atriviba 2:8\x*Egha a Elaijan korotiar ruarir kam inigha, Elaija faragha amiz…® mogh…®n d…®pam m…®soke. Egha a d…®pam m…®sozir dughiam…®n, a ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, a Elaijan God, a managh iti? A ti uaghan, na ko ikiam?‚Äù Ez…® d…®pam zuam…®ra bigha akuar pumuning…®n otoz…®, Elisa uamategha vong…®n ize.
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® 50plan God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba, danganir kam…®n ikiav…®ra ikia, egha bizir kam…®n garima, Elisa a gami. Egha me ghaze, ‚ÄúIa gan! God fom…®ra Elaija gan…®ngizir gavgavir kam, a dat…®r…®gh…®n Elisan iti.‚Äù Egha me iza a batogha, tevibar p…®righa dapaniba avigha, ghuaghira nguazim giregha, ziar ekiam a dan…®ngasa.
\p 
\v 16 Egha me kamagh…®n Elisa m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® gan. En adarazir aven, 50plan gumazir gavgaviba iti. Ez…® me mang…® n…®n gumazir ekiam bativasa e ifonge. Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Duam ti a inigha ghua m…®ghs…®atam…®n anetaki, o danganir zaritam…®n anetaki.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Elisa me m…®gei, ‚ÄúMark…®. Ia me amadaght…® me mang…® a burian mark…®.‚Äù
