\v 17 Ez…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba bar gavgavigha, a gakaghora an azangs…®si. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Elisa mong aghums…®gha, men t…®van aghuagha ghaze, ‚ÄúA dera, ia me amadaght…® me mang…®.‚Äù Ez…® me 50plan gumaziba amangiz…® me 3plan aruebar Elaija buriava, a batozir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 18 Dughiar kam…®n, Elisa Jerikon ikiava me m…®zuaima, me ua izez…®, a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® manmagh…®n ia m…®keme? Ez…® ia gavgavigha nan akam baraghan aghua.‚Äù
\s1 Elisa d…®pam gamiz…®, a deragha oto
\p 
\v 19 Dughiar kam…®n, Elisa Jerikon ikiav…®ra itima, nguibam…®n gumazamiziba iza kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir ekiam, n…® gan, nguibar kam bar dera. Ez…® d…®pam ikufi. Amizir naviba adaiba, me d…®par kam apava, me zuam…®ra, borir ghuariba bati. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, boriba ariaghiri.‚Äù
\p 
\v 20 Ez…® Elisa kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa mang…® itarir igiatam inigh, egh amangs…®zir tam a dat…®gh, a inigh izi.‚Äù Ez…® me Elisa m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ami.
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® Elisa a inigha ghua em…®m…®rir d…®pam…®n ghugha amangs…®zir kam a m…®k…®nigha ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei: K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® d…®par kam gamiz…®, a deragha oto. Eght…® d…®pam ua gumazibar amut…®, me ar…®m…®ghiran kogham. Egh ua amizibar amut…®, men ot…®r…®m…®rir dughiam zuam…®ram otoghan kogham.‚Äù
\v 22 Ez…® Elisa m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, d…®par kam deragha kamagh…®ra ikia iza dat…®r…®gh…®n iti.
\s1 Otarir igiar maba Elisa d…®pofi
\p 
\v 23 Ez…® g…®n Elisa Jeriko ategha Betel…®n ghu. Ez…® nguibam…®n otarir igiar maba nguibam…®n azenan iza an gani, egha me kamagh…®n Elisa d…®pova ghaze, ‚ÄúO gumazir onarim m…®sezim, n…® kamat…®gh! Gumazir onarim m…®sezim, n…® danganir kam gitagh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 24 Ez…® Elisa ragha m…®gh…®gha men gara ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ia gas…®ghas…®gham.‚Äù Ez…® as…®zir bean amebar pumuning zuam…®ra ruarim…®n azenan iza, otarir kabar tong…®n otarir 42plan m…®sogha, tintinibar men m…®karziba ab…®aghar…®ki.
