\v 25 Ez…® Elisa danganir kam ategha bar ghua Karmel…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n ghu. Egha g…®n Karmel ategha uamategha Samarian nguibar ekiam…®n ghu.
\c 3
\s1 Israelia Moapia m…®sosi
\p 
\v 1 Dughiar kam…®n, Jehosafat Judabar atrivim…®n iti, ez…® an namba 18…®n azenim…®n, Ahap…®n otarim Joram, Israelian atrivim…®n oto. Egha a 12plan azenibar Samarian atrivim…®n ike.
\v 2 Atrivim Joram arazir kuram Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n a gami. Egha an arazir bar kurar av…®ribagh amizir puvat…®, mati an amebam ko afeziam amiz…® mok…®n. Joram asem Bal…®n marvir guar an afeziam fom…®ra ingarizir kam batoke.
\v 3 Egha Nebat…®n otarim Atrivim Jeroboam, amizir arazir kurar kabara, Joram uam a dagh ami, arazir kurar kamagh gariba Jeroboam Israelia gekuiz…® me dagh ami. Joram arazir kurar kaba ataghizir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®.
\p 
\v 4 Dughiar kam…®n, kantri Moap…®n Atrivim Mesa sipsip…®n av…®riba iti. A Israelian atrivim…®n apengan iti, egha azeniba bar takis…®n m…®n uan 100,000plan sipsip…®n apurir igiaba isa Israel…®n atrivim gan…®di. Egha uaghan 100,000plan sipsip…®n apuriba am…®s…®va, dar ar…®zibar ghora Israelian atrivim bagha da amadi.
\v 5 Ez…® g…®n Israelian Atrivim Ahap aremez…®, Atrivim Mesa Israelian atrivir igiam…®n apengan ikian aghuagha, ua sipsipba takis…®n m…®n a gan…®dir puvat…®.
\v 6 Ez…® Atrivim Joram zuam…®ra d…®kavigha Samaria ategha, Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba bar me akufa.
\v 7 Egha Joram, Judabar Atrivim Jehosafat bagha akam amaga ghaze, ‚ÄúMoap…®n Atrivim nan apengan ikian aghua. Ez…® k…® mang…® a m…®soghasava ami. N…® na ko izam, o puvat…®gham?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Jehosafat kamagh…®n an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® n…® ko mangam. K…® n…®n ifongiam…®n g…®n mangasa iti. Ez…® nan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko hoziaba n…®n akurvaghasa iti.
\v 8 Egh e tuavir manam…®n mangam?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Joram kamagh…®n an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúE Idom…®n kantrin gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n aven zuir tuavim…®n mang…® otogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 Kamagh…®n, Israelian Atrivim Joram ko Judan Atrivim Jehosafat ko Idom…®n atrivim, me uan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha zui. Tuavir kam, a bar ruaraz…®, me 7plan aruebar arua zuima, men d…®paba bar g…®fa. Ez…® m…®dorozir gumaziba ko as…®zir biziba ateriba, damamin d…®paba puvat…®.
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® Atrivim Joram kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…®, e uarir apangkufi. Ikiav…®ra Itir God e 3plan atriviba, an en diagha e isa Moapian atrivim…®n dafarim gat…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® Atrivim Jehosafat kamagh…®n Atrivim Joram…®n azai, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam inigha izir gumazitam iti, o puvat…®? Tam ik…®t…®, e a m…®kemeght…® a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azaragham, e manmagh…®n damuam.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Atrivim Joram…®n gumazir dapanir mam, kamagh…®n an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúSafat…®n otarim Elisa, a iti. A fom…®ra God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Elaijan ingangarir gumazim…®n ike.‚Äù
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® Atrivim Jehosafat oregha ghaze, ‚ÄúElisa, a guizbang…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim.‚Äù Ez…® atrivir 3plan kaba Elisan ganasa ghue.
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® Elisa Israelian atrivim…®n ganigha ghaze, ‚ÄúIa manmaghsua na bagha izi? Ia akam inigha izir gumazir n…®n ameboghfeziaba fom…®ra ghua azangs…®ghizir kaba, me bagh mang…®.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Atrivim Joram kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúPuvat…®. Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…® e 3plan atriviba en diagha e isa Moap…®n atrivim…®n dafarim gat…®. Ez…® e n…® bagha izi.‚Äù
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® Elisa kamagh…®n Joram m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim…®n ingangarir gumazim. A zurara ikia mamagh…®ra iti, egha gavgaviba bar iti. Ez…® k…® an ziam…®n k…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei: Atrivim Jehosafat ti ia ko itir puvat…®z…®, k…® n…®n guam…®n ganighan koghai, o n…® ko m…®kemeghan koghai. Ez…® k…® fo, Jehosafat a gumazir aghuim. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® a bang…®n n…®n akam baragham.
\v 15 Eght…® ia dat…®r…®gh…®n mang…®, gumazir deragha gita m…®sogha ighiabagh amitam inigh izi.‚Äù Ez…® me gumazir gita m…®soghamim inigha ize. Ez…® a gita m…®sozir dughiam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gavgavim Elisan iza anevara.
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® Elisa akam akura ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God ghaze: Ia daghurir d…®par fom…®ra em…®ra, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n m…®s…®ngizir kam…®n, mozir d…®par av…®ribagh kuigh.
\v 17 Ia amozim ko am…®nim…®n ganighan kogham, eght…® d…®pam uan danganir kam giz…®vagham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ian bulmakauba ko donkiba damamin d…®par av…®riba ikiam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 18 Elisa ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, D…®pam ia gan…®dir ingangarir kam, an damazim…®n a bizir ekiam puvat…®. A bizir bar muziarim. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua bizir igharazitam damuasa. Ia Moapian m…®soghamin dughiam, a ia ateght…®, ia me ab…®nigham.
\v 19 Egh nguibar d…®vazir gavgaviba itiba ko, nguibar ekiar bar aghuiba vaghvagh da inigh. Egh ia men temer aghuiba ok…®, egh men mozir d…®paba apemegh. Egh ia dag…®aba is…® azenibar ingaramin nguaziba bar dav k…®nigh, eght…® me dagheba oparan kogham.‚Äù
\p Elisa m…®kemegh g…®vaz…®, atrivir 3pla anetegha ghu.
\v 20 Ez…® am…®mzaraghan bar m…®zaraghara, kar m…®zarazir ofa damuamin dughiam, aruem anadima, d…®pam zuam…®ra Idom…®n ikegha izaghira, nguazir otevir kam bar a giz…®fa.
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® Moapia kamagh…®n akam baraki, 3plan atriviba iz…® me m…®soghasa. Egha me bar gumazir m…®dorozim damuamin gavgaviba itibar diaz…®, me iza uari akufa. Egha me g…®n iza kantri Moap ko kantri Idom…®n m…®taghniam…®n tugha m…®soghasa danganiba isa m…®zua iti.
\v 22 Egha am…®mzaraghan, Moapia d…®kavigha garima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelia bagha d…®pam amadagha g…®fa. Ez…® aruer angazangarim d…®pam gisira, ez…® Moapia d…®pam…®n garima, a ghuzim…®n m…®n bar aghefe. Ez…® Moapia saghuiam…®n tuivav ikia an gari.
\v 23 Egha me kamagh…®n dei, ‚ÄúAme! Ia gan. Kar ghuzimra. Apaniba ti uariv sogha, uarira uan av…®ribav soghez…® me ariaghire, ez…® men ghuziba nguazim…®n iti. Aria, e mang…® men danganim…®n men biziba iniam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 24 Egha me d…®kavigha Israelian danganim…®n ghue. Egha me ghua otivir dughiam…®n, Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba puv me m…®sogha, men g…®nt…®gha bar ghua Moap…®n kantrin ghu. Egha Israelia Moapian av…®rim m…®suagharigha,
\v 25 men nguibabagh as…®ghas…®ki. Israelia Moapian danganiba bar dagh arui. Me mang…® azenibar ingaramin nguazir tam batoghamin dughiam…®n, m…®dorozir gumaziba bar dag…®aba inigha nguazir kam m…®k…®niz…® dag…®aba bar nguazim avara. Egha uaghan me mozir d…®paba bar da apemegha, temer aghuiba bar ada oke. Me nguibar ekiaba bar dagh as…®ghasigha, nguibar ekiar vam…®ra gas…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®, kar Kirheres, Moap…®n nguibar ekiam. Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazir katapel…®n asiba, me nguibar ekiar kam ek…®arugha dag…®abar asavamadima, da nguibam…®n aven zui.
\p 
\v 26 Ez…® Moap…®n atrivim apanir kabar garima, me a gafisi, kamagh…®n amiz…® a 700plan m…®dorozir gumazir m…®dorozir sababar suigha m…®sogha foziba ini, egha me Kirheres…®n nguibar ekiam ategh ar…® Idom…®n atrivim bagh mangasa ua iburaghburaki.
\v 27 Ez…® Moap…®n atrivim uan otarir ivariam ini, otarir kam an danganim inigh atrivim…®n ikiam. Egha atrivim otarir kam m…®suegha an ofa gami, mati Moapian asem…®n ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim. A nguibar ekiam av…®nizir d…®vazim gis…®n ofan kam gami. Israelia bizir kam…®n ganigha bar atiatingi.\f + \fr 3:27 \ft Hibrun akam deragha akar kam abigha m…®geir puvat…®. Fofozir gumazir maba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, Israelia ti kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, Moapian asem men ataram, kamagh…®n me atiati. Ez…® fofozir gumazir igharaziba ghaze, Israelia ti kamagh…®n atiati, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelian atari, egha a bizir kurar kam gamiz…® a Israelian damazim…®n oto. Ez…® fofozir gumazir maba ghaze, Israelia uari Moapian atrivim…®n arazir kam…®n osemegha m…®dorozim ataki.\f* Egha me m…®dorozim ategha, uamategha uan kantrin ghue.
\c 4
\s1 Elisa amuir odiarim…®n akura
\p 
\v 1 Dughiar mam…®n God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar okoruam…®n mav, an amuim Elisa bagha ize. An pam aremez…® an odiarim…®n iti. Egha a kamagh…®n Elisan diava arai, ‚ÄúO gumazir ekiam, nan pam areme. N…® fo, a zurara Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n atiati an apengan iti. Egha a faragha gumazir mam da pura dag…®aba ini. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® da ikarvaghamin dag…®aba puvat…®. Ez…® gumazir kam nan otarimning iniasa izi, egh aning damut…® aning an ingangarir gumazir k…®nimning…®n otogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 2 Elisa akar kam baregha kamagh…®n amizim m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® manmagh…®n n…®n akuragham? Bizir manam n…®n d…®penim…®n iti?‚Äù
\p Ez…® amizim kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® m…®ner mam iti, oliv…®n borem an iti, anar…®ra. K…® ua bizir igharaziba puvat…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 3 Ez…® Elisa kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® namakabar azaraght…®, me uan m…®ner pura itiba n…® dan…®ngigh. N…® m…®ner av…®riba inigh.
\v 4 Egh n…® m…®ner kaba inigh uan d…®penim…®n aven mang…®, egh tiam asaragh. Dat…®r…®gh…®n n…® uan otarimning ko borer n…®n m…®ner kam…®n itim is…®, m…®ner kabagh ingegh. N…® m…®netam gingeght…® a iz…®vaght…®, n…® a inigh danganitam dafagh. N…® kamagh…®ra damuv…®ra mang…®t…®, m…®ner kaba bar izefegh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® amizim akar kam baregha g…®vagha ghua, uan namakaba da m…®neba inigha, uan d…®penim…®n ghu. Egha a uan otarimning ko d…®penim…®n aven ghugha tiam asara. Ez…® an otarimning m…®neba isa a bagha izima, a borem m…®ner kabagh ingav…®ra iti.
\v 6 Amizim borem m…®nebagh ingegha g…®vagha, kamagh…®n uan otarir mam m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® m…®ner igharazim inigh iz…®.‚Äù
\p Ez…® otarim ghaze, ‚ÄúAmebam, m…®neba bar izefe.‚Äù Egha dughiar kamra, borem ua amizim…®n m…®nem…®n otivir puvat…®. A kamagh…®ra tu.
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® amizim ghua kamagh…®n God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Elisa m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® m…®ner kaba bar borem dagh ingegha g…®fa.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Elisa kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® borer kaba amadagh, egh dag…®aba inigh. Egh n…® uan pam inizir dag…®aba ikaragham. Eght…® dag…®ar naba ikiam, kar n…® uan otarimning ko ia daghebagh ivezam.‚Äù
\s1 Elisa Sunem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n amizim…®n otarim gamiz…®, a ua d…®kafi
\p 
\v 8 Dughiar mam…®n Elisa Sunem…®n nguibam…®n ghu. Amizir mam nguibar kam…®n ikia, egha dag…®ar av…®riba iti. Egha uan d…®penim…®n daghetam amasa Elisan azangs…®si. Ez…® Elisa zurara Sunem…®n izir dughiabar an amizir kam…®n d…®penim…®n apiaghirava api.
\p 
\v 9 Egha dughiar mam…®n amizir kam kamagh…®n uan pam m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® gan, gumazir kam zurara iza e koma api, k…® fo, a God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim, egha a God baghav…®ra itir gumazimra.
\v 10 Ga uaning, ga ti d…®penir ghuriar p…®n itim…®n daguraguir danganitam ak…®righam. Egh e akuir dakozitam ko, apir dakozitam ko, dabirabir tam ko, lam…®n tam, danganir kam…®n dar arigham. Eght…® gumazir kam izamin dughiam…®n, a danganir kam…®n ikiam.‚Äù Egha aning a bagha danganir kam ak…®ri.
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® dughiar mam…®n Elisa ua Sunem…®n izegha, danganir kam…®n ghuavanabogha, uan akuir dakozim gir…®ghav ikiava avughsi.
\v 12 An avughsa ikia kamagh…®n uan ingangarir gumazim Gehasi m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® mag…®r…® na bagh Sunem…®n amizir kam…®n ganigh, egh a m…®kemeght…® a iz…®.‚Äù Ez…® Gehasi amizim m…®kemez…® a iza an guam…®n tu.
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® Elisa Gehasi m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® kamagh…®n amizim…®n azaragh, ‚ÄòBar guizbang…®ra, n…® ingangarir ekiam gamua gan akura. E bizir tizim damigh, n…®n akurvazir aghuim ikaragham? Elisa ti mang…® atrivim o m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanim…®n azaraght…®, aning n…® bagh bizir aghuitam damuam? N…® kamagh…®n ifongez, o?‚Äô ‚Äù
\p Ez…® Gehasi ghua amizir kam…®n azaraz…®, amizim kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® uan adarazir tong…®n iti, egha bizitam…®n otevezir puvat…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® Elisa kamagh…®n Gehasin azara, ‚ÄúE bizir aghuir manatam…®n amizir kam…®n arazir aghuim ikarvagham?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Gehasi ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® gari, bizir vam…®ra iti, an pam bar ghuriz…®, a boriba puvat…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® Elisa Gehasi m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® amizim m…®kemeght…®, a iz…®.‚Äù Ez…® Gehasi ghua amizim m…®kemez…®, a iza tiar akam…®n tughav iti.
\p 
\v 16 \x - \xo 4:16 \xt Jenesis 18:14; 2 Atriviba 4:28\x*Ez…® Elisa amizim m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAzenir munam…®n dughiar kamra, n…® otaritam uan agharimning…®n a firagham.‚Äù
\p Ez…® amizim a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGa uaning, nan gumazir aruam, n…® God…®n akam akurir gumazim, n…® na gifaran mark…®.‚Äù
\v 17 Ez…® g…®n, amizir kam navim asangi. Egha Elisa m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra, azenir munam…®n, dughiar kamra an otarim bate.
\p 
\v 18 Azenir mabar g…®n otarim ekevegha, uan afeziam bagha azenibar ghu. Kar witbar ghorir dughiam, ez…® afeziam ingangarir gumaziba ko wit…®n azenim…®n iti.
\v 19 Otarim ingangaribar gara ikia, egha kamagh…®n uan afeziam…®n diava arai, ‚ÄúIiii afeziam! Nan dapanim puv…®ra na gami. A na gamuav…®ra iti! Iiii!‚Äù
\p Ez…® afeziam uan ingangarir gumazir mam m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® otarir kam inigh an amebam bagh mang…®.‚Äù
\v 20 Ez…® ingangarir gumazim otarim inigha an amebam bagha ghu. Ez…® otarim amebam…®n apozim gir…®ghav ikia ghua, dughiar aruer ar…®zim…®n tu, egha an areme.
\v 21 Ez…® amebam otarim…®n kuam inigha d…®penim…®n p…®n ghuanaga Elisan danganim…®n aven ghua dakozim anet…®. Egha amebam azenan ghugha tiam asara.
\p 
\v 22 Egha a uan pam…®n diaz…®, a izima a kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® ingangarir gumazitam m…®kemeght…®, a na bagh donki inigh iz…®. Eght…® k…® zuam…®ra mang…®, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir kam…®n ganigh, egh uamategh izam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 23 Ez…® an pam ghaze, ‚ÄúManmagh amiz…® n…® dat…®r…®gh…®ra mangasa? N…® Sabat…®n dughiam o iak…®nir igiam…®n dughiar ekiam m…®zuamam, o?‚Äù
\p Ez…® amizim ghaze, ‚ÄúMark…®, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®ra mangasa. N…® n…®m…®ra ik…®. Biziba deragham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 24 Ez…® ingangarir gumazim satel donki gat…®z…®, amizim a gapera. Egha amizim kamagh…®n ingangarir gumazim m…®gei, ‚ÄúE mangamin dughiam…®n, n…® donki damut…®, a zuam…®ra mang…®. N…® na bang…®n aghumra mangan mark…®. Donki aghumra mang…®s…® k…® ifuegh, n…® m…®k…®mam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 25 Egha amizim ingangarir gumazim ko, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Elisan ganasa Karmel…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n ghu.\f + \fr 4:25 \ft Karmel…®n M…®ghs…®am mong 40 kilomitan, Sunem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n saghon iti.\f* Aning saghon ikiav…®ra itima, Elisa aning…®n gani. Egha a uan ingangarir gumazim, Gehasi m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® munagh gan, Sunem…®n amizir kam izi.
\v 26 N…® ivegh a bagh mang…®va an azaragh fogh, a uan pam ko otarim me ti deragha iti, o puvat…®?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Gehasi ghua amizim…®n azaraz…®, amizim kamagh…®n an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúE deraghav…®ra iti.‚Äù
\v 27 Amizim iza m…®ghs…®am…®n Elisa batogha, aviragha Elisan dagarimning…®n suira. Ez…® Gehasi amizim…®n garima, a kamagh…®n amima, an a t…®vamadaght…® a tong saghon mangasa.
\p Ez…® Elisa kamagh…®n Gehasi m…®gei, ‚ÄúAnetakigh. K…® fo, an os…®mt…®zir bar ekiam iti. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God an os…®mt…®zim nan modogha an gun na m…®kemezir puvat…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 28 Ez…® amizim ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir ekiam, kar n…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am…®n God borir kam na gan…®ngi. K…® n…®n azarazir puvat…®. Ez…® k…® n…® m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® na gifaran mark…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 29 Elisa akar kam baregha, kamagh…®n Gehasi m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® deraghv…®ra uan inim ikegh, egh nan fidizir aghorim uan dafarim…®n an suiragh, egh zuam…®ra Sunem…®n nguibam…®n mang…®. Egh n…® gumazitam batogh, dughiam a dan…®ngan mark…®. Eght…® gumazitam dughiam n…® dan…®ngt…®, n…® an akam ikaraghan mark…®. N…® amizir kam…®n d…®penimra mang…®, egh fidizim otarir kam…®n guam gis…®n dat…®gh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 30 Ez…® otarim…®n amebam kamagh…®n garima, Elisa mangan ibura, ez…® a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam…®n, k…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei, k…® n…® ategh uab…®ra mangan kogham.‚Äù Kamagh…®n amiz…® Elisa d…®kavigha amizir kam ko uamategha Sunem…®n ghu.
\p 
\v 31 Ez…® Gehasi faragha ghua Elisan fidizir aghorim isa otarim…®n guam gat…®, ez…® a tong mozorogha amir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®. Egha Gehasi uamategha zui. A tuavim…®n aning batozir dughiam…®n, a kamagh…®n Elisa m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®n k…® ami, ez…® otarim ua d…®kavizir puvat…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 32 Egha me ghua d…®penim…®n otivigha, Elisa uan danganim…®n tiar akam…®n ghugha, otarir kam…®n kuam…®n garima a dakozim gir…®ghav iti.
\v 33 Egha an aven ghugha tiam asaragha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®gei.
\v 34 \x - \xo 4:34-35 \xt 1 Atriviba 17:21\x*Egha a dakozim gis…®n ghuavanabogha otarim…®n kuam gis…®n fuagha, uan akam isa otarim…®n kuam…®n akam gat…®gha, uan damazimning an damazimning…®n porogha, uan dafarimning isa an dafarimning gis…®n at…®. Elisa kamagh…®n amuav…®ra itima, otarim…®n m…®karzim ua fei.
\v 35 Ez…® Elisa dakozim ategha mong uan danganim…®n aven arui. Egha ua ghua otarim gis…®n avira. Ez…® otarim 7plan dughiabar asigha uan damazimning kui.
\p 
\v 36 Ez…® Elisa Gehasin diagha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® otarim…®n amebam m…®kemeght…® a iz…®.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Gehasi kamagh…®n amiz…®, amizir kam anaga akuir danganim…®n aven ghu. Ez…® Elisa a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uan otarim inigh.‚Äù
\v 37 Egha amizim Elisan dagarimning…®n borogh…®ra ir…®gha, dapanim aviragha nguazim m…®tuagha, ziar ekiam Elisa gan…®di. Egha g…®n d…®kavigha uan otarim inigha ghu.
\s1 Elisa d…®pars…®zim gamiz…®, a dera
\p 
\v 38 Dagheba puvat…®zir dughiar kurar mam, Israel…®n nguazim bato. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Elisa uamategha ghua Gilgal…®n nguibam…®n iti. Dughiar mam…®n, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar okoruam…®n, gumazir maba iza a da n…®ghn…®ziba isi. Me apiagha an akaba barasi, egha Elisa uan ingangarir gumazim kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® m…®ner ekiam inigh iz…®va God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba bagh d…®pars…®zim damu.‚Äù
\p 
\v 39 Ez…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam d…®pars…®zir tam damuasa ghua, zuravariba buri. Egha a ruarim…®n itir sevibar m…®n garir bizibar gara ghaze, ka ti dagher aghuiba. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a sevir ov…®zir av…®riba inigha, uan inim gar…®ghiz…® an inim bar iz…®fa. Egha a da inigha iza dar ghoregha m…®nem gaghui. Ez…® gumaziba deragha sevir ov…®zibagh fozir puvat…®.
\v 40 D…®pars…®zim isigha g…®vaz…®, God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba damasa me da isa itaribagh ar…®si. Ez…® me apir dughiam…®n, d…®pars…®zim men akabav sosi, ez…® me kamagh…®n Elisan dei, ‚ÄúO God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim, d…®pars…®zir kam bar puv…®ra m…®sosi. Ez…® e daman ibura. E ti ar…®m…®ghiregham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 41 Ez…® Elisa plauan me wit…®n ingarizir taba inigh izasa me m…®gei. Me da inigha izez…®ma, Elisa da m…®nem m…®k…®nigha, kamagh…®n uan ingangarir gumazim m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® d…®pars…®zim uam a is…® itaribar ar…®kigh, eght…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba damam.‚Äù Ez…® me apima, d…®pars…®zim dat…®r…®gh…®n ua men akabav sozir puvat…®.
\s1 Elisa 100plan gumaziba dagheba me gan…®di
\p 
\v 42 Ez…® dughiar mam…®n g…®n, gumazir man Balsalisan nguibam ategha, Elisa bagha ize. Kar bali aghoramin dughiam. Gumazir kam uan azenim…®n, balin faragha aniba aghoregha, 20plan balin bret…®n rubuzir tueziba ko balin tuezir puvat…®zir maba sara inigha uan m…®tarim gaghuigha, da inigha Elisa bagha ize. Ez…® Elisa uan ingangarir gumazim m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® dagher kaba is…® akam inigha izir gumazibar an…®ngt…®, me dar am…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 43 Ez…® an ingangarir gumazim ghaze, ‚ÄúDagher kaba av…®rasemezir puvat…®, Dagher kaba manmagh…®ra 100plan akam inigha izir gumazir kabar tughat…®gham.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Elisa an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, me dam…®t…®, dagher naba ik…®v…®ra ikiam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® dagheba is…® gumazibar anight…®, me dar am…®.‚Äù
\v 44 Ez…® ingangarir gumazim dagheba isa akam inigha izir gumazibagh an…®ngiz…®, me da api. Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra, me amegha iz…®vaz…®, dagher naba ikiav…®ra iti.
\c 5
\s1 Naman…®n lepan ar…®mariam g…®fa
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 5:1-14 \xt Luk 4:27\x*Naman, a Sirian m…®dorozir gumazibar gumazir dapanir ekiam. Naman…®n dafarim…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Sirian m…®dorozir gumazibar akuraz…®, me apaniba d…®kab…®ni, kamagh…®n amiz…®, Sirian atrivim bar a gifuegha, a bagha bar akonge. Naman a m…®dorozir gumazir bar aghuim, egha a lepan ar…®mariam iti.
\v 2 Dughiar mam…®n Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba ghua Israelia m…®sogha, guivir igiar mam…®n suiragha a sara ghu. Ez…® guivir igiar kam, a Naman…®n amuim…®n ingangarir amizim…®n iti.
\v 3 Dughiar mam…®n g…®n, Israelian guivir igiar kam kamagh…®n Naman…®n amuim m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…®n pam God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir Samarian itir kam bagh mang…®gh, ti deragham. God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir kam an ar…®mariam ak…®right…®, a ua deragham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Naman akar kam baregha, atrivim bagha ghua, guivir igiar kam…®n akam…®n gun a m…®keme.
\v 5 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® mang…®! K…® Israelian atrivim bagh ak…®nafaritam osirigh, n…® danight…® n…® a inigh mang…® a dan…®ngigh.‚Äù
\p Egha atrivim ak…®nafarim osirigha Naman gan…®ngi. Ez…® Naman 300,000 kina silvan dag…®aba ko 60 kilogrem gol, ko 10plan korotiar kurkiamiba sara inigha, d…®kavigha Samarian ghu.
\p 
\v 6 Egha Naman Sirian atrivim da ak…®nafarir kam inigha ghua, Israelian atrivim gan…®ngi. Ak…®nafarir kam kamagh…®n m…®gei: ‚ÄúAk…®nafarir kam, nan gumazir dapanim Naman k…® a bagh n…® m…®k…®masa. A lepan ar…®mariam iti, ez…® n…® a damight…®, a ua deraghasa k…® ifonge.‚Äù
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® Israelian atrivim ak…®nafarir kam…®n ganigha uan navir os…®mt…®zim akakagha uan korotiam ab…®ki. Egha a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAmei! Sirian atrivim tizim bagha kamagh…®n na bagh akam amada, k…® mang…® gumazir kam…®n ar…®mariam ak…®righam? A ti ghaze, k…® God, k…® gumazim damight…® a deragh ikiamin gavgavim iti, a? O k…® gumazim damight…®, an aremeghamin gavgavim iti, a? K…® fo, a na m…®soghasa tuaviba buri.‚Äù
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Elisa, kamagh…®n oraki, atrivim navir os…®mt…®zim ikia, uan korotiam ab…®ki. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Elisa kamagh…®n atrivim bagha akam amaga ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® manmaghsua navim osemegha uan korotiam ab…®ki? N…® gumazir kam amadaght…® a na bagh iz…®, eght…® k…® kamagh…®n an akaght…® a fogh suam, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam guizbang…®ra Israel…®n iti.‚Äù
\v 9 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, atrivim Naman m…®kemez…®, a uan karisba ko hoziaba sara ghua Elisan d…®penim…®n tiar akam…®n oto.
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® Elisa gumazir mam Naman bagha anemadaz…®, a d…®penim…®n azenan ghua kamagh…®n Naman m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® 7plan dughiabar Jordan…®n Fanem…®n d…®pam…®n rueght…®, n…®n ar…®mariam g…®vaght…®, n…®n m…®karzim ua deraght…®, n…® deragham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® Naman akar kam baregha puv atari, egha Elisan d…®penim ategha ghu. Naman ghaze, ‚ÄúElisa ti azenan izegh nan ganigh, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uan God ko m…®k…®m, egh ar…®mariam iti nagh…®n is…®n uan dafarim ighuavamangam. Egh arazir kam…®n a na damight…®, k…® ua deragham. Ez…® puvat…®.
\v 12 A Jordan…®n Fanem…®n d…®pam…®n ruasa na m…®gei. Ez…® Damaskus…®n Fanemning Abana ko Farpar, aning bar Israelian d…®pabagh afira! Eght…® d…®patam nan ar…®mariam ag…®vs…®, k…® ti uan kantrin aven itir d…®par kamning guruva ua deragham.‚Äù Naman kamagh…®n m…®g…®a, egha bar an…®ngaghegha ghu.
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® an ingangarir gumaziba an borogh…®n ghua kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir ekiam, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim bizir bar ekiatam damus…® n…® m…®k…®mt…®, e fo, n…® a damuam. Ez…® a kamagh…®n bizitam m…®kemezir puvat…®. A pura ruasa n…® m…®keme. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® an akam…®n g…®n mang…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Elisa, a Naman m…®kemez…® mogh…®n Naman an akam baregha, ghua Jordan…®n Fanem…®n ghuaghira 7plan dughiabar uab…® isa d…®pam gazui. Ez…® an ar…®mariam bar g…®vaz…® an m…®karzim ua bar zuegha, borir igiam…®n m…®n oto.
\p 
\v 15 Egha a uan ingangarir gumaziba ko, me ua God…®n ingangarir gumazim bagha ghue. Egha Naman, Elisan guam…®n tugha a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® dat…®r…®gh…®n fo, god…®n tam ua nguazir kam…®n nguibatam…®n itir puvat…®. Ia Israelia, ian God, a guizbang…®ra God. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ga uaning, k…® n…®n ingangarir gumazim, k…® bizir aghuim n…® dan…®ngasa, n…® na dama a inigh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® Elisa an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúPuvat…®. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n zurara itim…®n ingangarir gumazim. A nan garima, k…® an ziam…®n guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei, k…® bar n…® da bizitam inighan kogham.‚Äù Ez…® Naman bizir aghuitam Elisa dan…®ngasa bar gavgafi, ez…® Elisa bar aghua.
\p 
\v 17 Ez…® Naman ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® nan bizir aghuim inian aghua, a mark…®. Ga uaning, k…® n…®n ingangarir gumazim, n…® nan amamangat…®ght…®, k…® Israelian nguazir m…®nemeniar av…®ritaba inigh uan donkining dat…®ght…®, aning da ater e uamategh uan nguibam…®n mangam. Egh nguazir m…®nemeniar kabagh is…®n, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh, ofa gamir dakozim…®n ingaram. Guizbang…®ra, k…® god…®n igharazitaba bagh ofan bar isia m…®gh…®riba, ko ofan igharazibar amuan kogham. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God baghv…®ra ofan bar isia m…®gh…®riba ko ofan igharazibar amuam.
\v 18 Ez…® n…® nan os…®mt…®zim g…®foghasa k…® ifonge, eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God nan arazir kuraba g…®n amadagham. Nan gumazir ekiam zurara ghua asem Rimon…®n ziam fe, ez…® k…® a ko iti. E Rimon…®n ziam fer d…®penim…®n aven zuir dughiam…®n, atrivim nan agharim…®n suisi. Egha a tevibar p…®ra asem Rimon ziam fer dughiam…®n, a na getuima, k…® uaghan aser kam…®n marvir guam…®n borogh…®n teviba ap…®ri. K…® fo, k…® uamategh mang…®t…®, arazir kam g…®n uam otivam. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God nan arazir kuraba g…®n amangasa k…® ifonge.‚Äù
\p 
\v 19 Ez…® Elisa ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® os…®man mark…®. N…® navir am…®rizim inigh mang…®.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Naman Elisa ategha ghu. Egh a t…®ghar saghon mangamin dughiam…®n,
\v 20 Elisan ingangarir gumazim, Gehasi, uab…®ra kamagh…®n uab…® m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúNan gumazir ekiam, Sirian gumazim Naman ataghiz…®, a pura zui. Manmaghsua a bizir Naman a dan…®ngamim inizir puvat…®? Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam…®n, k…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei, k…® Naman…®n g…®n ivegh mang…®, egh a da bizitaba inigham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 21 Egha d…®kavigha Naman…®n g…®n zui. Ez…® Naman garima, gumazir mam an g…®n ivegha izi, ez…® a uan karis ategha ghuaghira tuavim…®n tughav itima, Gehasi iza a bato. Ez…® Naman kamagh…®n Gehasin azara, ‚ÄúBizitam ia batoz, o?‚Äù
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® Gehasi ghaze, ‚ÄúPuvat…®. Nan gumazir ekiam kamagh…®n n…® m…®k…®masa na amada: God…®n akam inigha izir gumazimning dat…®r…®gh…®ra an d…®penim…®n ize. Aning Efraim…®n m…®ghs…®aba itir God…®n akam inigha izir gumazimning. Ga uaning, n…® silvan beghiam ko korotiar pumuning, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir kamning bagh dar an…®ngigh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 23 Ez…® Naman kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúBeghiar vam…®ra mark…®, n…® pumuning inigh.‚Äù A m…®gh…®ghav…®ra da iniasa Gehasi m…®gei, ez…® Gehasi da iniasa ifonge. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Naman beghiar pumuning isa silvan av…®riba aning gaghui, silvan kabar d…®bobonim, 60,000 kinan tu. Egha uaghan korotiar aghuir pumuning ini, egha bizir kaba inigha uan ingangarir gumazimning gan…®ngi, ez…® aning da atera Gehasin faragha zui.
\v 24 Me ghua Samarian m…®ghs…®am…®n otivigha, Gehasi bizir kaba inigha d…®penim…®n aven da at…®. Egha ingangarir gumazir kamning, ua Naman bagha aning amada.
\v 25 Aning ghuz…®, Gehasi ua d…®penim…®n aven ghugha Elisan damazim…®n tu. Ez…® Elisa kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúGehasi, n…® managh ghugha izi?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Gehasi ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir ekiam, k…® danganitam…®n ghuzir puvat…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 26 Ez…® Elisa kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® ifaran mark…®. N…® ti ghaze, k…® n…®n ganizir puvat…®, a? Nan duam n…® ko ikia garima, gumazir kam karis ategha n…® bativasa izaghir…®. Gehasi, kar dag…®aba ko, korotiaba ko, oliv…®n azeniba ko, wain…®n azeniba ko, sipsipba ko, bulmakauba ko, ingangarir gumazamizir k…®niba iniamin dughiam puvat…®. Arazir kam derazir puvat…®.
\v 27 N…® Naman da dag…®aba ini. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, lepan ar…®mariar faragha Naman…®n ikezir kam, a dat…®r…®gh…®n n…®n ikiam. Egh n…® ko g…®n otivamin adarasi, ia zurara lepan ar…®mariar kam iniam.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Gehasi Elisa ataghizir dughiam…®n, Gehasi lepan ar…®mariam ini. Ez…® an m…®karzim, ghuariar ghurghurim…®n m…®n bar ghurghuri.
\c 6
\s1 Elisa sobiav zem gamiz…®, a ua d…®pam…®n azenan oto
\p 
\v 1 Dughiar kam…®n, Elisa God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir okoruam…®n gara me geghufi. Ez…® dughiar mam gumazir kaba kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúEn d…®penim sufi, egha en tughat…®zir puvat…®.
\v 2 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® e ateght…®, e bar Jordan…®n Fanem…®n mangam. Egh e vaghvagh temer vam…®ra vam…®ram okam. Egh e uari bagh d…®penir igiatam, Jordan…®n Fanem…®n m…®riam…®n an ingaram.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Elisa ghaze, ‚ÄúA dera, ia mamagh…®n damu.‚Äù
\p 
\v 3 Ez…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGa uaning, gumazir ekiam, n…® e ko izasa e ifonge.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Elisa a ikara, ‚ÄúA dera, k…® ia ko mangam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Egha a me ko ghua Jordan…®n Fanem…®n otivigha, magh…®ra temeba oti.
\v 5 Me ingara itima, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam…®n sobiav zem asiaghir…®gha d…®pam giraghu. Ez…® akam inigha izir gumazir kam uan sobiam inian iburagha kamagh…®n dei, ‚ÄúAme! Gumazir ekiam, k…® gumazir igharazim…®n sobiam inigha ize. Ez…® a d…®pam giraghu.‚Äù
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Elisa, kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúSobiam managh…®ra iraghu?‚Äù Ez…® akam inigha izir gumazim, sobiam iraghuzir danganim…®n Elisan aka. Ez…® Elisa temer aguar dozir mam atugha, sobiam iraghuz…® nagh…®n d…®pam m…®k…®ni, ez…® sobiam uam anabo.
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® Elisa ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® dat…®r…®gh…®n sobiam inigh.‚Äù Ez…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim uan dafarim amadagha sobiam ini.
\s1 Elisa Sirian m…®dorozir gumazibar t…®fa
\p 
\v 8 Dughiar mam…®n, Sirian atrivim uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko iz…® Israelia m…®soghasa. Egha atrivim uan gumazir dapaniba ko, uariv g…®a n…®ghn…®zim batogha ghaze, me danganir me ikiamim…®n ingarigh, egh kagh ikegh d…®kavigh mang…® Israelia m…®sogham.
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Elisa, a Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba ikiamin danganim g…®fo, egha Israelian atrivim bagha akam amada. A uaghan Israelian atrivim m…®g…®a ghaze, Israelia danganir kam…®n borogh…®n mangan mark…®. Me an borogh…®n mang…®t…®, Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba me gas…®ghasigham.
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® atrivim akar kam baregha, m…®dorozir gumaziba danganir Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba ikiamin nagh…®n ikiasa me amada. Ez…® Siriaba danganir kam…®n otivigha Israelian m…®dorozir gumazibar garima, me fom…®ra iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me danganir kam…®n ikian ibura. Arazir kam dughiar av…®ribar otifi.
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® Sirian atrivim bizir kam bang…®n n…®ghn…®zir kurar bar av…®ribagh ami. Egha a uan gumazir dapanibar diaz…®, me izima a men atara pamtem…®n kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa na m…®kemegh, en gumazir manam Israelian atrivim…®n akurvasi?‚Äù
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® an m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanir mam a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúO atrivim, en gumazitam arazir katam gamizir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®. Kar Elisara, a Israelian God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim. E damuasa amir biziba bar, a zurara Israelian atrivim m…®gei. N…® m…®geir akaba Elisa bar a dagh fo. N…® akuir danganim…®n ik…® m…®k…®mt…®, Elisa fogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n gumazir dapanibav gei, ‚ÄúIa mang…® fogh, Elisa danganir manam…®n iti. Egh ia m…®dorozir gumaziba amadaght…®, me mang…® an suiragh.‚Äù Ez…® me ghua kamagh…®n fo, Elisa Dotan…®n nguibar ekiam…®n iti.
\p 
\v 14 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, atrivim m…®dorozir gumazir av…®rim am…®sefe, egha me amangiz…® me hoziaba ko karisba inigha Dotan…®n ghue. Me ghua d…®magarim…®n otivigha nguibam koro.
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® bar m…®zaraghara Elisan ingangarir gumazim d…®kavigha d…®penim…®n azenan ghu. Egha a garima, Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba uan hoziaba ko karisba sara nguibar ekiam ek…®arugha g…®fa. Egha a ghua kamagh…®n Elisa m…®gei, ‚ÄúAme! Gumazir ekiam, Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba e ek…®arugha g…®fa. E manmagh…®n damuam?‚Äù
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® Elisa kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® atiatingan mark…®. Me guizbang…®ra m…®dorozir gumazir av…®rim iti, ez…® en akurvaghamin m…®dorozir gumazir bar av…®rim iti, ez…® en m…®dorozir gumazibar d…®bobonim, men m…®dorozir gumazibar d…®bobonim bar a gafira.‚Äù
\p 
\v 17 Ez…® Elisa kamagh…®n God ko m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® gumazir kam…®n damazimning kuight…®, a k…® m…®geir darazir ganika.‚Äù Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ingangarir gumazir kam…®n damazimning kuiz…®, a garima, hoziar av…®riba ko karis…®n av…®riba Elisa itir m…®ghs…®ar kam bar a giz…®fa. Ez…® karisba ko hoziar kaba, da avim…®n m…®rara gari.
\p 
\v 18 Ez…® Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba Elisan suighasa izav…®ra itima, Elisa kamagh…®n God ko m…®gei, ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamaghsua, n…® Sirian m…®dorozir gumazibar damaziba okavight…®, me ganan kogham.‚Äù Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God men damaziba okafi.
\p 
\v 19 Ez…® Elisa danganir Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba itim…®n ghugha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa ti ongani. Tuavir kam, ia inigh nguibar ekiar ia mangasava amim…®n mang…®ghan kogham. Ez…® mark…®, ia nan g…®n iz…®t…® k…® ian aku gumazir ia ruir kam bagh mangam.‚Äù Ez…® me an g…®n zuima, a men akua Samarian nguibar ekiam…®n ghu.
\p 
\v 20 Egha me nguibar ekiam…®n aven ghue. Ez…® Elisa kamagh…®n God ko m…®gei, ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® Sirian m…®dorozir gumazibar damaziba kuight…®, me ua gan.‚Äù Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God men damaziba kuiz…®, me ua gari. Egha me kamagh…®n gara fo, me Samarian nguibar ekiam…®n aven iti.
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® Israelian atrivim men ganigha kamagh…®n Elisan azara, ‚ÄúGumazir ekiam, k…® ti me m…®sueght…® me ar…®ghiregham, a?‚Äù
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® Elisa ghaze, ‚ÄúPuvat…®. N…® m…®dorozim…®n aven apanibar suizir dughiam…®n, n…® zurara me m…®sozi me ariaghirir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® gumazir kabav soghan mark…®. N…® dagheba ko d…®paba me dan…®ng, eght…® me g…®n uan atrivim bagh uamategh mangam.‚Äù
\v 23 Ez…® Israelian atrivim Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba bagha isar ekiam gamigha me gan…®ngi. Me amegha g…®vaz…®, a ua me amangiz…® me Sirian atrivim bagha ghue. Egha dughiar kam…®n, Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba ua iza Israelia m…®sozir puvat…®.
\s1 Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba Samarian nguibar ekiam ek…®aru
\p 
\v 24 Azenir maba g…®vaz…®, Sirian Atrivim, Benhadat, uan m…®dorozir gumaziba akuvagha, Samarian nguibar ekiam konasa zui, egh Samaria m…®soghasa.
\v 25 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Samarian nguibar ekiam dagheba bar puvat…®. Ez…® Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba dughiar ruarim…®n nguibam ek…®arugha itima, Samarian gumazamiziba dagheba bagh mang…® da inigh nguibar ekiam…®n aven izasa ibura. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazitam donkin dapanim gives…®, kamagh…®n a 80 kinan a givezam. Eght…® gumazitam 250 grem…®n kuarazir bunbam…®n buaribagh ives…®, a 5 kinan dagh ivezam.
\p 
\v 26 Dughiar mam…®n Israelian atrivim nguibar ekiam av…®nizir d…®vazir m…®tiar gavgavim gis…®n arui, ez…® amizir mam kamagh…®n an dei, ‚ÄúO nan atrivim, n…® en akuragh!‚Äù
\p 
\v 27 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® ti ghaze, k…® wit ko wain iti, a? K…® ua manmagh…®n ian akuragham? Puvat…®. Ikiav…®ra Itir God ti n…®n akuragham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 28 Egha atrivim an azara, ‚ÄúK…® manmagh…®n n…®n akuraghasa n…® ifonge?‚Äù
\p Ez…® amizim kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGa amizir kamning, kamagh…®n akam ak…®ri, nan otarim ga faragh anemam, egh dughiar igharazim…®n, ga an otarim amam.
\v 29 \x - \xo 6:29 \xt God…®n Araziba 28:57; Azir Akam 4:10\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® uan otarim m…®suegha ga aneme. Egha am…®mzaraghan, k…® an borim m…®soghasa a m…®gei. Ez…® puvat…®. A uan otarim modogha g…®fa.‚Äù
\p 
\v 30 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, atrivim akar kam baregha bar osemegha, uan korotiam ab…®ki. A nguibar ekiam av…®nizir d…®vazir m…®tiar gavgavim gis…®n aruav…®ra itima, gumazamiziba dat…®r…®gh…®n an buaber korotiam…®n garima, atrivim uan korotiar azenan itim…®n aven aneru.
\v 31 Egha atrivim ghaze, ‚ÄúElisa en os…®mt…®zir kabar m…®ngarim. Ez…® k…® dat…®r…®gh…®ra an f…®rim atught…® an aremegham. K…® kamagh…®n damighan koght…®, God uab…® na m…®sueght…® k…® aremegham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 32 Atrivim kamagh…®n m…®g…®a, Elisa m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa gumazir mam amadaz…®, a ghu. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Elisa uan d…®penim…®n itima, Samarian gumazir dapanir maba a ko iti. Gumazir kam atrivim anemadaz…®, a t…®ghar izima, Elisa kamagh…®n gumazir dapanibav gei, ‚ÄúEn atrivim, a gumazir gumazibav sozi me ariaghirim. Egha a dat…®r…®gh…®n nan f…®rim aghorasa gumazir mam a amada. Eght…® gumazir kam iz…® otoghamin dughiam…®n, ia pamtem…®n tiam asaragh anep…®right…®, an aven izan kogham. Ez…® atrivim uab…® gumazir kam…®n g…®n izi.‚Äù
\p 
\v 33 Elisa m…®g…®av…®ra itima, gumazir kam atrivim ko oto. Egha atrivim kamagh…®n Elisa m…®gei,\f + \fr 6:33 \ft Hibrun akam…®n akar otevir kam, atrivim, vez…®n kam…®n puvat…®. Ez…® me kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, atrivim m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n Elisa gami.\f* ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God uab…® dughiar kurar kam gamiz…® an e bato. An en akurvaghs…® bizitam damighan kogham. E a m…®zuaman kogham.‚Äù
\c 7
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Elisa kamagh…®n akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, aruem gurum…®n kamagh…®ra gant…®, gumazamiziba nguibam…®n tiar akam…®n mang…®, egh me 1 kinara, 3 kilogrem plauan aghuir me wit…®n ingarizim givezam, egh 1 kinara, 6 kilogrem bali givezam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 2 Ez…® gumazir dapanir atrivim geghuva a ko izezim, Elisan akam baregha, kamagh…®n an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® oragh! Ikiav…®ra Itir God ti uan Nguibam…®n tiar akaba kuigh dagher av…®riba e gingegham, k…® ghaze, e zuam…®ra ti dagheba dag…®ar muziarim…®n kamagh…®n dagh ivezeghan kogham.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Elisa kamagh…®n gumazir dapanir kam m…®gei, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra, n…® bizir kam…®n gant…®, an otogham. Egh n…® dagher katam ameghan kogham.‚Äù
\s1 Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba are
\p 
\v 3 Ez…® aruer kam…®n 4plan gumazir lepan ar…®mariam itiba, me Samarian nguibar ekiam…®n, tiar akar ekiam…®n azenan iti. Egha me uarira uariv g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúE tizimsua puram apiav ikia ovevem m…®zuai?
\v 4 E mang…® dagheba buriam. E Samarian nguibar ekiam…®n aven mangan kogham. Me dagheba puvat…®, kamagh…®n amiz…®, m…®tiriam puv…®ra en aghegham. Egh uaghan, e danganir kamra dapiagh ik…®va ar…®ghiregham. E ti Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba itir danganim…®n mangam. Eght…® me e m…®sueght…®, e ar…®m…®ghiregham, a dera. Me uaghan e ateght…®, e angam…®ra ikiam, a uaghan deragham, pura bizim. E fo, e ovengasa iti.‚Äù
\p 
\v 5 Egha me bar guarat…®zim…®n d…®kavigha Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba itir danganim…®n ghue. Egha me danganim…®n borogh…®ra ghua garima, gumazitam itir puvat…®.
\v 6-7 Bar guizbang…®ra, Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba bar aregha g…®fa. Guarat…®zir kam…®n, Ekiam Sirian m…®dorozir gumazibagh amima, me n…®g…®nir ekiam barasi, mati m…®dorozir gumazir av…®rim uan hoziaba ko karisba ko izi. Egha Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba ghaze, ‚ÄúIa gan! Israelian atrivim ti Hitian atrivim ko Isip…®n atrivim givezez…®, aning uan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha e m…®soghasa izi.‚Äù Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba kamagh…®n m…®kemegha, d…®kavigha zuam…®ra danganim ategha arav ghue. Me uan averpeniba ko hoziaba, ko donkiba ataghiz…® da iti, egha me are. Me bizitam inigha ghuzir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® 4plan lepan gumazir kaba men danganim…®n otivigha, ghua averpenir mam…®n aven ghuegha garima, Sirian m…®dorozir gumazibar dagheba ko d…®paba iti. Ez…® me dagheba apa d…®paba saram api. Me g…®n silva ko gol ko korotiaba inigha ghua, danganir mam…®n da monge. Egha me ua iza averpenir igharazim…®n biziba uaghan da ini, egha me da isa ghua da modi.
\v 9 Egha g…®n me uarira uariv g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúE ti arazir aghuim gamir puvat…®. E bizir bar aghuim dat…®r…®gh…®n an gari, egh e mang…® gumazamizibav kemeka. E uan akabar kumigh ik…® mang…® am…®mzaraghan otogh, e ivezir kuram iniam. Aria, e mang…® atrivim…®n gumazir dapanibav kemeka.‚Äù
\p 
\v 10 Egha me d…®magarimra ua Samarian ghugha nguibar ekiam…®n tiar akam…®n garir gumazibar d…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúE Sirian m…®dorozir gumazibar danganim…®n ghuegha garima, gumazitam itir puvat…®. Egha uaghan gumazibar m…®g…®r…®g…®ataba baraghizir puvat…®. Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba, me arav ghue, ez…® men biziba bar men danganim…®n ikiav…®ra iti. Me hoziaba ko donkibar beniba f…®rizir puvat…®. Beniba men suighav…®ra itima, men averpeniba ikiav…®ra iti. Ez…® dagheba ko biziba averpenibar ikiav…®ra iti.‚Äù
\p 
\v 11 Tiar akam…®n garir gumaziba akar kam baregha, akam inigh atrivim…®n d…®penim mangasa gumazamizibar dei.
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® atrivim d…®magarim…®n akar kam ini. Egha d…®kavigha uan gumazir dapanibav m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® Sirian m…®dorozir gumazibar n…®ghn…®zim g…®fo. Me kamagh…®n fo e daghebar otefe. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me averpeniba ategha ghua, tuzir danganibar moga iti. Me ghaze, e nguibam ategh azenan mang…®t…®, me en suigh en nguibar ekiam iniam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® atrivim…®n gumazir dapanir mam kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúE ti gumazitaba ameght…®, me 5plan hoziar nguibam…®n ikiav…®ra itiba inigh mang…® fogham, bizir manam Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba bato. Eght…® Siriaba, e amangizir gumazir kabagh as…®ghasight…®, a dera, pura bizim. E fo, e bar nguibar ekiam…®n aven iti, e oveaghuezibar m…®n ar…®ghiregham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e gumazitaba ateght…®, me 5plan hoziar ikiav…®ra itiba inigh mangam.‚Äù\f + \fr 7:13 \ft Hibrun akam deragha akar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f*
\p 
\v 14 Egha me gumazir mabav sefe. Ez…® atrivim karis…®n pumuning ko hoziaba isa gumazir kabagh an…®ngi, egha me amangiz…® me foghasa ghue, bizir manam Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba bato.
\p 
\v 15 Egha gumazir kaba ghua kamagh…®n fo, Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba are. Ez…® me men g…®n ghua Jordan…®n Fanem…®n otogha, me iniba ko m…®sozir biziba ko men bizir igharazir tuavim…®n irezibar gani. Egha me uamategha iza atrivim m…®keme.
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® Samarian gumazamiziba bizir kam baregha, me zuam…®ra ivemara ghua, Sirian m…®dorozir gumazibar averpenibar men bizir me taghiziba ini. Egha me plauan av…®riba ko baliba ini. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, me 1 kinara, 3 kilogrem plauan aghuir me wit…®n ingarizim givesi, egha 1 kinara, 6 kilogrem bali givesi.
\v 17 Atrivim…®n akurvazir gumazir dapanim, atrivim nguibar ekiam…®n tiar akar ekiam…®n garir m…®dorozir gumazibar ganasa anem…®sefe. Ez…® a tiar akam…®n borogh…®ra tughav itima, gumazamiziba ivemara Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba faragha ikezir danganim…®n ghue. Gumazamizir av…®rim ivemara tiar akam…®n azenan ghua, anekuniz…®, a ir…®z…® me a d…®ka ghuav…®ra itima, an areme. Atrivim faragha ghua Elisan gani, ez…® Elisa God…®n akar kam isa atrivim gan…®ngi. Ez…® a dat…®r…®gh…®n guizbang…®n oto.
\p 
\v 18 Elisa faragha kamagh…®n atrivim m…®keme, ‚ÄúAruem gurum…®n kamagh…®ra gant…®, gumazamiziba nguibam…®n tiar akam…®n mang…®, egh me 1 kinara, 3 kilogrem plauan aghuir me wit…®n ingarizim givezam, egh 1 kinara, 6 kilogrem bali givezam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 19 Egha gumazir dapanir dat…®r…®gh…®n aremezir kam, a kamagh…®n Elisan akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® oragh! Ikiav…®ra Itir God ti uan Nguibam…®n tiar akaba kuigh dagher av…®riba e gingegham, k…® ghaze, e zuam…®ra ti dagheba dag…®ar muziarim…®n kamagh…®n dagh ivezeghan kogham.‚Äù
\p Egha Elisa kamagh…®n gumazir dapanir kam m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra, n…® bizir kam…®n gant…®, an otogham. Egh n…® dagher katam ameghan kogham.‚Äù
\v 20 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n bizir kam Elisa m…®kemez…® mogh…®n oto. Gumazir dapanir kam nguibam…®n tiar akam…®n tughav iti. Ez…® gumazamiziba dagheba iniasa ivemara azenan ghua, anekuniz…®, a ir…®z…® me a d…®ka ghuav…®ra itima, an areme.
\c 8
\s1 Sunem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n amizim, ua Israel…®n ize
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 8:1 \xt 2 Atriviba 4:8-37\x*Dughiar mam, Elisa ghua Sunem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n amizim m…®keme, amizir kamra an borim faragha areme, ez…® Elisa a gamiz…®, a ua d…®kafi. Elisa kamagh…®n amizim m…®keme, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, m…®tiriar ekiam…®n dughiam en nguazim…®n otivam, eght…® gumazamiziba 7plan azenibar dagheba puvat…®gham. Eght…® n…® uan pam ko borim inigh nguazir igharazim…®n mang…® ik…® mang…®t…®, dughiar kurar kam g…®vagham.‚Äù
\v 2 Ez…® amizir kam Elisan akam…®n g…®n ghua, uan pam ko borim inigha ghua Filistian nguazim…®n ikiav…®ra itima, 7plan azeniba g…®fa.
\v 3 Egha g…®n 7plan azenir kaba g…®vaz…®, a uan pam ko borim inigha ua Israel…®n ize. Egha a ua uan d…®penim ko nguazim iniasa atrivim…®n azangasa ghu.
\p 
\v 4 Amizim atrivim bagha zuima, atrivim Elisan ingangarir gumazim Gehasi m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGa uaning, n…® mirakel…®n ekiar Elisa amizibar na geghanasa k…® ifonge.‚Äù
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® Gehasi, Elisa fom…®ra otarir aremezim gamiz…® a ua d…®kavizir bizim geghari. Egha an egharav…®ra itima, amizir kam ua uan biziba iniasa atrivim…®n azangs…®ghasa izav oto. Ez…® Gehasi amizir kam…®n ganigha, kamagh…®n atrivim m…®gei, ‚ÄúAtrivim, n…® gan! Kar amizir kamra. Ez…® kar otarir aremezir kamra, Elisa a gamiz…® a ua d…®kafi.‚Äù
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® atrivim Elisa amizir bizim bagha amizir kam…®n azai, ez…® amizim a geghari. Egha g…®n atrivim uan gumazir dapanir mam…®n diaz…® a izima, a kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® amizir kam…®n akuraght…®, a uan biziba uamategh bar ada inigh. N…® uaghan an akuraght…®, a dagher azenibar otivizibar dag…®aba iniam, kar a 7plan azenibar kantrin igharazim…®n itima, an azenim…®n otivizir dagheba.‚Äù
\s1 Sirian Atrivim Benhadat areme
\p 
\v 7 Dughiar mam, Elisa Sirian nguibar ekiam Damaskus…®n ghu. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Sirian Atrivim Benhadat, ar…®mariam iti. Ez…® me kamagh…®n atrivim m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod…®n akam inigha izir gumazir kam Elisa, a dat…®r…®gh…®n Damaskus…®n iza kagh iti.‚Äù
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® atrivim uan gumazir dapanir mam Hasael kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® d…®kavigh bizir aghuitam God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim dan…®ng…®s…® a inigh mang…® an ganigh. Egh n…® a m…®kemeght…®, a kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azaragh, nan ar…®mariam g…®vagham, o puvat…®gham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Hasael bizir bar aghuir me Damaskus…®n ingariziba ini. Ez…® 40plan kamelba da ateram. Egha ada isa kamelbagh arigha Elisa bagha ghu. A ghua otogha kamagh…®n Elisan m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir Ekiam, Sirian Atrivim Benhadat, a n…®n otarim…®n m…®n iti, a uan ar…®mariam bagh n…®n azangasa na amada, an ar…®mariam g…®vagham, o puvat…®gham?‚Äù
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® Elisa kamagh…®n an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® kamagh…®n atrivim m…®kemegh, an ar…®mariam g…®vagham. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n nan aka, bar guizbang…®ra an aremegham.‚Äù
\v 11 Elisa akar kam gamigha g…®vagha, dughiar ruarim puv Hasael…®n gara ghuav…®ra itima, Hasael aghums…®gha n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh ami. Ez…® Elisa azi.
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® Hasael kamagh…®n an azai, ‚ÄúNan gumazir ekiam, n…® tizim bagh azi?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Elisa kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® fo, n…® g…®n arazir kurar av…®ribar Israelian gumazamizibar amuam. N…® uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, men d…®vazir gavgavibagh as…®ghas…®gh, egh dar apongt…® da isiam. Egh ia Israelian gumazir igiabav soght…® me ar…®ghiram. Egh ia borir muziariba, nguazim…®n me ap…®st…® me ar…®ghiram. Egh ia naviba adair amizibar garir dughiam, ia m…®dorozir sababa inigh men naviba of…®ram. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® azi.‚Äù
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 8:13 \xt 1 Atriviba 19:15\x*Ez…® Hasael akar kam baregha, kamagh…®n Elisan akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® pura gumazir k…®nim. K…® manmagh…®n bizir ekiar kam damuam?‚Äù Ez…® Elisa kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n nan akagha g…®fa, n…® Sirian atrivim…®n otivam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 14 Aning m…®kemegha g…®vagha, Hasael ua Atrivim Benhadat bagha ghu. Ez…® atrivim an azara, ‚ÄúElisa manmagh…®ra n…® m…®keme?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Hasael ghaze, ‚ÄúElisa ghaze, bar guizbang…®ra n…®n ar…®mariam g…®vaght…®, n…® ua deragham.‚Äù
\v 15 Egha am…®mzaraghan Hasael atrivim m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa n…®ghn…®si. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a inim inigha, d…®pam garugha a inigha ghua, atrivim…®n guam avara. Egha m…®gh…®gha an suiraz…®, atrivim am…®nim isava avegha, areme. Ez…® g…®n Hasael an danganim inigha uab…® Sirian atrivim…®n oto.
\ms1 Israel…®n kantri ko kantrin Judan eghaghanim ghua Israel…®n kantri ikuvizir dughiam…®n tu
\mr (Sapta 8:16--17:41)
\s1 Jehoram Judabar atrivim…®n oto
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 21:1-20)
\p 
\v 16 Ahap…®n otarim Joram, 5plan azenibar Israelian atrivim…®n iti, ez…® Jehosafat…®n otarim Jehoram, a uan afeziam…®n danganim inigha, Judabar atrivim…®n oto.
\v 17 A 32plan azeniba ikiava atrivim…®n oto, egha a 8plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n iti.
\v 18 A Israelian Atrivim Ahap…®n guivim…®n iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, an Ahap…®n adarazi ko Israelian atrivir igharazibar arazir kurabar g…®nt…®si. Egha arazir kurar av…®riba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh ami.
\v 19 \x - \xo 8:19 \xt 1 Atriviba 11:36\x*Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Judan kantri gas…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®. Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan ingangarir gumazim, Atrivim Devit g…®n…®ghn…®si. A fom…®ra Devit ko akar d…®k…®r…®zim gamua ghaze, Devit…®n ik…®zibar tong…®n gumazitam zurara atrivim…®n ikiam, eght…® Devit…®n lam…®n angazangarim mungeghan kogham. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God akar d…®k…®r…®zir kam g…®n…®ghn…®si. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a Judan kantri gas…®ghas…®ghan aghua.\f + \fr 8:19 \ft N…® 1 Atriviba 11:36…®n gan.\f*
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 8:20 \xt Jenesis 27:40\x*Dughiar Jehoram Judan atrivim…®n itim…®n, Idomian gumazamiziba an akam batogha an apengan ikian aghua. Egha me uari bagha atrivir mam am…®sefe, ez…® a me gativagha men gari.
\v 21 Ez…® Jehoram d…®kavigha uan m…®dorozir gumazir karisbar tuiva m…®soziba inigha, me Idomia m…®soghasa Sair…®n nguibar ekiam…®n amadaghan ghue. Me ghua otiviz…® Idomian gumaziba iza Jehoram…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba ek…®arugha, me m…®soghasa. Ez…® d…®magarim…®n, Jehoram uan m…®dorozir gumazir karisbar m…®soziba ko, me bar pamten m…®sogha Idomian gumaziba adugha zui. Ez…® Israelian m…®dorozir gumazir igharaziba m…®dorozim ategha, uamategha ara uan nguibabar ghue.
\v 22 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Judaba Idomia d…®kab…®razir puvat…®. Ez…® Idomian gumazamiziba, uari uan kantri gativagha ikia iza dat…®r…®gh…®n tu. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, Lipnan gumazamiziba uaghan akaba batogha, ua Judabar apengan itir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 23 Atrivim Jehoram amizir bizir igharazibar eghaghaniba, da ak…®nafarir me kamagh…®n d…®borim, Judan Atrivibar Eghaghaniba, an aven iti.
\v 24 Ez…® g…®n Atrivim Jehoram uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremez…®, me an kuam inigha Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n ghua, an inazir afeziabar moziba itir danganim…®n anefa. Ez…® an otarim Ahasia, an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto.
\s1 Ahasia Judabar atrivim…®n oto
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 22:1-6)
\p 
\v 25 Ahap…®n otarim Joram, a 12plan azenibar Israelian atrivim…®n itima, Jehoram…®n otarim Ahasia, Judabar atrivim…®n oto.
\v 26 Ahasia a 22plan azeniba ikia, egha atrivim…®n oto. Egha azenir vam…®ran Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n ike. An amebam, Atalia, a Israelian Atrivim Omrin, igiar guivim.
\v 27 Ahasian amebam Ahap…®n ik…®zim…®n ize, kamagh…®n amiz…®, a Ahap…®n ik…®zim…®n arazir kurabar g…®n ghua, arazir kuraba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh ami, mati Ahap…®n ik…®zim amiz…® mok…®n.
\p 
\v 28 Dughiar mam…®n, Atrivim Ahasia, Israelian Atrivim Joram…®n porogha a ko ghua, aning Sirian Atrivim Hasael…®n m…®sosi. Me Gileat…®n Distrigh…®n, Ramot…®n nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®ra uariv sosi. Ez…® Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba Joram b…®raz…®, a bar ikufi.
\v 29 Ez…® Joram m…®dorozim ategha ghua, Jesril…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ikia, ua deraghasa m…®zua iti. A Jesril…®n ikiav…®ra itima Atrivim Ahasia an ganasa ghu.
\c 9
\s1 God Jehu am…®sevez…®, a Israelian atrivim…®n oto
\p 
\v 1 Atrivim Joram Jesril…®n nguibar ekiam…®n itima, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Elisa, akam inigha izir gumazibar okoruam…®n tong…®n, gumazir igiar mam…®n diaz…® a ize. Ez…® a kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® deraghv…®ra uan inim kegh, egh oliv…®n borem itir m…®sevir muziarim inigh d…®kavigh Gileat…®n Distrigh…®n itir nguibar ekiam Ramot…®n mang…®.
\v 2 Egh n…® Ramot…®n otogh, mang…® Jehosafat…®n otarim Jehu batogh,\f + \fr 9:2 \ft Jehun afeziam, a Judan atrivim…®n ikezir gumazir kam Jehosafat puvat…®. Atrivim Jehosafat…®n eghaghanim, a 1 Atrivim sapta 22 ko 2 Atrivim sapta 3…®n iti. Jehosafat, a gumazir igharazim.\f* a Nimsin igiavotarim. Eght…® a uan namakaba ko ik…®t…®, n…® a inigh danganir mogomer tam…®n aven mang…®.
\v 3 Egh borem itir m…®sevir kam inigh borem an dapanim gingegh kamagh…®n a m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian atrivim…®n ikiasa n…® am…®sefe.‚Äô N…® bizir kam damigh g…®vagh, egh tiar akam kuigh zuam…®ram ar…® mang…®gh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Elisa m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir igiar kam d…®kavigha Ramot…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghu.
\v 5 Egha an otogha garima, Jehu aperaghav ikia m…®dorozir gumazibar, gumazir dapanir igharaziba ko m…®gei. Egha a Jehu m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir ekiam, k…® akar mam n…®n iti.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Jehu an azara, ‚ÄúEn tinara, n…® akam an iti?‚Äù
\p Ez…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…®rara, k…® akam n…®n iti.‚Äù
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 9:6 \xt 1 Atriviba 19:16\x*Ez…® Jehu d…®kavigha d…®penim…®n aven ghuz…®, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim an g…®n ghua oliv…®n borem inigha Jehun dapanim ginga kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelian God, kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòK…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Israelian atrivim…®n ikiasa n…® am…®sefe. Eght…® n…® nan gumazamiziba Israelia, me gativagh men ganam.
\v 7 Egh n…® Ahap…®n ik…®zim m…®sogh…®rar…®kigh, kar atrivir n…® fom…®ra an ingangarir gumazir dapanim…®n ikezim. Eght…® k…® arazir kam…®n, Atrivir Amizim Jesebel…®n arazir bar kuraba ikarvagham. Kar fom…®ra nan akam inigha izir gumaziba ko nan ingangarir gumazibav soghez…®, me ariaghirezir amizim.
\v 8 Eght…® k…® Ahap…®n adarazi bar me gas…®ghasigham. Bar guizbang…®ra, Israelian tong…®n otivir Ahap…®n ik…®zim…®n gumaziba, k…® bar mogh…®ra me ag…®vagham, gumazir igiaba ko aruaba sara.
\v 9 K…® bar fom…®ra Nebat…®n otarim Jeroboam…®n ik…®zim, ko Ahiyan otarim Atrivim Basan ik…®zim gas…®ghas…®ki. Egh kamagh…®ra k…® Ahap…®n ik…®zim bar me gas…®ghasigham.
\v 10 \x - \xo 9:10 \xt 1 Atriviba 21:23\x*Eght…® Atrivir Amizim Jesebel aremegham, eght…® an kuam afamin gumaziba puvat…®gham. Puvat…®, afiaba Jesril…®n nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®ram an kuam amam.‚Äô ‚Äù Ez…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir kam Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akar kam…®n gun m…®kemegha g…®vagha, tiar akam kuigha arav ghu.
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 9:11 \xt 2 Atriviba 9:33-36\x*Ez…® Jehu ua atrivim…®n gumazir dapanir igharaziba bagha ghuz…®, men mav an azara, ‚ÄúBiziba bar deraghv…®ra iti, o? Manmaghsua gumazir onganir kam iza n…®n gani?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Jehu kamagh…®n an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIa gumazir kamagh…®n garibar arazibagh fo, me zurara pura tintinibar m…®g…®r…®g…®abagh ami.‚Äù
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® me kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® ifari. N…® deraghv…®ra e m…®k…®m. N…® e gifar akam mongan mark…®.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Jehu bighav…®ra kamagh…®n gumazir dapanibav gei, ‚ÄúGumazir kam iza kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, a Israelian atrivim…®n ikiasa na m…®sevegha g…®fa.‚Äô ‚Äù
\v 13 Gumazir dapaniba akar kam baregha, zuam…®ra uan korotiar ruariba suegha d…®penim…®n adidiaba ave, ez…® Jehu ad…®diam…®n tughav iti. Ez…® me s…®gham givia kamagh…®n dei, ‚ÄúJehu atrivim…®n otogha g…®fa.‚Äù
\s1 Jehu, Israelian Atrivim Joram m…®soghez…®, an areme
\p 
\v 14-15 Jehu, a Jehosafat…®n otarim, egha Nimsin igiavotarim. A dat…®r…®gh…®n nguibar ekiam Ramot…®n ikia, egha Atrivim Joram m…®sueght…® an aremeght…®, an an danganim inigh atrivim…®n otivasa uan gumazir dapaniba ko akabar k…®ri. Ez…® Atrivim Joram Jesril…®n ikiav…®ra iti. Faragha Israelia, Sirian Atrivim Hasael ko m…®sozir dughiam…®n, Atrivim Joram m…®dorozim…®n aven os…®mt…®zir ekiam ini, egha a derazir puvat…®. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Jehu uan gumazir dapaniba kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa na ko navir vam…®ra ik…®, egh ia deraghv…®ra gan, egh gumazitam ateght…®, a Ramot ategh Jesril…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazamiziba bagh mang…®, bizir k…® damuamin kabar gun m…®k…®man mark…®.‚Äù
\v 16 Egha Jehu uan karis…®n anabogha, m…®dorozir gumazir maba ko me Ramot ategha Jesril…®n ghue. Atrivim Joram…®n ar…®mariam g…®vazir puvat…®, egha a Jesril…®n uan dakozim gir…®ghav iti. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, Judan Atrivim Ahasia, Joram…®n ganasa Jesril…®n ghugha, aning uaghara Jesril…®n iti.
\p 
\v 17 Ez…® ganganir gumazir mam, nguibar ekiam Jesril av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n tauan tughav ikia garima, Jehu ko an m…®dorozir gumaziba izi. Ez…® a dia kamagh…®n gumazir nguibam…®n itibav gei, ‚ÄúK…® m…®dorozir gumazir av…®rim…®n garima, me izi.‚Äù
\p Ez…® gumazir maba ghua, ganganir gumazir kam…®n akabar gun Atrivim Joram m…®kemez…®, a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa m…®dorozir gumazitam m…®kemeght…®, a hoziam inigh, ivegh mang…® me batogh kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòBiziba bar ti ian deraz, o puvat…®?‚Äô ‚Äù
\p 
\v 18 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazir mam hoziam gaperagha ivegha ghua kamagh…®n Jehu m…®gei, ‚ÄúAtrivim kamagh…®n foghasa, biziba bar ti ian deraz, o puvat…®?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Jehu an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúKar n…®n bizim puvat…®. N…® pura en g…®n iz…®.‚Äù
\p Ez…® ganganir gumazim, m…®dorozir gumazir kam bagha garav…®ra itima, a ua izezir puvat…®. Ez…® a kamagh…®n atrivim bagha akam amada, ‚ÄúM…®dorozir gumazir n…® amadazim, a ghua me bato, egha ua izezir puvat…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 19 Ez…® atrivim m…®dorozir gumazir igharazim amadaz…®, a ghu. Egha m…®dorozir gumazir kam me batozir dughiam…®n, a uaghan kamagh…®n Jehu m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAtrivim kamagh…®n foghasa, biziba bar ti ian deraz, o puvat…®?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Jehu a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúKar n…®n bizim puvat…®. N…® pura en g…®n iz…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 20 Ez…® ganganir gumazim, m…®dorozir gumazir kam bagha garima, a izezir puvat…®, egha a kamagh…®n atrivim bagha akam amada, ‚ÄúM…®dorozir gumazir n…® amadazim, a uaghan ua izezir puvat…®. Ez…® k…® gumazir karis…®n itim…®n garima, a Nimsin otarim Jehu ami mogh…®n, bar arazir onganim gami. An hoziabagh amima da bar puv…®ra ivemara, karisba am…®k…®rvagha izi.‚Äù
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® Atrivim Joram ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® na bagh karis ak…®r.‚Äù Ez…® me anek…®righa g…®vaz…®, Israelian Atrivim Joram uan karis…®n anabo, ez…® Judabar Atrivim Ahasia karis…®n igharazim…®n ghuavanabo. Egha aning Jehu bativasa ghu. Egha aning ghua, Jesrilian gumazim Nabot…®n nguazim…®n borogh…®n a bato.
\p 
\v 22 Joram, Jehu batozir dughiam…®n, a kamagh…®n Jehun azara, ‚ÄúBiziba bar ti n…®n deraz, o puvat…®?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Jehu kamagh…®n an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúDa manmagh…®n deragham? N…®n amebam Jesebel asebar g…®n ghuav…®ra iti, egha arazir kuraba ko imezibagh amuav…®ra iti, mati tuavim…®n amizim tintinibar arua gumazir igharaziba ko akui mogh…®n ami. N…®n amebam…®n arazir kurar kaba bar ek…®va zui.‚Äù
\p 
\v 23 Joram, Jehun akar kam baregha, zuam…®ra uan karis giragha arav ghu. Egha kamagh…®n Ahasian dei, ‚ÄúAhasia, gumazir kam na ab…®nasa ize!‚Äù
\v 24 Egha Jehu uan barir pim bar pamtem…®n a gekuigha, Joram…®n ak…®rim gase. Ez…® barim an d…®ghorim ab…®ghiz…®, a uan karis…®n averiam gir…®gha areme.
\p 
\v 25 Ez…® Jehu, kamagh…®n gumazir dapanim Bitkar m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® Joram…®n kuam inigh Nabot…®n nguazim…®n anekunigh, kar Jesril…®n gumazim. N…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God fom…®ra Joram…®n afeziam Atrivim Ahap m…®kemezir akar kam g…®n…®ghn…®ghv…®ra ik…®. Dughiar kam…®n, ga uan karisning inigha Ahap…®n g…®n zuima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Ahap m…®keme.
\v 26 \x - \xo 9:26 \xt 1 Atriviba 21:19\x*‚ÄòK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® bogh…®mra gumazibar garima, me n…®n ifongiam…®n g…®n ghua, Nabot ko an otaribav soghez…®, me ariaghire. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, guizbang…®ra, k…® Nabot…®n nguazimra n…®n arazir kurar kaba ikaragham.‚Äô ‚Äù
\p Egha Jehu ua kamagh…®n Bitkar m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God fom…®ra m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, n…® Joram…®n kuam inigh mang…® Nabot…®n nguazir kam…®n anekunigh.‚Äù
\s1 Judan Atrivim Ahasia areme
\p 
\v 27 Ez…® Judan Atrivim Ahasia, Atrivim Joram…®n garima, an aremegha g…®vaz…®, a uan karis…®n ikia egha ara Bethagan…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghu. Ez…® Jehu uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko Ahasian ag…®nt…®si, egha Jehu kamagh…®n m…®dorozir gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa uaghan a gasegh!‚Äù Ez…® a uan karis…®n ghua Gur…®n m…®ghs…®am…®n ghuavanadima, me Ipleam…®n nguibam…®n borogh…®n a gase. Ez…® Ahasia bar ara ghua Megidon nguibar ekiam…®n ghugha g…®n areme.
\v 28 Ez…® Ahasian gumazir dapaniba an kuam inigha, karis…®n mam gat…®gha uam a inigha Jerusalem…®n ghu. Egha me Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n an inazir afeziabar mozibar danganim…®n anefa.
\p 
\v 29 Joram azenir namba 11…®n Israelian atrivim…®n itima, Ahasia Judabar atrivim…®n oto.
\s1 Me Atrivir Amizim Jesebel…®n m…®soghez…®, an areme
\p 
\v 30 Ez…® Jehu uan adarazi ko me Ahasian ag…®ntigha g…®vagha, ua Jesril…®n ize. Atrivir Amizim Jesebel danganir kam…®n ikiava, kamagh…®n akam baraki, Joram areme. Ez…® Jesebel uan damaziba agh…®va uan dapanir ar…®zim ad…®i, egha atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n aven tughav ikia, winduan beragha tuavim…®n gari.
\v 31 Egha Jehu nguibar ekiam…®n tiar akar ekiam…®n aven zuir dughiam…®n, Jesebel kamagh…®n an d…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúO Simri,\f + \fr 9:31 \ft Jesebel ziar kam Jehu gat…®, Simri. A fo, Simri fom…®ra atrivim…®n ingangarir gumazir mam, a uan atrivim m…®soghez…®, an areme. Ez…® Jehu dat…®r…®gh…®n uaghan arazir kamram ami. N…® 1 Eghaghaniba 16:8-20…®n gan.\f* n…® uan gumazir ekiam m…®soghez…® an aremezir gumazim, n…® ti deragha iti?‚Äù
\p 
\v 32 Jehu oregha winduan p…®n gara egha kamagh…®n dei, ‚ÄúTina nan adarazi bagh izasa ifonge? Tav iti, o?‚Äù Ez…® ingangarir gumazir maba atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n ikia, Jehun akam baregha, iza winduan beragh an gari.
\p 
\v 33 Ez…® Jehu kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa amizir kam akunight…® a izighir…®.‚Äù Ez…® me Jesebel akuniz…® a iraghu. Ez…® an ghuzim tintinibar d…®penir b…®riba ko hoziaba rue. Ez…® Jehu uan hoziaba ko karisbagh amima, da Jesebel…®n kuam d…®kab…®ri.
\p 
\v 34 Ez…® g…®n Jehu atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n aven ghughava api. A dagheba ko d…®paba amegha g…®vagha, kamagh…®n gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúGod kamagh…®n m…®kemegha g…®fa, amizir kurar kam mar ikufigh. Guizbang…®ra, amizir kam atrivir mam…®n guivim. Kamagh…®n amiz…® ia an kuam afagh.‚Äù
\v 35 Ez…® me an kuam inigha mozim dar…®ghasa azenan ghu. Egha me an kuam burima, a itir puvat…®. Me an dapanir agharim ko dagarimning ko dafarir beramningra gari.
\p 
\v 36 \x - \xo 9:36 \xt 1 Atriviba 21:23\x*Egha me ua ghuegha bizir kam…®n gun Jehu m…®geima, a ghaze, ‚ÄúBizir otozir kam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uan ingangarir gumazim Elaija, a Tisben nguibam…®n gumazim, an akam garugha m…®keme. Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®keme, ‚ÄòJesebel aremeghamin dughiam, afiaba iz…® Jesril…®n nguibar ekiam…®n an kuam amam.
\v 37 Eght…® an m…®karzir otevir m…®zumziariba tintinibar nguazim giregh ik…®va, afiar buaribar m…®n ganam. Eght…® gumaziba dar gan…®va, foghan kogham kar ti Jesebel…®n m…®karzir otevir naba, o?‚Äô ‚Äù
\c 10
\s1 Me Ahap…®n ik…®zim m…®soghez…®, me bar ariaghire
\p 
\v 1 Atrivim Ahap…®n otariba ko, an igiavotariba me Samarian nguibar ekiam…®n iti.\f + \fr 10:1 \ft Hibrun akam ghaze, Jesril. Gumazir fom…®ra itir maba Grigh…®n akam…®n akar kam g…®ra, me ghaze a Samarian nguibar ekiam…®n m…®gei.\f* Men d…®bobonim, 70…®n tu. Ez…® Jehu ak…®nafarir maba osirigha, Samarian gumazir dapaniba ko gumazir aruaba ko, gumazir Ahap…®n ovavir borir otaribar gariba bagha da amaga kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze,
\v 2-3 ‚ÄúAhap…®n otariba, ia ko iti. Ez…® ia m…®dorozir karisba ko hoziaba ko afuziba, ko m…®soghamin bizir maba sara ikia, egha d…®vazir gavgavim av…®nizir nguibar ekiam…®n iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, dughiar ia ak…®nafarir kaba iniamim…®n, ia Ahap…®n ovavir boribar tong…®n, gumazir bar aghuitam atrivim…®n ik…®s…® anem…®sefegh. Egh ia an akuragh a bagh m…®sogh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® gumazir dapaniba ko gumazir aruaba akar kam inigha, bar atiatigha ghaze, ‚ÄúJehu atrivir pumuning ab…®ragha g…®fa. Eght…® e manmagh…®n aneb…®ragham? E bar ibura.‚Äù
\p 
\v 5 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazir atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n garim ko nguibar ekiam…®n gumazir dapanir faragha zuim, ko gumazir aruaba, ko gumazir Ahap…®n ovavir boribar gariba, me Jehu bagha kamagh…®n akam amada, ‚ÄúE n…®n ingangarir gumaziba, e n…®n ifongiam…®n g…®n mangasa. E gumazitam am…®seveght…® an atrivim…®n otoghan kogham. Bar puvat…®gham. N…® tizim damus…®, n…® puram a damu.‚Äù
