\v 9 Egha am…®mzaraghan, Jehu d…®kavigha nguibar ekiam…®n tiar akam…®n ghugha dapanir kabar gari. Gumazamizir av…®rim danganir kam…®n iti, ez…® Jehu tugha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® uab…® uan gumazir ekiam Atrivim Joram ab…®raghasa n…®ghn…®si. Egha k…® a m…®soghez…® an areme. Egha k…® fo, ia gumazir kam m…®soghez…® an aremezir puvat…®. Ez…® tinara gumazir kabav soghez…®, me ariaghire? E fozir puvat…®.
\v 10 \x - \xo 10:10 \xt 1 Atriviba 21:20-24\x*Ez…® bizir kam kamagh…®n en aka, akar Ikiav…®ra Itir God fom…®ra isa Ahap…®n ik…®zim gan…®ngiziba, da bar guiz…®n otivaghiri. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God, akar a uan ingangarir gumazim, Elaijan akam garugha m…®kemezim, an otogha g…®fa.‚Äù
\v 11 \x - \xo 10:11 \xt Hosea 1:4\x*Egha g…®n Jehu, Ahap…®n ik…®zir Jesril…®n itir igharaziba, ko an gumazir dapaniba, ko an namakar aghuiba, ko an ofa gamir gumaziba, a bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Jehu tav ataghiz…® a itir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®.
\s1 Jehu, Atrivim Ahasian ik…®zim m…®soghez…®, me ariaghire
