\v 14 Ez…® Jehu akar kam baregha, kamagh…®n uan adaraziv gei, ‚ÄúIa gumazir kabar suikigh.‚Äù Ez…® me gumazir kaba bar men suigha, me inigha ghua mozir bar ekiam itir danganim…®n zui. Egha me Ahasian adarazi bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire, ez…® tav itir puvat…®. Men d…®bobonim, 42…®n ghu.
\s1 Jehu Ahap…®n ik…®zim…®n igharaziba bar me m…®soghez…®, me ariaghire
