\v 22 Me aven ghuegha g…®vaz…®, Jehu, ofa gamir gumazir korotiar aghua asem Bal…®n ziam febar garim, kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® korotiaba inigh, gumazamizir iza asem Bal…®n ziam febar an…®ngigh.‚Äù Ez…® gumazir kam Jehu m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ami.
