\v 23 Ez…® g…®n, Jehu ko Rekap…®n otarim, Jonadap aning Bal…®n ziam fer d…®penim…®n aven ghu. Egha Jehu kamagh…®n gumazamizibav gei, ‚ÄúIa deraghv…®ra uarir gan, egh uari asavsuigh, gumazamizir Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fe tam ti e ko ikiama. E gumazamizir asem Bal…®n ziam febara ikiam.‚Äù
\v 24 A m…®kemegha g…®vagha, Jonadap ko danganir ofa gamir dakozir itim…®n aven ghua, asem Bal bagha ofan bar isia m…®gh…®riba ko ofan igharazibagh ami.
\p Gumazamiziba t…®ghar izamin dughiam…®n, Jehu faragha 80plan m…®dorozir gumazibav sevegha asem Bal…®n ziam fer d…®penim…®n azenan m…®zuam ikiasa me m…®keme. Egha a kamagh…®n me m…®keme, ‚ÄúIa asem Bal…®n ziam fer gumazamiziba bar me m…®sueght…® me ar…®ghiregh. Eght…® m…®dorozir gumazitam gumazamizir kabar tav ateght…® an ar…®mang…®gham, m…®dorozir gumazir kam aremegham.‚Äù
