\v 25 Egha Jehu ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rizim gamigha g…®vagha, kamagh…®n uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko gumazir dapanibav gei, ‚ÄúIa aven iz…® bar me m…®sueght…® me ar…®ghiregh. Ia tav ateght…® an ar…® mangan mark…®.‚Äù Ez…® me aven ghua m…®dorozir sabam…®n bar me m…®suaghar…®ki. Egha me g…®n men kuaba inigha ghua nguibar ekiam…®n azenan da kuni. Egha me uamategha nguibar ekiam…®n itir Bal…®n ziam fer d…®penim bagha zui.
\v 26 Me Bal…®n ziam fer d…®penim…®n aven ghuegha, guarir ak…®nir asebar nedaziba itir gumaziba dar ziaba feba, inigha azenan iza avim…®n dagh aboro.
\v 27 Egha me asem Bal…®n marvir guam gas…®ghas…®gha, an ziam fer d…®penim gas…®ghas…®ki. Egha me asem Bal…®n ziam fer d…®penir kam gamiz…® a buarir d…®penim…®n oto, egha ikia iza dat…®r…®gh…®n tu.\f + \fr 10:27 \ft Akar kam, ‚Äúdat…®r…®gh…®n,‚Äù e itir dughiam m…®geir puvat…®. Puvat…®. A dughiar gumazim ak…®nafarir kam osirizim m…®gei.\f*
\p 
\v 28 Arazir kam…®n, Jehu asem Bal…®n ziam fer arazim ag…®fa, ez…® Israelia uam an ziam fer puvat…®.
\v 29-30 \x - \xo 10:29-30 \xt 1 Atriviba 12:28-30\x*Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Jehu m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® nan navir averiam…®n ifongiam…®n g…®n ghua, egha n…® bizir kaba Ahap…®n adarazigh ami, ez…® n…®n arazir kam nan damazim…®n dera. Kamagh…®n amiz…® k…® g…®n n…®n adarazir gumaziba ateght…®, me atrivibar otivam. N…®n ikegh mang…® n…®n otarim ko an otarim, ko an igiavotarim ko an az…®zim…®n tugham.‚Äù Ez…® g…®n Jehu Atrivim Jeroboam…®n arazir kurabar g…®n zui, gumazir kam a fom…®ra Israelia gekuiz…® me arazir kuram gami. Jeroboam gol…®n bulmakaun pumuning…®n ingarigha, mam inigha Betel…®n nguibam…®n anet…®, egha mam inigha Dan…®n nguibam…®n anet…®. Ez…® Jehu Israelia ataghiz…®, me bulmakaun kamning…®n ziam fe.
\v 31 Ez…® Jehu uaghan Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelian God…®n Araziba uan navir averiam…®n aven bar deraghav…®ra dar g…®n mangasa gavgavizir puvat…®. An ak…®rim ragha Jeroboam…®n arazir kurabagh asarazir puvat…®. Jeroboam, a fom…®ra Israelia gekuiz…®, me arazir kurabagh amizir atrivim.
\s1 Jehu areme
\p 
\v 32 Dughiar kam…®n Jehu atrivim…®n itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God kantrin igharaziba atagh…®razi, me Israelia gafigha men nguazir otevir maba isi. Sirian Atrivim Hasael Israelian nguazir otevir kam bar a iniasa me m…®sosi.
\v 33 A Jordan…®n Fanem…®n aruem anadi nagh…®n iti. Ez…® Hasael Israelia ab…®ragha, men nguazir kaba ini, a saut…®n amadaghan Arnon…®n Fanem…®n borogh…®n itir, Aroer…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ikegha ghua, not…®n amadaghan ghua, Gileat ko Basan…®n Distrighning…®n tu. Kar Gat…®n anabam, ko Ruben…®n anabam, ko Manasen anabam…®n akuar mam…®n adarazir nguaziba.
\p 
\v 34 Ez…® bizir igharazibar eghaghanir Atrivim Jehu amiziba, da ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti, me a d…®bora ghaze, Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghaniba. Ak…®nafarir kam ingangarir gavgavir an amiziba bar dagh eghari.
\v 35 Egha g…®n Jehu uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremez…®, me Samarian nguibar ekiam…®n mozim…®n anefa. Ez…® an otarim Jehoahas, an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto.
\v 36 Jehu Samarian ikia, 28plan azenibar Israelian atrivim…®n ike.
\c 11
\s1 Atalia Judan Atrivir Amizim…®n oto
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 22:10--23:15)
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Atrivim Ahasian amebam Atalia kamagh…®n akam baraki, an otarim Ahasia aremegha g…®fa, ez…® a zuam…®ra m…®dorozir gumazibav kemez…®, me Judan atrivibar ik…®zim…®n gumaziba bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire.
\v 2 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumaziba Ahasian otarim Joas m…®soghez…® an aremezir puvat…®. Me kamagh…®n fozir puvat…®, Atrivim Joram…®n guivim Jehoseba ko Atrivim Ahasian buaramizim, moga Joas inigha amizir an ganamim, ko aning isa danganir me daguivsiaba ar…®zim…®n aven aning modo. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Atalia Joas m…®soghez…® an aremezir puvat…®.
\v 3 Ez…® Jehoseba 6plan azenibar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven Joas modoz…® an a ko iti. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Atalia Judan atrivir amizim…®n ikiav…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® namba 7…®n azenim…®n Atalia amizir atrivim…®n itima, ofa gamir gumazim Jehoiada, m…®dorozir gumazir amizir atrivim…®n gariba ko, m…®dorozir gumazir atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n gariba, me bagha akam amaga ghaze, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n iz…®. Me izegha g…®vaz…®, Jehoiada me ko akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavir mam gami. A me bagha akar mam ak…®riz…®, me bizir a damuasa me m…®kemeziba bagha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavim gami. Ez…® a g…®n Ahasian otarim Joas inigha iza men aka.
\v 5-8 Egha Jehoiada kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúE Joas damight…® an atrivim…®n otivasa k…® ifonge. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® bizir ia damuamiba bagh ia m…®k…®masa. K…® fo, m…®dorozir gumazir okoruar pumuning Sabat…®n dughiam…®n, ingangarim ag…®vagha avughsi, ez…® igharaziba men danganiba isa ingangarim gami. Ez…® Sabat…®n kam otivasa, ez…® m…®dorozir gumazir okoruar 3pla, ia bar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim izasa k…® ifonge. M…®dorozir gumazir Sabat…®n dughiam…®n ingangarim gamiba, kar atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n gari darasi, ko Sur…®n tiar akam…®n garir darasi, ko m…®dorozir gumazir ak…®rang…®n tuivigha ikia, d…®vazim…®n tiar akam…®n gariba, me bar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n iz…® Joas geghuv an ganam. M…®dorozir gumaziba bar m…®dorozir sababar suigh…®va, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n danganiba bar da tuivigh ik…®, egh deraghv…®ram atrivim bagh gan. Eght…® a danganitam…®n mang…®t…®, m…®dorozir gumaziba a ko mang…®. Egh m…®dorozir gumaziba gumazitam ateght…®, an an borogh…®n izan mark…®. Eght…® gumazitam rogh…®ra iz…®t…®, me gumazir kam m…®sueght…® an aremegh.‚Äù\f + \fr 11:5-8 \ft Hibrun akam vez…®n kabar m…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevir maba deragha dar m…®ngariba ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f*
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazibar dapaniba, ofa gamir gumazim Jehoiadan akar kam…®n g…®n ghua Sabat…®n dughiam…®n, me m…®dorozir gumazir ingangarim ag…®vagha avughsasa amir kaba, ko m…®dorozir gumazir men danganiba iniamiba, bar men akua Jehoiada bagha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n izi.
\v 10 Dughiar kam…®n, Atrivim Devit…®n afuziba ko oraba, da Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n iti. Ez…® Jehoiada bizir kaba inigha m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanibagh an…®ngi.
\v 11 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumaziba ghua, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n uari bagha danganiba inigha, saut…®n amadaghan ikegha ghua not…®n amadaghan tu. Me uaghan ofa gamir dakozim…®n borogh…®n tuivighav ikia, egha m…®dorozir sababa suigha, atrivim ek…®arugha bar deraghv…®ra gara iti.
\v 12 M…®dorozir gumaziba uari ak…®righa m…®zua itima, ofa gamir gumazim Jehoiada, Joas…®n akua azenan iza, atrivibar dapanir asuam Joas…®n dapanim garu. Egha Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim itir ak…®nafarir r…®ghizir mam a gan…®ngi. Egha me g…®n oliv…®n borem Joas…®n dapanim gingegha anem…®sevez…®, an atrivim…®n oto. Ez…® gumazamiziba bar akuegha dafaribav sogha, kamagh…®n dei, ‚ÄúJoas dughiar ruarim…®n atrivim…®n ikiam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® Atrivir Amizim Atalia m…®dorozir gumaziba ko gumazamizibar d…®mdiam baregha, uan d…®penim ategha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n danganir gumazamiziba uari akuva itim…®n ghu.
\v 14 \x - \xo 11:14 \xt 2 Atriviba 23:3\x*A ghua otogha garima atrivir igiam, atriviba ami mogh…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n guam…®n itir guarir ak…®nim…®n borogh…®n tughav iti. Egha a m…®dorozir gumazibar dapaniba ko gumazir s…®ghabagh ivibar garima, me atrivir igiam…®n borogh…®n iti. A uaghan garima gumazamiziba bar akuegha, men marazi uaghan is…®ghabagh ivi. Ez…® Atalia puv atara uan korotiam ab…®gha d…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa gumazamizir kuraba. Ia bar arazir kuram gamua na ab…®nasa.‚Äù
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® Jehoiada Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n borogh…®n Atalia m…®sueght…® an aremeghan an aghua. Egha a kamagh…®n m…®dorozir gumazir dapanibav gei, ‚ÄúIa Atalian suiraght…®, m…®dorozir gumaziba anek…®arugh a kurugh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n azenan mang…®. Eght…® gumazitam an g…®n mang…®t…®, ia gumazir kam m…®sueght…® an aremegh.‚Äù
\v 16 Ez…® me Atalian suiragha, a inigha God…®n D…®penim ategha ghua atrivim…®n d…®penim av…®nizir d…®vazir hoziaba aven zuir tiar akam…®n aven ghugha, a m…®soghez…® an areme.
\s1 Ofa gamir gumazim Jehoiada gumazamizibar akuraz…®, // me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n g…®rara zui
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 23:16-21)
\p 
\v 17 God…®n ofa gamir gumazim Jehoiada, Atrivim Joas ko gumazamizibar akurvazi, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim gamua ghaze, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gumazamizibara ikiam. Egha a uaghan atrivim ko gumazamizibar akuraz…®, me uarir tong…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim gami.
\v 18 Egha g…®n gumazamiziba asem Bal…®n ziam fer d…®penim…®n ghua, bar a gas…®ghas…®ki. Egha me ofa gamir dakoziba ko asem Bal…®n marvir guabagh as…®ghas…®ki. Egha me Bal…®n ofa gamir gumazim Matan m…®soghez…® an areme. Ez…® Jehoiada m…®dorozir gumazir maba m…®sevez…® me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n gara a geghufi.
\v 19 Ez…® Jehoiada, m…®dorozir gumazibar dapaniba ko, m…®dorozir gumazir atrivim…®n gariba ko, atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n garir m…®dorozir gumaziba, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ghugha atrivir igiam inigha an akua atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n zuima, gumazamiziba bar men g…®n zui. Me bar ghua otivigha, tiar akar me kamagh…®n d…®borim, M…®dorozir Gumazibar Tiar Akam, an aven ghua Joas isava atrivir dabirabim gat…®z…® an a gapera.
\v 20 Ez…® gumazamiziba bar akonge. Me fo, m…®dorozir gumaziba atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n borogh…®n Atalia m…®soghez…® an areme. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazamiziba navir am…®rizim sara Jerusalem…®n apiaghav iti.
\v 21 Joas 7plan azeniba ikia, egha atrivim…®n oto.
\c 12
\s1 Joas Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim ak…®ri
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 24:1-14)
\p 
\v 1 Jehu Israelian atrivim…®n itima, an namba 7…®n azenim…®n aven Joas Judan atrivim…®n oto. Egha Joas Jerusalem…®n ikia, 40plan azenibar atrivim…®n iti. Joas…®n amebam Sibia, a Berseban amizim.
\v 2 Ez…® Joas atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, God…®n ofa gamir gumazim Jehoiada an n…®ghn…®zibar k…®ra zui, kamagh…®n amiz…®, Joas arazir aghuiba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh ami.
\v 3 Egha Joas, m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itir asebar ziaba fer d…®penibagh as…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®, ez…® gumazamiziba danganir kabar ghuav…®ra ikia ofabagh amua, egha pauran mughuriar aghuim zuiba tue.
\p 
\v 4 Dughiar mam…®n, Joas ofa gamir gumazibar diaz…® me izima a me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa ofa gamir gumazamiziba bar, dag…®ar me inigha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n iziba ini, kar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n takis…®n dag…®aba, ko dag…®ar gumaziba uan akar d…®k…®r…®zibar g…®n mang…® dan…®ngamiba, ko me uan ifongiabar God gan…®dir dag…®aba.\f + \fr 12:4 \ft Hibrun akam deragha vez…®n kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®. N…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n takis…®n dag…®abagh foghs…®, n…® Ua Me Ini 30:11-16…®n gan. Egh n…® akar d…®k…®r…®zim…®n dag…®abagh foghs…®, n…® Ofa Gami 27:1-7…®n gan.\f*
\v 5 Ia ofa gamir gumaziba vaghvagh, deraghv…®ra dag…®ar gumazamiziba ia gan…®dibar gan. Egh ia gant…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n danganitam ikuvigham, eght…® ia dag…®ar kabar taba inigh gumazibagh ivezeght…®, me danganir ikuvizir kam ak…®righam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® azenir mabar g…®n, kar Joas…®n namba 23plan azenibar an atrivim…®n iti, egha an ofa gamir gumazibar garima, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim ak…®rasa bizitam gamir puvat…®.
\v 7 Ez…® a Jehoiada ko ofa gamir gumazir igharazibar diaz…® me izez…®, a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa manmaghsua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n danganir ikuvigha itiba ak…®ran aghua? Kamagh…®n, ia gumazamiziba da isir dag…®abagh ativagh dar ganan mark…®. Ia dag…®ar kabar taba is…®, gumazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim ikuvizir bizibar k…®rs…® k…® m…®s…®vamibar an…®ngam.‚Äù
\v 8 Ez…® ofa gamir gumaziba Joas…®n akam…®n amamangat…®, egha me ua gumazamiziba da dag…®aba inian koghasa akam ak…®ri, egha uaghan me uari Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n bizir ikuvizibar ak…®ramin ingangaribar ganan kogham.
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® g…®n ofa gamir gumazim Jehoiada boksiar mam inigha, an asuam…®n torim gamigha, a isa ofa gamir dakozim…®n borogh…®n anet…®. Ez…® gumazamiziba iza Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aven zuir dughiam…®n, me boksiar kam…®n garima, an ofa gamir dakozim…®n agharir guivim…®n amadaghan iti. Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir D…®penim…®n tiar akam…®n gariba, me gumazamiziba inigha izir dag…®aba isa boksiar kam gazui.
\v 10 Egha ofa gamir gumaziba garima, boksiam iz…®vasava amima, me gumazir atrivim…®n ak…®nafariba osirim ko God…®n ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim bagha akam amada. Ez…® aning iza dag…®ar kaba isa m…®tarim gaghua da inigha ghua da medi.
\v 11-12 Me da mengegha g…®vagha, da isa Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim ak…®rir gumazir dapanibagh an…®di. Ez…® gumazir kaba dag…®aba isa gumazir d…®penibar ingariba, ko gumazir dag…®ar d…®penibar ingara foziba, ko dag…®aba aghorir gumazibagh ivesi. Egha me uaghan temer arariba, ko ingaramin dag…®abagh ivesi. Ez…® ingangarir kam…®n akurvazir bizir manaba iti, me uaghan dagh ivesi.
\v 13-14 Ez…® silvan dag…®ar me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n iniziba, da ingangarir vam…®ra iti, kar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim ak…®ramin dag…®aba. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me dag…®ar kaba inigh, itarir ekiaba, ko itarir me silvan ingariziba, ko s…®ghaba, ko bizir lam amungamiba, ko Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven, ingaramin bizir igharazir me gol ko silvan ingariziba, me dagh ivezan kogham.
\v 15 \x - \xo 12:15 \xt 2 Atriviba 22:7\x*Gumazir ingangarim…®n gariba me dag…®aba okeir puvat…®. Ez…® gumazir aruaba dag…®ar kaba bagha men azangs…®zir puvat…®, me manmagh…®ra dag…®ar kabagh ami.
\v 16 \x - \xo 12:16 \xt Ofa Gami 7:7\x*Ez…® dag…®ar gumazamiziba os…®mt…®zim agevir ofa bagha an…®diba, ko dag…®ar arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofaba bagha an…®diba, me da isa Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n itir boksiam gazuir puvat…®. Me da isa God…®n ofa gamir gumazibagh an…®di.
\s1 Sirian atrivim Judabav soghasa
\p 
\v 17 Atrivim Joas Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim ak…®rasa gumazibav sevegha g…®fa, ez…® g…®n, Sirian Atrivim Hasael uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, iza Get…®n nguibar ekiam koro. Me Getia ab…®ragha g…®vagha, egha ragha Jerusalemia ko m…®soghasa ghue.
\v 18 Ez…® Atrivim Joas, Atrivim Hasael iz…® Jerusalem m…®soghan aghuagha, bizir ekiar bar aghuim isa Hasael bagha anemada. Joas…®n inazir afeziaba, kar Atrivim Jehosafat ko, Atrivim Jehoram ko, Atrivim Ahasia, me bar Joas…®n ifongiam…®n g…®n ghua, bizir bar aghuiba isa Ikiav…®ra Itir God gan…®ngi. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Joas bar a da ini. Egha a uaghan Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim ko atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n dag…®aba modir danganim…®n itir golba bar ada ini. Egha a bizir bar aghuir kaba Sirian Atrivim Hasael bagha da amada. Ez…® Hasael da inigha g…®vagha, Jerusalem ategha ghu.
\p 
\v 19 Ez…® bizir igharazibar eghaghanir Atrivim Joas amiziba, da ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti, me a d…®bora ghaze, Judabar Atrivibar Eghaghaniba.
\v 20-21 Dughiar mam…®n, Joas…®n ingangarir gumaziba Joas m…®sueght…®, an aremeghasa akam ak…®ri. Ez…® men mamning, Simeat…®n otarim Josakar, ko Somer…®n otarim Jehosabat, aning tuavim…®n itir d…®penir mam…®n a m…®soghez…® an areme, kar tuavir ghuaghira Silan nguibam…®n otozim. D…®penir kam, me fom…®ra Jerusalem…®n borogh…®n nguazibagh kua da isa Jerusalem…®n danganir ira ghuezibav k…®ra da apemezir danganim…®n iti. Kamagh…®ra Joas aremez…®, me an kuam isa Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n ghua an inazir afeziaba ko anefa. Ez…® an otarim Amasia, an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto.
\c 13
\s1 Joahas Israelian atrivim…®n oto
\p 
\v 1 Ahasian otarim, Joas a 23plan azenibar Judabar atrivim…®n itima, Jehun otarim, Joahas a Israelian atrivim…®n oto. Egha a 17plan azenibar Samarian nguibar ekiam…®n atrivim…®n iti.
\v 2 Nebat…®n otarim, Atrivim Jeroboam arazir kuram gamiz…® mogh…®n, Joahas arazir kuram Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n a gami. Jeroboam fom…®ra Israelia gekuiz…®, me arazir kuraba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh gami. Ez…® Jeroboam amizir arazir kaba, Joahas dat…®r…®gh…®n arazir kamagh…®ra garibagh ami, egha da ataghizir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®.
\v 3 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God puv…®ra Israelian atari, egha Sirian Atrivim Hasael ataghiz…®, a dughiar av…®ribar iza Israelia m…®sogha me ab…®ri. Ez…® g…®n Hasael…®n otarim Benhadat, Sirian atrivim…®n oto. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God anetaghiz…®, a uaghan Israelia d…®kab…®nasava ami.
\v 4 Ez…® Atrivim Joahas Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®gei. Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God fogha g…®fa, Sirian atrivim bar pazav…®ra Israelia gami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, God Joahas…®n d…®mdiam baraki.
\v 5 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian akurvaghasa gumazir mam am…®sefe, ez…® gumazir kam Siriabar dafarim da ua me ini. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Israelia fom…®ra deragha ikez…® mogh…®n, dat…®r…®gh…®n men nguibabar dabirabim ua dera.
\v 6 Egha me arazir kurar kam ataghizir puvat…®, kar arazir kurar Jeroboam…®n ik…®zim fom…®ram amiziba. Jeroboam uaghan Israelia gekuiz…®, me dagh ami. Me dat…®r…®gh…®n arazir kurar kabagh amuav…®ra iti. Egha me aser amizim Aseran marvir guar Samarian itim, me a batoghezir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba Israelian m…®dorozir gumazir av…®ribav soghez…® me ariaghire. Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba bar puv…®ra me gamua, me d…®kab…®ra me gamima me nguazir m…®nemniam…®n m…®n otifi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, dughiar kam…®n, Joahas m…®dorozir gumazir av…®riba puvat…®. Israelia dat…®r…®gh…®n 50plan m…®dorozir gumazir hoziabagh apia m…®sozibara iti. Egha me m…®soghamin 10plan karisba ikia, egha 10,000plan m…®dorozir gumazir igharaziba iti.
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® bizir igharazibar eghaghanir Atrivim Joahas amiziba, da ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghaniba. Ak…®nafarir kam, ingangarir gavgavir an amiziba bar dagh eghari.
\v 9 Egha g…®n Joahas uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremez…®, me an kuam inigha Samarian nguibar ekiam…®n ghua anefa. Ez…® an otarim Jehoas, an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto.
\s1 Jehoas Israelian atrivim…®n oto
\p 
\v 10 Joas 37plan azenibar Judan atrivim…®n iti, ez…® Joahas…®n otarim Jehoas, a Israelian atrivim…®n oto. Egha 16plan azenibar atrivim ikia, Samarian nguibar ekiam…®n iti.
\v 11 Nebat…®n otarim, Atrivim Jeroboam fom…®ra arazir kuram gamiz…® mogh…®n Atrivim Jehoas arazir kuram Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n a gami. Jeroboam fom…®ra Israelia gekuiz…®, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kuram gami. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Jehoas, Jeroboam…®n m…®n arazir kurar kamagh…®ra garibagh ami. Egha an arazir kurar kaba ataghizir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®.
\v 12 Ez…® bizir igharazibar eghaghanir Atrivim Jehoas amiziba, da ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghaniba. Ak…®nafarir kam, Israelian Atrivim Jehoas, Judan Atrivim Amasian adarazi ko m…®soghezir dughiam…®n, amizir bizir gavgavibagh eghari.
\v 13 Ez…® g…®n Jehoas uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremez…®, me an kuam inigha Samarian ghua, Israelian atrivibar mozibar borogh…®n anefa. Ez…® Jehoas…®n otarim Jeroboam…®n igharazim an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto.
\s1 Elisa areme
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 13:14 \xt 2 Atriviba 2:12\x*Ez…® Jehoas atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, Elisa ar…®mariar bar ekiam ini. A bar aremeghasava ami, ez…® Atrivim Jehoas ghua an gari. Jehoas an apangkuvigha azia a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúNan afeziam! Nan afeziam! N…® Israelian akurvazir gumazir bar gavgavim, mati m…®dorozir hoziaba ko m…®dorozir karisba.‚Äù
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® Elisa kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® barir pim inigh iz…®.‚Äù Ez…® Jehoas ghua a inigha izi.
\p 
\v 16 Egha Elisa a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® barir pim inigh a gekuigh as…®s…®v…®ra gan.‚Äù Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n amiz…®, Elisa uan dafarim isa atrivim…®n dafarim gis…®n at…®.
\p 
\v 17 Egha g…®n Elisa kamagh…®n atrivim m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® dat…®r…®gh…®n mang…® d…®penir winduan aruem anadi nagh…®n itim kuigh.‚Äù Ez…® Jehoas uan barir pim ategha ghua windua kui.
\p Ez…® Elisa ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® barir pim gekuigh barim gas…®vamadagh.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Jehoas kamagh…®n amiz…®, Elisa diagha ghaze, ‚ÄúBarir kam, kar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n barim, a Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba ab…®ragham. Eght…® n…® Afegh…®n nguibam…®n Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba ko m…®sogh bar me ag…®vagham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 18 Egha Elisa ua kamagh…®n atrivim m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® bariba inigh.‚Äù
\p Ez…® atrivim da inigha g…®vaz…®, Elisa ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® barir kaba is…® nguazim gap…®sigh.‚Äù Ez…® Jehoas bariba isa 3plan dughiabar nguazim gap…®si.
\p 
\v 19 Ez…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Elisa an ganigha atara kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® 5pla o 6plan dughiabar nguazim gap…®zighan aghua? N…® kamagh…®n amigha ti, Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba ag…®vaghai. Egh n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n 3plan dughiabara, me ab…®ragham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 20 Ez…® g…®n Elisa aremez…®, me an kuam inigha dag…®ar mozir me ingarizim…®n anefa. Azeniba zurara, Moapian gumazir okoruar maba iza paza Israelia gami.
\p 
\v 21 Dughiar mam…®n Israelian gumaziba iza gumazir mam…®n kuam afasa. Egha me garima, Moapian marazi izima, me zuam…®ra gumazir kam…®n kuam isa Elisan mozir an aghariba iti nagh…®n anekunighava are. Ez…® gumazir kam…®n kuam mozim…®n ghuaghira Elisan agharibagh is…®n ir…®, ez…® zuam…®ra, an angam…®ra itir ik…®r…®m…®rim ua iza an kuam…®n anaboz…® a ua d…®kafi.
\s1 Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba ua Israelia m…®sosi
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® azeniba bar Jehoas…®n afeziam, Joahas Israelian atrivim…®n itima, Sirian Atrivim Hasael, Israelia m…®sogha os…®mt…®zim me gan…®ngi.
\v 23 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelian apangkuvigha bar me gifonge. A fom…®ra Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir Abraham ko Aisak ko Jekop ko amizir kam gin…®r…®gha, a Israelian akuragha me gas…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®. Egha a Israelia batueght…®, me an damazim…®n saghon mangan an aghua.
\p 
\v 24 Ez…® g…®n Atrivim Hasael aremez…®, an otarim Benhadat an danganim inigha Sirian atrivim…®n oto.
\v 25 \x - \xo 13:25 \xt 2 Atriviba 13:18\x*Ez…® Israelian Atrivim Jehoas, uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, Atrivim Benhadat…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba ko me uariv sosi. Egha Jehoas, a Benhadat ab…®ragha, Jehoas…®n afeziam, Joahas…®n dughiam…®n, nguibar Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba Israelia da inizir kaba, a uam ada ini. Jehoas 3plan dughiabar Benhadat ab…®ra.
\c 14
\s1 Amasia Judan atrivim…®n oto
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 25:1-24)
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Joahas…®n otarim, Jehoas azenir pumuning…®n Israelian atrivim…®n itima, Joas…®n otarim Amasia Judan atrivim…®n oto.
\v 2 A 25plan azeniba ikia, egha atrivim…®n otogha, 29plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n atrivim iti. An amebam, Jehoadin, a Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n amizir mam.
\v 3 Amasian afeziam Joas fom…®ra amiz…® mogh…®n, an arazir aghuibara Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh ami. Egha a uaghan uan ovavim Atrivim Devit amizir arazir aghuibar g…®n zuir puvat…®.
\v 4 Guizbang…®ra, Amasia m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itir asebar ziaba fer danganir kabagh as…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®. Ez…® gumazamiziba danganir kabar ghua aseba bagha ofabagh amua, egha pauran mughuriar aghuim zuiba tue.
\p 
\v 5 Amasia Judan kantri gativagha gavgavigha an garir dughiam…®n, a m…®kemez…®ma, me ghua, an ingangarir gumazir dapanir an afeziam Atrivim Joas m…®soghezir kamning…®n, m…®soghez…® aning areme.
\v 6 \x - \xo 14:6 \xt God…®n Araziba 24:16\x*Ez…® a ingangarir gumazir kamning…®n boribav soghez…®, me ariaghirezir puvat…®. A me ataghiz…®, me iti. An Ak…®nafarim…®n itir Moses Osirizir Araziba itir akabar g…®n zui. Ak…®nafarir kam…®n aven Ikiav…®ra Itir God Akar Gavgavim e gan…®ga ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazitam…®n borim arazir kuratam damight…®, ia an arazir kuram ikarvaghs…®, an amebam ko afeziam m…®sueght…®, aning aremeghan kogham. Eght…® kamagh…®ra, amebam ko afeziam arazir kuratam damight…®, ia aning…®n arazir kuram ikarvaghs…®, aning…®n boribav sueght…®, me aremeghan kogham. Gumazim arazir kuram damight…®, ia anar…®ra m…®sueght…®, an aremegh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 7 Dughiar mam…®n, Amasia uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko me ghua Idomian m…®dorozir gumazir 10,000pla, Danganir Zarir Amangs…®zir Av…®rim Itim…®n me ko m…®sosi. Egha me Idomia ab…®ragha, Selan nguibar ekiam ini. Egha Amasia nguibar ekiar kam, ziam Joktel a gat…®. Ez…® me dughiar kam…®n ikegha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, ziar igiar kam a gar…®si.
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® g…®n Amasia, Israelian Atrivim Jehoas bagha gumaziba amangi. Atrivim Jehoas, a Joahas…®n otarim, egha Jehun igiavotarim. Gumazir kaba ghua Jehoas batogha, kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúIsraelia, Atrivim Amasia ia m…®soghasa m…®gei. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia iz…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® Jehoas, Judan Atrivim Amasian akam ikaragha kamagh…®n akar is…®n zuim…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúLebanon…®n kantrin aven, d…®koniba itir ikar…®zir mam, temer sidan mam bagha akam amaga kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® uan guivim, nan otarim bagh anemangasa k…® ifonge. Eght…® aning uaning…®n ikiam.‚Äô D…®koniba itir ikar…®zir kam, akar kam m…®kemez…®, g…®n as…®zir atiar mam danganir kam garua, ikar…®zir kam d…®kab…®niz…®, a ikufi.‚Äù
\p 
\v 10 Jehoas akar is…®n zuir kam gamua, ua kamagh…®n Amasia m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® fo, bar guizbang…®ra, n…® Idomia m…®sogha bar me ab…®ra. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® bar akuegha uan ziam bar a fe. N…® m…®dorozir kam…®n ziar ekiam ini. Egh n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n bar akuegh, deraghv…®ra uan nguibam…®n ik…®. Egh n…® ua e m…®soghs…® m…®dorozim foran mark…®. Puvat…®ght…®ma, n…® ko Judan gumazamiziba bar, ia pazav…®ra iregh bar ikuvigham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® Amasia Jehoas…®n akam baraghan aghua. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Israelian Atrivim Jehoas Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, me nguibar ekiar Judan kantrin itim Betsemes…®n ghugha, Judabar Atrivim Amasia ko an m…®dorozir gumaziba, ko m…®sosi.
\v 12 Me uariv sogha ghuav…®ra itima, Israelia Judan m…®dorozir gumaziba d…®kab…®raz…®, Judan m…®dorozir gumaziba ara ua uan nguibabar ghue.
\v 13 Ez…® Israelian Atrivim Jehoas, Betsemes…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ikia, Judabar Atrivim Amasian suiragha a isa kalabus gat…®. Atrivim Joas…®n otarim Amasia, a Atrivim Ahasian igiavotarim. Ez…® g…®n, Atrivim Jehoas Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, Betsemes…®n nguibar ekiam ategha Jerusalem…®n ghue. Egha me Jerusalem av…®nizir d…®vazir gavgavim gas…®ghas…®ki, me Efraim…®n Tiar Akam…®n ikegha ghua, Tiar Akar M…®kebam…®n itim…®n tu. D…®vazir kuvizir kam…®n ababanim, a 200 mitan m…®n ghu.
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® Jehoas Jerusalem…®n aven ghua, nguibar ekiam…®n itir golba ko silvaba bar ada ini. A uaghan itarir ekiaba ko itarir igharazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n itiba, ko atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n mongezir dag…®aba bar ada ini. Egha uaghan Judan gumazir ekiar maba isa kalabus gat…®gha kamagh…®n Amasia m…®gei, ‚ÄúAmasia, n…® uam Israelia e m…®soghs…® n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®. N…® kamagh…®n damight…®, k…® n…®n gumazir ekiabav sueght…®, me ar…®ghiregham.‚Äù An akar kam m…®kemegha g…®vagha, gumazir ekiar kaba ko gumazamizir maba ko bizir kaba sara inigha ua Samarian ghu.
\s1 Atrivim Jehoas areme
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® bizir igharazibar eghaghanir Atrivim Jehoas amiziba, da ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghaniba. Ak…®nafarir kam, Israelian Atrivim Jehoas, Judan Atrivim Amasian adarazi ko m…®soghezir eghaghanim, ko an amizir bizir gavgavir igharazibagh eghari.
\v 16 Ez…® g…®n Jehoas uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremez…®, me an kuam inigha Samarian nguibar ekiam…®n ghua, Israelian atrivibar mozibar borogh…®n anefa. Ez…® an otarim, Jeroboam…®n igharazim, an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto.
\s1 Atrivim Amasia areme
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 25:25-28)
\p 
\v 17 Israelian Atrivim Jehoas aremegha g…®vaz…®, Judan Atrivim Amasia ua 15plan azenibar ikegha, areme.
\v 18 Ez…® bizir igharazibar eghaghanir Atrivim Amasia amiziba, da ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, Judabar Atrivibar Eghaghaniba.
\p 
\v 19 Atrivim Amasia Jerusalem…®n itima, gumazir maba a m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa akam ak…®ri. Ez…® an akar kam baregha, ara Lakis…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghu. Ez…® an apanir kaba gumazir maba amangiz…®, me an g…®n Lakis…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghua, a m…®soghez…®, an areme.
\v 20 Ez…® me an kuam inigha hoziabagh at…®gha ua Jerusalem…®n ize. Egha me an kuam isa Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n, an inazir afeziaba afez…® nagh…®n anefa.
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® g…®n Judan gumazamiziba bar Usia ini, an ziar igharazim Asaria. Egha me a gamiz…®, a uan afeziam Amasian danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto. Usia 16plan azeniba ikia, atrivim…®n oto.
\v 22 Egha mong g…®n, an atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, a ghua m…®sogha apanibar dafarim…®n Elat…®n nguibam uam a ini. Egha nguibar kam…®n danganir ikuviziba a ua dar k…®ri.
\s1 Jeroboam…®n igharazim, Israelian atrivim…®n oto
\p 
\v 23 Joas…®n otarim Amasia 15plan azenibar Judan atrivim…®n itima, Jehoas…®n otarim, Jeroboam Israelian atrivim…®n oto. Egha a 41plan azenibar atrivim…®n ikia, egha Samarian iti.
\v 24 Egha Nebat…®n otarim Jeroboam…®n faragha itim, an amiz…® mogh…®n a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kurabagh ami. Fom…®ra Jeroboam…®n faragha itim, Israelia gekuiz…®, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kurabagh ami. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Jeroboam…®n kam arazir kurar kabara, Jeroboam…®n faragha itim amiz…® mogh…®ra, an adagh ami.
\v 25 \x - \xo 14:25 \xt Jona 1:1\x*Jeroboam t…®ghar atrivim…®n otivamin dughiam…®n, apaniba Israelian nguazir otevir av…®riba ini. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Jeroboam m…®sogha, ua nguazir kaba ini, a tuavir ghuaghira Hamat…®n nguibar not…®n amadaghan itim…®n ikegha ghua, Amangs…®zim Itir D…®par Akarem…®n, saut…®n amadaghan itim…®n tu. Ez…® arazir kam…®n, Jeroboam Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God…®n akam gamiz…®, a guizbang…®ram oto. Akar kam, God faragha a isa Amitain otarim, Jona,\f + \fr 14:25 \ft Gumazir kamra, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim, Jona, vez…®n kam a geghari.\f* a God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim a gan…®ngiz…®, an a gun m…®keme. God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir kam Jona, a Gathefer…®n nguibam…®n gumazir mam.
\v 26 Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelian apanibar garima, me os…®mt…®zir ekiam me gar…®ghav…®ra ikia, egha me ag…®vasava ami. Ez…® gumazir vaghvaziba ikiav…®ra iti.\f + \fr 14:26 \ft N…® God…®n Araziba 32:36…®n gan.\f* Egha uaghan men akurvaghamin gumaziba puvat…®.
\v 27 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar Israelian ziam angaright…®, gumaziba ua me g…®n…®ghn…®ghan kogham, a kamagh…®n m…®kemezir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a Jehoas…®n otarim, Atrivim Jeroboam apanibar dafarim…®n ua me iniasa anem…®sefe.
\p 
\v 28 Ez…® bizir igharazibar eghaghanir Atrivim Jeroboam amiziba, da ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghaniba. Ak…®nafarir kam, an ingangarir gavgavir an amiziba ko, a Damaskus…®n nguibar ekiam ko Hamat…®n nguibar ekiam, ua da iniasa m…®soghezir m…®dorozibar eghaghanibagh eghari. Nguibar ekiam Hamat, Judaba faragha a gatifa.
\v 29 Ez…® g…®n Jeroboam uan inazir afeziar Israelian atriviba ikezibar m…®n areme. Ez…® an otarim Sekaraia an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto.
\c 15
\s1 Usia Judan atrivim…®n oto
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 26:1-23)
\p 
\v 1 Jeroboam 27plan azenibar Israelian atrivim…®n itima, Amasian otarim, Usia Judan atrivim…®n oto. Usian ziar igharazim, Asaria.
\v 2 A 16plan azeniba ikia, egha atrivim…®n oto, egha 52plan azenibar atrivim…®n ikia, egha Jerusalem…®n iti. An amebam Jekolia, Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n amizim.
\v 3 Ez…® Usian afeziam Amasia amiz…® mogh…®n, Usia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir aghuibagh ami.
\v 4 Egha Usia m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itir asebar ziaba fer danganibagh as…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazamiziba danganir kabar ghua aseba bagha ofabagh amua, egha pauran mughuriar aghuim zuiba tue.
\p 
\v 5 Dughiar mam…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God lepan ar…®mariam gamiz…®, a Usian m…®karzim bato, eght…® ar…®mariar kam g…®vaghan kogham. Ez…® an atrivir d…®penim ategha ghua d…®penir igharazim…®n iti, ez…® an otarim Jotam, an atrivir ingangarim gami, egha atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n gara, egha kantri gativagha ikia ghuav itima, Atrivim Usia areme.
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® Atrivim Usia amizir bizir igharazibar eghaghaniba, ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, Judan Atrivibar Eghaghaniba.
\v 7 \x - \xo 15:7 \xt Aisaia 6:1\x*Ez…® Atrivim Usia uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremez…®, me an kuam inigha Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n ghua an kuam isa an inazir afeziabar mozibar borogh…®n anefa. Ez…® an otarim Jotam, an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto.
\s1 Sekaraia Israelian atrivim…®n oto
\p 
\v 8 Usia 38plan azenibar Judan atrivim…®n itima, Jeroboam…®n igharazim…®n otarim, Sekaraia, Israelian atrivim…®n oto. Egha a Samarian nguibar ekiam…®n ikia, 6plan iak…®nibara atrivim…®n ike.
\v 9 Egha Sekaraian ovaviba amiz…® mogh…®n, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kurabagh ami. An arazir Nebat…®n otarim Jeroboam amizir arazir kurar kaba ataghizir puvat…®. Jeroboam fom…®ra Israelia gekuiz…®, me arazir kuraba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh ami. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Sekaraia uaghan arazir kabaram ami.
\v 10 Ez…® Jabes…®n otarim Salum, gumazir maba ko uari akuvagha, Sekaraia m…®sueght…®, an aremeghasa tuaviba buri. Egha g…®n Salum uab…®, gumazamizibar damazim…®n, Sekaraia m…®soghez…® an aremez…®, Salum uab…® atrivim…®n oto.
\v 11-12 Ez…® arazir kam…®n, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemezir akar d…®k…®r…®zim gamiz…®, a guizbang…®ram oto.\f + \fr 15:11-12 \ft N…® 2 Atriviba 10:30…®n gan.\f* Fom…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Atrivim Jehu m…®keme, ‚ÄúK…® g…®n n…®n adarazir gumaziba ateght…®, me atrivibar otivam. N…®n ikegh mang…® n…®n otarim ko an otarim, ko an igiavotarim ko an az…®zim…®n tugham.‚Äù Ez…® Sekaraia amizir bizir igharazibar eghaghaniba, da ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghaniba.
\s1 Salum Israelian atrivim…®n oto
\p 
\v 13 Usia 39plan azenibar Judan atrivim…®n iti, ez…® Jabes…®n otarim Salum, Israelian atrivim…®n oto. Egha Samarian ikia, iak…®nir vam…®ran atrivim…®n ike.
\v 14 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, Gadin otarim Menahem, Tirsan nguibam ategha Samarian ghugha, Salum m…®soghez…® an areme, ez…® a uab…® atrivim…®n oto.
\v 15 Ez…® Salum amizir bizir igharazibar eghaghaniba, da ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghaniba. Ak…®nafarir kam uaghan Salum ko gumazir igharaziba me Atrivim Sekaraia m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa amizir arazibagh eghari.
\p 
\v 16 Dughiar Menahem uan gumaziba ko, me Tirsa ategha Samaria bagha zuim…®n, me Tipsan nguibar ekiam…®n otifi. Ez…® Tipsan gumaziba uan nguibam…®n aven mangasa Menahem…®n gumazibar amamangat…®zir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Menahem m…®dorozim foregha me uariv sogha, Menahem uan adarazi ko me bar pazav…®ra, Tipsan nguibar ekiam gas…®ghas…®ki. Egha me Tipsan nguibam…®n gumazamiziba ko nguibar dozir an borogh…®n itibar gumazamizibav m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Egha me amizir naviba adaiba inigha men navibagh iniva da of…®rima, me ariaghiri.
\s1 Menahem Israelian atrivim…®n oto
\p 
\v 17 Usia 39plan azenibar Judan atrivim…®n itima, Gadin otarim Menahem Israelian atrivim…®n oto. Egha a Samarian nguibar ekiam…®n ikia 10plan azenibar atrivim…®n iti.
\v 18 Egha an arazir kuraba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh ami, mati Nebat…®n otarim Jeroboam, amiz…® mok…®n. Jeroboam fom…®ra Israelia gekuiz…®, me arazir kuraba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh ami. Ez…® Menahem dat…®r…®gh…®n arazir kaba atagh…®razir puvat…®, an adagh amuav…®ra ikia ghuav areme.
\v 19 Menahem atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, Tiklat Pileser, Asirian atrivim…®n ikia, egha iza Israelia ko m…®sosi. Ez…® Tiklat Pileser…®n ziar igharazim, Pul. Ez…® Menahem 3,000,000 kina silva inigha, Tiklat Pileser givezasa a gan…®ngi, eght…® a ua m…®soghan kogh…®va, egh Menahem…®n akuraght…®, a Israelian kantrin atrivir gavgavim…®n ikiam.
\v 20 Menahem manmagh…®n dag…®ar kaba ini, a gumazir dag…®ar av…®riba itiba vaghvagha me gaghorima, me 50 silvan dag…®aba a gan…®ngiz…®, ana da isa Atrivim Tiklat Pileser gan…®ngi. Ez…® Tiklat Pileser Israelian kantri ategha ghu.
\p 
\v 21 Menahem amizir bizir igharazibar eghaghaniba bar, da ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghaniba.
\v 22 Ez…® Menahem uan inazir afeziabar m…®n areme. Ez…® an otarim Pekahia, an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto.
\s1 Pekahia Israelian atrivim…®n oto
\p 
\v 23 Usia 50plan azenibar Judan atrivim…®n iti, ez…® Menahem…®n otarim Pekahia, Israelian atrivim…®n oto. Egha Samarian nguibam…®n ikia azenir pumuningra atrivim…®n ike.
\v 24 An arazir kuraba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh ami. Fom…®ra Nebat…®n otarim Jeroboam Israelia gekuiz…®, me arazir kuraba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh ami. Ez…® Pekahia dat…®r…®gh…®n arazir kurar kabaram amua da ataghizir puvat…®.
\v 25 Ez…® Pekahian m…®dorozir gumazibar garir gumazir mam, an ziam Peka, a Remalian otarim. A Gileat…®n Distrigh…®n 50plan gumaziba ko, Pekahia m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa akam ak…®ri. Dughiar kam…®n, Pekahia Samarian ikia uan atrivir d…®penim…®n aven itir danganir gavgavim itima, gumazir kaba danganir kam…®n aven ghua, a m…®soghez…®, an areme. Egha me uaghan Argop ko Arie m…®soghez…®, aning areme. Ez…® Peka, Atrivim Pekahian danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto.
\p 
\v 26 Ez…® Pekahia amizir bizir igharazibar eghaghaniba, ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghaniba.
\s1 Peka Israelian atrivim…®n oto
\p 
\v 27 Atrivim Usia 52plan azenibar Judan atrivim…®n iti, ez…® Remalian otarim Peka, Israelian atrivim…®n oto. Egha a Samarian nguibar ekiam…®n ikia, 20plan azenibar atrivim…®n iti.
\v 28 Egha an arazir kuraba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh ami. Nebat…®n otarim Jeroboam fom…®ra Israelia gekuiz…®, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kurabagh ami. Ez…® Peka uaghan arazir kabaram amua da ataghizir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 29 Peka Israelian atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, Asirian Atrivim, Tiklat Pileser iza, Israelia m…®sogha, Ijon…®n nguibar ekiam, ko Abel Betmakan nguibar ekiam, Janoan nguibar ekiam, Kedes…®n nguibar ekiam, Hasor…®n nguibar ekiam, Gileat…®n Distrik, Galilin Distrik, ko Naptalin anabam…®n nguaziba bar ada ini. Egha a danganir kabar gumazamiziba inigha, Asirian kantrin ghua me isa kalabuziabar m…®n ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar me ar…®ki.\f + \fr 15:29 \ft N…® ak…®nafarir kam…®n ak…®rang…®n itir Akar M…®ngaribar gan. A Israelian kalabus…®n itir dughiam m…®gei.\f*
\p 
\v 30 Ez…® Usian otarim Jotam, a 20plan azenibar Judan atrivim…®n itima, Elan otarim, Hosia gumazir maba ko, Atrivim Peka m…®sueght…®, an aremeghasa tuavir mam bato. Egha g…®n Hosia, Peka m…®soghez…®, an aremez…®, Hosia uab…® an danganim inigha Israelian atrivim…®n oto.
\v 31 Ez…® Atrivim Peka amizir bizir igharazibar eghaghaniba bar, da ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghaniba.
\s1 Jotam Judan atrivim…®n oto
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 27:1-9)
\p 
\v 32 Ez…® Remalian otarim Peka azenir pumuning…®n Israelian atrivim…®n itima, Usian otarim Jotam, a Judan atrivim…®n oto.
\v 33 A 25plan azeniba ikia, atrivim…®n otogha Jerusalem…®n ikia, 16plan azenibar atrivim…®n iti. An amebam Jerusa, a Sadok…®n guivim.
\v 34 Ez…® Jotam…®n afeziam Usia amiz…® mogh…®n, an arazir aghuiba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh ami.
\v 35 Egha Jotam m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itir asebar ziaba fer danganibagh as…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazamiziba danganir kabar ghuav…®ra ikia, aseba bagha ofabagh amua, pauran mughuriar aghuim zuiba tue. Ez…® Jotam m…®kemez…®, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim av…®nizir D…®vazim…®n Tiar Akar P…®n Itim…®n ingari.
\p 
\v 36 Ez…® bizir igharazir Jotam amizibar eghaghaniba, da ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, Judabar Atrivibar Eghaghaniba.
\v 37 Ez…® Jotam atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Sirian Atrivim Resin ko Israelian Atrivim Peka, aning…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba amangiz…®, me dughiar faragha zuim…®n, Judaba konasa ghue.
\v 38 Ez…® Jotam uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremez…®, me an kuam inigha Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n ghua, an inazir afeziabar mozibar borogh…®n anefa. Ez…® an otarim Ahas, an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto.
\c 16
\s1 Ahas Judan atrivim…®n oto
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 28:1-27)
\p 
\v 1 Remalian otarim Peka 17plan azenibar Israelian atrivim…®n itima, Jotam…®n otarim, Ahas Judan atrivim…®n oto.
\v 2 Egha Ahas 20plan azeniba ikia, atrivim…®n otogha, 16plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n iti. An ovavim Devit arazir aghuibagh ami, ez…® Ahas Ikiav…®ra Itir God, an God, an an damazim…®n arazir aghuibagh amir puvat…®.
\v 3 \x - \xo 16:3 \xt God…®n Araziba 12:31\x*Puvat…®. A Israelian atriviba amiz…® mogh…®n, puram arazir kuram gami. Egha uaghan a bar arazir igharazim gami. A uan otarim m…®suegha, aseba bagha ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim…®n m…®n a tua. Egha a fom…®ra nguazir kam…®n ikezir gumazamizibar arazir kurabar g…®n zui. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar men arazibar aghuagha me batuegha, nguazir kam isa Israelia gan…®ngi.
\v 4 Ez…® Ahas m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itir asebar ziaba fer danganibar zui. Danganir kaba, da uaghan m…®ghs…®ar dozibagh is…®n ikia, temer ekiabar apengan iti. Egha an aseba bagha ofabagh amua, pauran mughuriar aghuim zuiba tue.
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 16:5 \xt Aisaia 7:1\x*Dughiar kam…®n, Sirian Atrivim Resin, ko Israelian Atrivim Peka, a Remalian otarim, aning uan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha, Jerusalem konasa ghu. Egha me Jerusalemia ko m…®sosi, me Atrivim Ahas ko an m…®dorozir gumaziba d…®kab…®nasa amuava avenge.
\v 6 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, Sirian Atrivim Resin, ua Elat…®n nguibam iniasa m…®sosi. Egha a ua Elat…®n nguibam inigha, Judan Elat…®n aven itiba batoke. Egha a Idomia ataghiz…®, me ghua Elat…®n nguibam…®n iti. Egha an ikia iza dat…®r…®k…®n.\f + \fr 16:6 \ft M…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevir kam, ‚Äúdat…®r…®k…®n,‚Äù a dat…®r…®gh…®n e itir dughiar kam m…®geir puvat…®. A gumazir ak…®nafarir kam osirizim…®n dughiam m…®gei.\f*
\v 7 Ez…® Atrivim Ahas gumazir maba amangiz…®, me Asirian Atrivim Tiklat Pileser bagha ghua kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® Atrivim Ahas, k…® n…®n ingangarir gumazim, egha k…® n…®n borim…®n m…®n iti. Dat…®r…®gh…®n Sirian atrivim ko Israelian atrivim na ko m…®sosi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® iz…® me m…®soght…®, me e gas…®ghasighan kogham.‚Äù
\v 8 Egha Ahas Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n itir gol ko silvan dag…®aba, ko atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n itir dag…®aba sara inigha Asirian atrivim givezeght…®, a Judabar akurvaghasa da amada.
\v 9 Ez…® Atrivim Tiklat Pileser, Ahas…®n akam baregha, uan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha ghua, Damaskus…®n nguibar ekiam…®n m…®sogha a ini. Egha Tiklat Pileser, Atrivim Resin…®n m…®soghez…®, an areme. Egha Damaskus…®n gumazamiziba, kalabuziar gumazamizibar m…®n me inigha, Kir…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghu.
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® g…®n Atrivim Ahas, Asirian Atrivim Tiklat Pileser…®n ganasa Damaskus…®n ghu. A danganir kam…®n itir dughiam…®n, a Damaskus…®n itir asebar ziaba famin ofa gamir dakozim…®n gani. Egha an nedazim…®n ingarigha, ofa gamir dakozir kam…®n ingarir araziba osiri. Egha Jerusalem…®n God…®n ofa gamir gumazim Uria bagha anemada, egha a m…®kemez…®, a kamagh…®ra ofa gamir dakozir mam…®n ingari.
\v 11 Ez…® Uria akam baregha, kamagh…®ra garir ofa gamir dakozir Damaskus…®n itim…®n ingari. Ahas t…®ghar ua Jerusalem…®n izamin dughiam…®n, Uria ofa gamir dakozir kam gamigha g…®fa.
\v 12 Ahas ua izezir dughiam…®n, a ghua ofa gamir dakozim…®n gari. Egha ofa damuasa ofa gamir dakozir ekiar kam…®n borogh…®n ghua ad…®r…®ziam…®n ghuavanabo.
\v 13 Egha an ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim, ko wit tuer ofa, ko wain inger ofabagh ami. Egha as…®zir ghuzim inigha, God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofa bagha, ghuzim isa ofa gamir dakozim…®n a kavamadi.
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 16:14 \xt Ua Me Ini 27:1-2; 2 Eghaghaniba 4:1\x*Bar fom…®ra iza dughiar kam…®n, ofa gamir dakozir me fom…®ra bras…®n ingarizim, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n ikia an D…®penim…®n guam…®n tughav iti. Ez…® Atrivim Ahas dat…®r…®gh…®n ofa gamir dakozir kam, an danganim…®n a inigha, a gis…®vagha not…®n amadaghan ofa gamir dakozir igiar kam…®n m…®riam…®n anesara. God…®n ofa gamir dakozir kam, faragha ofa gamir dakozir igiar kam ko Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n tiar akam…®n, t…®zim…®n tughav ti.
\v 15 Ez…® Atrivim Ahas kamagh…®n Uria m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® zurara ofa damuamin dughiaba, n…® ofa gamir dakozir igiar kamra mang…®. N…® m…®zarazibar ofan bar isia m…®gh…®ribar amuva, guarat…®zibar wit tuer ofabar amu. Egh n…® atrivim bagh ofa damuva, egh uaghan gumazamiziba bar me bagh ofa bar amu. Kar ofan bar isia m…®gh…®riba ko wit tuer ofaba. Egh n…® gumazamiziba bagh ofan igharazibar amu, kar wain inger ofaba. Egh n…® as…®zibar ghuziba bar ada inigh ofa damu, egh da kavamang…®t…®, da ofa gamir dakozir igiar kamra ir…®. Ez…® bras…®n ingarizir ofa gamir dakozim, kar nan bizimra. K…® an ofabar amu egh God…®n azangs…®ght…®, a na m…®k…®mt…® bizir k…® damuasa n…®ghn…®ziba k…® dar amuam.‚Äù
\v 16 Ez…® Uria atrivim…®n akar kaba baregha zurara dar g…®n ghua, egha kamagh…®n ami.
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 16:17 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 4:2-6\x*Ez…® g…®n Atrivim Ahas ingangarir gumazibav kemez…®, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aven ghugha, Solomon…®n ingangarir gumaziba fom…®ra wilkar…®n bras…®n amizibar aghariba akaraghar…®ki. Egha uaghan itarir ekiar wilkar gis…®n itiba ini. Egha me bulmakaun bras…®n teng…®n d…®par ekiam…®n apengan itiba ini. Me g…®n dag…®aba inigha teng…®n ekiar kam afasa dakozir igiam…®n ingari.\f + \fr 16:17 \ft Hibrun akam deragha akar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f*
\v 18 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n borogh…®ra, bizir mam mati d…®penir dozir mam…®n m…®n iti, me Sabat…®n dughiam…®n uari bagha aruem…®n fefem avasa an ingari. Egha me dat…®r…®gh…®n a g…®raz…®, gumaziba an guam…®n ganan kogham. Ez…® me, tiar akar atrivim God…®n D…®penim…®n aven zuim, me uaghan an itir kurkazir aghuim g…®raz…®, gumaziba ua kurkazir kam…®n ganan kogham. Atrivim Ahas Asirian atrivim…®n ifongiam…®n g…®n ghua, arazir kabagh ami.\f + \fr 16:18 \ft Ahas uan ingangarir kabar amuasa, bras…®n kaba ini. Solomon fom…®ra God…®n D…®penim bagha bizir kabar ingari. N…® 1 Atriviba 7:23-39…®n gan.\f*
\p 
\v 19 Ez…® Atrivim Ahas amizir bizir igharazibar eghaghaniba bar, da ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, Judabar Atrivibar Eghaghaniba.
\v 20 \x - \xo 16:20 \xt Aisaia 14:28\x*Ez…® Ahas uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremez…®, me an kuam inigha Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n ghua, a isa an inazir afeziabar mozibar borogh…®n anefa. Ez…® an otarim Hesekia an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto.
\c 17
\s1 Hosia Israelian atrivim…®n oto
\p 
\v 1 Atrivim Ahas Judan atrivim…®n itima, an namba 12…®n azenim…®n aven, Elan otarim Hosia, a Israelian atrivim…®n oto. Egha 9plan azenibar atrivim…®n ikia Samarian nguibar ekiam…®n iti.
\v 2 An arazir kuraba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh ami. Egha a Israelian atrivir igharazir an faragha zuiba amiz…® mogh…®n, an arazir kurar bar av…®ribagh amizir puvat…®.
\v 3 An atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, Asirian Atrivim Salmaneser iza Israelia ko m…®sosi. Egha Asirian m…®dorozir gumaziba Israelia ab…®ra, ez…® Hosia Salmaneser…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zim…®n a gamua ghaze, an an apengan ik…®va, egh zurara azenibar a takis…®n m…®n dag…®aba a dan…®ngam.
\v 4 Egha azenir mam…®n, Hosia gumazir maba amangiz…®, me Isip…®n Atrivim So bagha ghuegha an azai, eght…® a Hosian akuragham. Egha uaghan azenir kam…®n, Hosia azenibar zurara ami mogh…®n, a Salmaneser bagha takis…®n m…®n dag…®aba amadir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Salmaneser kamagh…®n fo, Hosia a gifaragha uan akar d…®k…®r…®zim ab…®ki. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a uan m…®dorozir gumaziba amangiz…® me ghua, Hosian suiragha kalabus gat…®.
\s1 Asiriaba Samariabav sogha me ab…®ni
\p 
\v 5 Dughiar Asirian Atrivim Salmaneser, Hosia kalabus gat…®zim…®n g…®n, Salmaneser uan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha ghua Israelian nguazim…®n aven arua bar me m…®sosi. Me ghua Samarian nguibar ekiam…®n otivigha, me korogha, 3plan azenibar me ko m…®sosi.
\v 6 Ez…® namba 9…®n azenim…®n Hosia Israelian atrivim…®n itima, Asirian atrivim Samariaba d…®kab…®ragha, men nguibar ekiam ini. Egha a Israelia inigha Asirian kantrin ghu. Egha marazi isa Halan nguibar ekiam gat…®, egha marazi isa Gosan…®n Distrigh…®n aven itir, Habor…®n Fanem…®n borogh…®ra me ar…®ki. Ez…® marazi Midian kantrin nguibabar iti.
\p 
\v 7 Os…®mt…®zir Israelia bativir kaba, dar m…®ngarim kamak…®n. Me Ikiav…®ra Itir God, men God…®n damazim…®n arazir kuram gami. Ikiav…®ra Itir God fom…®ra men inazir afeziaba Isip…®n atrivim…®n dafarim…®n ua me ini. Ez…® me bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®zir pu. Bar puvat…®. Israelia asebar ziaba fe,
\v 8 egha me uan atirivibar arazir kurar me faragha amizibar g…®n zui. Egha me ik…®zir igharazir fom…®ra nguazir kam…®n ikezibar, arazir kurabar g…®n zui. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ik…®zir kaba batuegha, nguazir kam isa Israelia gan…®ngi.
\v 9 Ez…® Israelia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, men God ak…®rim ragha a gasaragha moga, arazir kurar bar av…®ribagh ami. Kar, arazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n derazir puvat…®ziba. Me m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itir asebar ziaba famin danganiba, uan nguibar ekiaba ko nguibar doziba bar, dar borogh…®n, dar ingari.
\v 10 \x - \xo 17:10 \xt 1 Atriviba 14:23\x*Egha me m…®ghs…®abar oraziba ko temer ekiabar apebabar dughuazibar ghua, uari bagha dag…®ar guarir d…®ghoriba itiba ko temer guarir aser amizim Aseran nedazim itiba saram asava, egha dar ziaba fe.
\v 11 Egha me danganir kabar ikia, asebar ziaba fer arazir ik…®zir igharaziba fom…®ram amizibagh ami, ik…®zir kaba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God fom…®ra nguazir kam…®n me batoke. Me pauran mughuriar aghuim zuiba tua, aseba bagha ofa gami. Ez…® Israelian arazir kurar kaba Ikiav…®ra Itir God gamima, an an…®ngaghe.
\v 12 Fom…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n me m…®keme, ‚ÄúIa asebar marvir guabar ziaba fan mark…®.‚Äù Ez…® me an akam baraghan aghuagha marvir guar kabar ziaba fe.
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan akam inigha izir gumaziba amangiz…®, me vaghvagha Israel ko Judan ghuegha, kamagh…®n Akar Gavgavim me gan…®ga ghaze, ‚ÄúIa n…®ghn…®zibagh iragh, egh ia uan arazir kuraba ategh nan Akar Gavgaviba, ko arazir k…® ifongezibar g…®n mang…®. Arazir kaba, k…® ian inazir afeziabagh an…®ngi. K…® akar kaba isa, uan ingangarir gumazibar akabagh at…®z…®, me ia m…®keme, kar nan akam inigha izir gumaziba.‚Äù
\v 14 Ez…® Israelian dapaniba gavgavigha God…®n akam barazir puvat…®, egha an akam batuegha uan inazir afeziabar arazibar g…®n zui. Inazir afeziar kaba, me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ikian aghua, a men God.
\v 15 Israelia ak…®rim ragha arazir God ifongezibagh asava, Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir a men inazir afeziaba ko amizim, ko an ikiangs…®zir a me gan…®ngiziba, me bar dar aghua. Me akaba batogha, egha ghua asebar ziaba fe. Aser kaba guizbang…®n godba puvat…®. Ez…® Israelian gumazamiziba bizir ifavarir k…®nir kabar ziaba fe, me uari pura bizir ifavarir k…®nibar m…®n otifi. Fom…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God me m…®keme, me men borogh…®ra itir ik…®zibar arazibar g…®n mangan mark…®, ez…® Israelia an akam batuegha, arazir kabar g…®n zui.
\v 16 \x - \xo 17:16 \xt 1 Atriviba 12:28\x*Egha me Ikiav…®ra Itir God, men God…®n Akar Gavgaviba bar da batuegha da ab…®ki. Egha me gol inigha bulmakaun apurir pumuning…®n marvir guamning…®n ingarigha, aning…®n ziamning fe. Egha me aser amizim Aseran marvir guam…®n ingarigha an ziam fe. Egha uaghan, overiam…®n itir m…®koveziba bar dar ziaba fava, egha asem Bal…®n ziam fe.
\v 17 \x - \xo 17:17 \xt God…®n Araziba 18:10\x*Egha me uan otariba ko guivibav sogha, avim…®n aven me tua aser kabar ofa gami. Egha me ganganir gumaziba ko gumazamizir aremezibar duaba ko m…®geiba bagha ghua, egha uarir akurvaghasa men azai. Egha me imezibagh amir arazibagh ami. Israelia ti n…®ghn…®zir vam…®ra iti, a kamak…®n, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kuram damuv…®ra ikiasava ami. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God men arazir kurar kam…®n ganigha puv…®ra men atari.
\v 18 Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar Israelian an…®ngaghegha, men guabar ganan aghua. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a men nguazim…®n me batoghez…®, me ghua saghon itir kantrin ghu. Ez…® Judan anabam…®n gumazamiziba uan nguazim…®n ikiav…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 19 Egha Judaba, me uaghan Ikiav…®ra Itir God, men God, an Akar Gavgavibar g…®n zuir puvat…®. Israelia g…®n ghuezir arazir kurar kabara, Judan gumazamiziba uaghan dar g…®n zui.
\v 20 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ak…®rim ragha bar Israelia gasara. Egha a puv me gamua, egha apaniba amangiz…® me iza me gas…®ghas…®ki. Israelia arazir kuraba ataghizir puvat…®, ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God men aghuagha, me batoghez…® me an damazim…®n saghon ghue.
\p 
\v 21 Fom…®ra Israelia ko Judaba uari inigha Atrivim Devit…®n adarazir apengan iti. Egha g…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelia gamiz…®, me Judan adarazi ko uari ab…®ki. Egha Israelian adarazi d…®kavigha Nebat…®n otarim Jeroboam am…®sevez…®, a men atrivim…®n oto. Egha Jeroboam me gamima, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God ategha, arazir kurar av…®rir bar ekiabagh ami.
\v 22 Egha g…®n Israelia uaghan, Jeroboam amiz…® mogh…®n, arazir kurar bar igharazibagh ami. Me arazir kaba ataghizir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®.
\v 23 Ez…® g…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar men aghua, egha me batoghez…® me uan kantrin saghon ghue. Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n arazir kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n, God dughiar av…®riba ikiangs…®zir akaba isa Israelia bagha uan akam inigha izir gumazibagh an…®ngi. Kar an ingangarir gumaziba, ez…® me arua Israelia m…®g…®av…®ra iti, ez…® me me baraghan aghua. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Asiriaba iza Israelia m…®sogha me ab…®ragha, me inigha uan kantrin ghue, ez…® me kantrin kam…®n ikiav…®ra iti.\f + \fr 17:23 \ft M…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevir kam, ‚Äúikiav…®ra iti,‚Äù a e dat…®r…®gh…®n itir dughiam m…®geir puvat…®. A gumazir ak…®nafarir kam osirizim…®n dughiam m…®gei.\f*
\s1 Ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamiziba Israel…®n nguazim gapia
\p 
\v 24 Asirian atrivim ghua, Babilon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazamiziba, ko Kutan nguibar ekiam, Ivan nguibar ekiam, ko Hamat…®n nguibar ekiam, ko Sefarvaim…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazamiziba, a bar me inigha Samarian nguibar ekiabar ghuegha, Israelian nguibar ekiabar me ar…®ki. Ez…® gumazamizir kaba bar Israelian nguazim gapia.
\p 
\v 25 Egha me iza kagh apiagha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fer puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God laionba amangiz…®, da iza men maraziv suaghar…®ki.
\p 
\v 26 Ez…® gumazir maba ghua kamagh…®n Asirian atrivim m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazamizir n…® inigha ghua Samarian nguibabagh ar…®ghiziba, me nguazir kam…®n asebar arazibagh fozir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, aser kam laionba amangiz…® da iza gumazamizibav sozi me ariaghiri.‚Äù
\p 
\v 27 Atrivim akar kam baregha uan gumazir dapanir mam m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® Israelian ofa gamir gumazir e inigha kagh izezir kabar tam inigh iz…®. Egh uam anemadaght…®, a Samarian kantrin mang…® ik…®, egh nguazir kam…®n asebar arazibar gumazamizibar sure damu.‚Äù
\v 28 Ez…® me Israelian ofa gamir gumazir mam inigha, ua Samarian anemada, ez…® a ghua Betel…®n nguibam…®n ikiava, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fer arazibar gumazamizir kabar sure gami.
\p 
\v 29 Ez…® ik…®zir kabar gumazamiziba me uan arazibar g…®n ghuav…®ra ikia, egha uari bagha asebar marvir guabar ingari. Egha me marvir guar kaba isa, Israelia fom…®ra asebar ziaba fasa m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itir danganir ingarizir kabagh ar…®ki. Egha ik…®zir vaghvaziba uari bagha marvir guabar ingara da isa nguibar me itibagh ar…®si.
\v 30 Babilon…®n ikegha izezir gumazamiziba, uari bagha asem Sukotbenot…®n marvir guam…®n ingari, ez…® Kutan gumazamiziba, asem Nergal…®n marvir guam…®n ingari, ez…® Hamatia uari bagha asem Asiman, marvir guam…®n ingari,
\v 31 ez…® Ivan gumazamiziba asem Niphas…®n marvir guam ko asem Tartak…®n marvir guam…®n ingari. Ez…® Sefarvaimia me uan boribav sogha da tua, ofan m…®n asemning Adramelek ko Anamelek gan…®di.
\v 32 Egha gumazamizir kaba uaghan Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fe. Me uari uan adarazir gumazir maba m…®sevima, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa gamir gumazibar otifi. God…®n ofa gamir gumazir kaba me asebar ziam fer danganir m…®ghs…®abar itibar ikia, egha gumazamizir as…®zir me ofa bagha isa izibar ofa gami.
\v 33 Egha arazir kam…®n me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fa, egha uaghan me uan nguibam…®n amir arazim…®n g…®n ghua uan asebar ziaba fe.
\p 
\v 34 \x - \xo 17:34 \xt Jenesis 32:28; 35:10\x*Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n uaghan gumazamizir kaba arazir kam…®n g…®n ghuav…®ra iti. Me guizbang…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fer puvat…®, egha me arazir God ifongeziba ko, bizir a damuasa me m…®kemeziba ko, Araziba ko, Akar Gavgaviba, me dar g…®n zuir puvat…®, kar a Jekop…®n ovavir boribagh an…®ngizir araziba. Jekop a gumazir kam, God ziar igharazir kam Israel a gan…®ngi.
\v 35 Ikiav…®ra Itir God fom…®ra Israelia ko akar d…®k…®r…®zir mam gami, egha m…®gh…®gha kamagh…®n me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa asebar ziaba fan mark…®. Ia men apengan ikian mark…®, egh me bagh teviba ap…®ran mark…®. Egh me bagh ofabar amuan mark…®. Bar mark…®.
\v 36 \x - \xo 17:36 \xt God…®n Araziba 6:13\x*Ia nan ziamra f…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, egh nan apengan ik…®. Nan gavgavir ekiam…®n, k…® Isip…®n ia inigha ize. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia na bagh teviba ap…®r…®va, na baghv…®ra ofabar amu.
\v 37 Ia arazir k…® ifongeziba, ko bizir k…® damuasa ia m…®kemeziba, ko nan Araziba bar, ko nan Akar Gavgavir k…® ia bagha osirigha ia gan…®ngiziba, ia bar dar g…®n mang…®. Ia asebar ziaba fan mark…®.
\v 38 Ia Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir k…® ia koma amizir kam, g…®n amangan mark…®. Egha ia mang…® asebar ziaba fan mark…®.
\v 39 Puvat…®. Ia nan ziamra f…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God. Egh ia nan apengara ik…®. Ia kamagh…®n damut…®, k…® ian akuraght…® apaniba ia ab…®nan kogham.‚Äù
\v 40 Ez…® gumazamizir kaba an akam barazir puvat…®gha, uan arazir me fom…®ra amizibar g…®n ghuav…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 41 Ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamizir iza Samarian itir kaba, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fa, egha uaghan uan asebar ziaba fe. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n men ovavir boriba uaghan, men arazir kabara g…®n ghuav…®ra iti.\f + \fr 17:41 \ft M…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevir kam ‚Äúdat…®r…®k…®n,‚Äù a ves 34 ko ves 41…®n iti, an e itir dughiar kam m…®geir puvat…®. A gumazir ak…®nafarir kam osirizim…®n dughiam m…®gei.\f*
\c 18
\ms1 Judan kantri ghuaghira ghua bar ikuvigha g…®vazir dughiam…®n eghaghanim
\mr (Sapta 18--25)
\s1 Hesekia Judan atrivim…®n oto
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 29:1-2; 31:1)
\p 
\v 1 Elan otarim Hosia, an namba 3…®n azenim…®n, a Israelian atrivim…®n itima, Ahas…®n otarim Hesekia, Judan atrivim…®n oto.
\v 2 Hesekia azenir 25pla ikia, egha atrivim…®n oto, egha 29plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n iti. An amebam Abiya, Sekaraian guivim.
\v 3 Hesekia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir aghuibagh ami, mati an ovavim Atrivim Devit amiz…® mok…®n.
