\v 12 Os…®mt…®zir Israelia bativir kaba, dar m…®ngarim kamak…®n. Me Ikiav…®ra Itir God, men God, me an akam batosi, egha a me ko amizir Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam abigha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ingangarir gumazim Moses, me gan…®ngizir Akar Gavgaviba barazir puvat…®gha, an arazibar g…®n zuir puvat…®.
