\v 18 Ez…® Asirian gumaziba Atrivim Hesekia bagha akam amaga ghaze, a iz…®. Ez…® a uan fofozir gumazibar dapanir 3pla amangiz…®, me Asirian gumazir kaba bativasa ghue. Kar, Hilkian otarim Eliakim, an atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n garir gumazim, ko Sepna, atrivim…®n ak…®nafariba osirir gumazim, ko Asap…®n otarim Joa, an atrivim amir bizibar eghaghaniba, bar ada osirir gumazim, me zui.
\v 19 Egha gumazir dapanir 3plan kaba, Asiriaba bativiz…®, Asirian m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanir ekiabar mav, akar gavgavim…®n me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa mang…®, Asirian atrivir ekiam…®n akar gavgavir kam…®n gun Hesekia m…®kemegh. A kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòHesekia, n…® gavgavir manam ikia, egha nan apengan ikian aghua?
