\v 23 ‚ÄúHesekia, n…® iz…® nan gumazir ekiam Asirian atrivim ko akam ak…®righ. N…® ti 2,000plan m…®dorozir gumazir gavgavibar apight…®, nan atrivim 2,000plan hoziaba n…® danight…®, me dar apiagh m…®sogham. K…® fo, n…® uab…® gumazir kamagh…®n garitaba itir puvat…®.
