\v 26 Eliakim ko Sepna ko Joa akar kam baregha, me Asirian m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanir kam m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® Aram…®n akam…®n e m…®k…®m, e a g…®fo. N…® Hibrun akam m…®k…®man mark…®. Puvat…®ght…®, gumazir nguibar ekiam…®n d…®vazir gavgavir m…®tiam gis…®n m…®tivighav itiba n…®n akam baregham.‚Äù
