\v 5 Ez…® Aisaia, Hesekian akam baregha,
\v 6 kamagh…®n gumazir an akam inigha izezir kabav gei, ‚ÄúIa uamategh atrivim bagh mang…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam…®n gun a m…®kemegh. Ikiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® akar a nan tiraghtirazir kam m…®gh…®gh, a g…®n…®ghn…®gh atiatingan mark…®. A pura Asirian atrivim…®n ingangarir gumazir k…®nim, a m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam gami.
