\v 25 ‚Äú ‚ÄòSenakerip, n…® kamagh…®n fozir puvat…®, k…® fom…®ra bizir kabar amuasa n…® am…®sefe.
\q2 K…® nguibar gavgavir d…®vazir gavgaviba itiba, k…® dagh as…®ghas…®ghasa, gavgavim n…® gan…®ngi.
