\v 33 K…® Asiriabar atrivim uam a puright…®, a izezir tuavim uam an mangam.
\q2 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a Jerusalem…®n aven izeghan kogham.
\q3 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme.
