\p 
\v 35 Egha d…®magarir kamra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ensel…®n mam d…®kavigha ghua, Asiriabar m…®dorozir gumaziba itir danganim…®n, men 185,000plan m…®dorozir gumazibav soghez…®, me ariaghire. Ez…® am…®nim tiraz…® bar m…®zaraghara, gumazamiziba d…®kavigha m…®dorozir gumazir kabar kuabar gari.
\v 36 Ez…® Senakerip m…®dorozir gumazir ikiav…®ra itiba ko, d…®kavigha uamategha Asirian kantrin ghuegha, Niniven nguibar ekiam…®n iti.
\v 37 Egha a dughiar mam…®n uan asem Nisrok…®n d…®penim…®n ghugha an ziam fe. Ez…® an otarimning, aning…®n ziamning, Adramelek ko Sareser, aning m…®dorozir sabam inigha aven ghugha a m…®soghez…® an aremez…®, aning ara ghua Ararat…®n kantrin iti. Ez…® an otarir igharazim, an ziam Esarhadon, a uan afeziam…®n danganim inigha, Asirian kantrin atrivim…®n iti.
\c 20
\s1 Atrivim Hesekia ar…®mariam iniz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God an akura
\r (Aisaia 38:1-8; 38:21-22; 2 Eghaghaniba 32:24-26)
\p 
\v 1 Dughiar kam…®n, Asiriaba bar arazir kurabar Judabagh amima, Hesekia ar…®mariam inigha atam areme. Ez…® Emos…®n otarim Aisaia ghua an ganigha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…®n ar…®mariam g…®vaghan kogham, a ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…® n…® ovegham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® gumazamizir n…®n d…®penim…®n itiba, me m…®kemeght…®, me n…®n ingangariba bar dar amu dar k…®righ.‚Äô ‚Äù
