\v 2 Ez…® Hesekia akar kam baregha, uan guam isa a itir d…®penim…®n averiam…®n b…®rim…®n gara, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®g…®a ghaze,
\v 3 ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® uan navir averiam…®n aven n…® baghav…®ra ikia, n…®n ifongiam…®n g…®n ghua, bar guizbang…®ra zurara n…®n ingangarim derav…®ra a gamuav…®ra iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® amizir ingangariba, n…® dagh n…®ghn…®gh na ateght…®, k…® ovengan kogham.‚Äù Egha Hesekia Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®kemegha g…®vagha, bar puv…®ram azi.
\p 
\v 4 Aisaia atrivim…®n d…®penim ategha zui. Egha t…®ghar d…®penir av…®zim atagh…®razima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n a m…®gei,
\v 5 ‚ÄúN…® ua mang…® Hesekian ganigh, a nan gumazamizibar atrivim, egh a m…®kemegh: K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…®n inazir afeziam Devit…®n God, k…® n…®n azangs…®zim baregha n…®n temeribar ganigha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® n…® damut…®, n…® ua ghuamaghegham. Guizbang…®ra, n…® gurum…®n nan D…®penim…®n mang…®gh nan ziam f…®.
\v 6 Egh kamagh…®n Hesekia m…®k…®m: K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme: K…® n…® ateght…®, n…® 15plan azenibar ua ikegh g…®n aremegham. K…® uaghan n…®n akuragh, egh Asiriabar atrivim…®n amamangat…®ghan koght…®, a n…® ab…®raghan kogh Jerusalem inighan kogham. Bar puvat…®gham. K…® uan akar d…®k…®r…®zir k…® fom…®ra uan ingangarir gumazim Devit ko amizim g…®n…®ghn…®gha kamagh…®n damuasa.‚Äù
