\v 19 Ez…® Hesekia akar kam baregha, kamagh…®n Aisaia m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n akar n…® na m…®geim, a dera.‚Äù
\p Guizbang…®ra, Hesekia kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® dat…®r…®gh…®n atrivim…®n itir dughiar kam…®n, bizir kurar kaba otivan kogham. E pura navir am…®rizim…®n ik…®t…® m…®doroziba puvat…®gham.‚Äù
\s1 Atrivim Hesekia areme
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 32:32-33)
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 20:20-21 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 32:32-33\x*Atrivim Hesekia amizir bizir igharazibar eghaghaniba bar, ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, Judabar Atrivibar Eghaghaniba. Ak…®nafarir kam Hesekia amizir ingangarir gavgavibagh eghari. Egha ak…®nafarim uaghan bizir kabagh eghari, Hesekia d…®pam…®n suiraght…® a ikiasa d…®par akarer mam g…®kui. Egha d…®pam inigh Jerusalem…®n aven mangasa nguazim…®n averara torir ruarir mam g…®kui.
\v 21 Atrivim Hesekia uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremez…®, an otarim Manase, an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto.
\c 21
\s1 Manase Judabar atrivim…®n oto
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 33:1-20)
\p 
\v 1 Manase azenir 12pla ikiava, Judabar atrivim…®n oto, egha 55plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n ike. An amebam…®n ziam, Hepsiba.
\v 2 \x - \xo 21:2 \xt Jeremaia 15:4\x*Manase arazir aghuim…®n g…®n zuir pu. Bar puvat…®. A gumazamizir igharazir fom…®ra nguazir kam…®n ikezibar arazir m…®z…®r…®zir kurabar g…®n zui, ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God me batuegha nguazir kam isa Israelia gan…®ngi. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Manase Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kabagh ami, kar arazir God bar aghuaziba.
\p 
\v 3 Fom…®ra an afeziam Hesekia m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itir asebar ziaba fer danganiba ap…®raghar…®ki. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Manase ua dar ingari. Egha asem Bal…®n ziam fasa ofa gamir dakozibar ingari. Egha a Israelian Atrivim Ahap, fom…®ra amiz…® mogh…®n, an aser amizim Aseran nedazim itir temer guarir ak…®nibar ingari. Egha uaghan overiam…®n itir m…®kovezibar ziaba fe.
\v 4 \x - \xo 21:4 \xt 2 Samuel 7:13\x*Egha an aseba bagha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven ofa gamir dakozibar ingari. E bar fo, fom…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uan D…®penir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha kamagh…®n m…®keme, ‚ÄúJerusalem…®n itir D…®penir kam, an aven gumazamiziba nan ziamra f…® ikiam.‚Äù
\v 5 Ez…® Manase, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aven itir danganir uari akuvir pumuning…®n, an overiam…®n itir m…®kovezibar ziaba fasa, ofa gamir dakozir mabar ingari.
\v 6 Egha a uan otarim m…®soghez…® an areme, ez…® an ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim…®n m…®n a tuaz…® a bar isia m…®gh…®ri. Egha a uab…®n akuraghasa ariaghirezir gumazamizibar duabar diava, egha uaghan uab…®n akurvaghasa kukunir gumazibar azai, egha akavsiar igharagha garir av…®ribagh ami. Manase arazir kurar av…®riba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh ami, ez…® an arazir kurar kaba Ikiav…®ra Itir God gamiz…®, a bar an…®ngaghe.
