\v 7 \x - \xo 21:7-8 \xt 1 Atriviba 9:3-5; 2 Eghaghaniba 7:12-18\x*Egha Manase aser amizim Aseran marvir guar kam inigha, a isa Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven anet…®. Fom…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God D…®penir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha kamagh…®n Devit ko an otarim Solomon m…®keme, ‚ÄúJerusalem…®n itir D…®penir kam, k…® uab…® Israelian anababar tong…®n a ginaba, eght…® me zurara an iz…®, nan ziamra fam.
\v 8 Egh ia nan gumazamiziba, nan Akar Gavgaviba ko nan Arazir nan ingangarir gumazim, Moses, ia gan…®ngiziba bar adar g…®n mang…®t…®, nguazir k…® fom…®ra ian inazir afeziabagh an…®ngiz…® ia dat…®r…®gh…®n apiaghav itir kam, k…® ia batueghan kogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® Israelia nan akam baraghan aghuagha, an g…®n zuir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®. Ez…® Atrivim Manase Judaba ko Jerusalemian n…®ghn…®zibagh amua me getuima me bar arazir kurabagh amuav…®ra iti. Ez…® men arazir kurar kaba, da gumazamizir fom…®ra nguazir kam…®n ikezibar arazir kurabagh afira. Gumazamizir kaba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God me batoghez…®, Israelia nguazir kam…®n aven ize.
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Atrivim Manasen arazir kurar kabar ganigha, egha an akar kam isa uan akam inigha izir gumazibagh an…®ngi, kar an ingangarir gumaziba. Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam kamak…®n:
\v 11 ‚ÄúAtrivim Manase arazir bar kurar igharagha garir k…® aghuazibagh ami, da Amoria fom…®ra amizir arazir kurabagh afira. An asebar marvir guabar ingara men ziaba fe, egha arazir kam…®n a Judan gumazamizibagh ekua zuima, me uaghan arazir kuraba nan damazim…®n dagh ami.
\v 12 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei: K…® bar Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam ko Judabar kantri gas…®ghasigham. Eght…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba bizir kam…®n akam baregh, me d…®gavir bar kuram damigh, egh n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribar amuam.
\v 13 Mati k…® faragha Samarian nguibar ekiam ko Atrivim Ahap uan adarazi ko me gamiz…® mogh…®n, k…® arazir kamra Jerusalem damuam. K…® bar Jerusalem gas…®ghasigh egh an gumazamiziba bar me gas…®ghasigham. Eght…® Jerusalem mati itarim, me a ruegha g…®vaz…®, m…®nezir muziarir taba an itir puvat…®z…® mogh…®n a pura ikiam.
\v 14 Eght…® varazira ik…®t…®, k…® men akuraghan kogham. Bar puvat…®. K…® me is…® apanibar dafarim dar…®gham. Eght…® apaniba paz…® me damuva, men biziba bar ada okemegham.
\v 15 Nan arazir kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n: men ovaviba fom…®ra Isip ataghizir dughiam…®n ikegha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, nan gumazamiziba nan damazim…®n arazir kurar kabagh amuav…®ra iti. Ez…® men arazir kam na gamiz…®, k…® bar men an…®ngaghe.‚Äù
\p 
\v 16 Manase Judan gumazamizibagh amima, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kurabagh ami. Egha a uab…® uaghan uan adarazi men apanim gami. Egha Jerusalem…®n danganir m…®kebaba bar, Manase gumazamizir aghuir arazir kurabagh amir puvat…®zir av…®ribav soghez…® me ariaghire.
\p 
\v 17 Atrivim Manase amizir arazir igharazibar eghaghaniba, ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, Judabar Atrivibar Eghaghaniba. Ak…®nafarir kam, an amizir arazir kurabagh eghari.
\v 18 Manase uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremez…®, me an kuam isa an atrivim…®n d…®penim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n ghua nguazir otevir mam…®n anefa, me a d…®bora ghaze, Usan Azenim. Ez…® an otarim, Emon an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto.
\s1 Emon Judabar atrivim…®n oto
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 33:1-25)
\p 
\v 19 Emon 22plan azeniba ikia egha atrivim…®n oto, egha a Jerusalem…®n ikia azenir pumuningra atrivim…®n ike. An amebam…®n ziam, Mesulemet, a Harus…®n guivim, an nguibam Jotba.
\v 20 Emon…®n afeziam Manase amiz…® mogh…®n, Emon uaghan Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kurabagh ami.
\v 21 An afeziam fom…®ra amiz…® mogh…®n, a uan afeziam amizir arazir kurabara g…®n ghua asebar marvir guabar ziaba fe.
\v 22 An ak…®rim ragha Ikiav…®ra Itir God gasara, an inazir afeziabar God, egha a Ikiav…®ra Itir God ifongezir arazibar g…®n zuir puvat…®.
\v 23 Ez…® dughiar mam…®n, Emon…®n ingangarir gumazibar dapaniba uari akuvagha, a m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa tuaviba buria akam m…®sosi. Egha me g…®n atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n aven a m…®soghez…® an areme.
\v 24 Ez…® g…®n Judan gumazamiziba, ingangarir gumazibar dapanir Emon m…®soghezir kaba inigha, uaghan me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Egha me Emon…®n otarim Josaia gamiz…®, a uan afeziam…®n danganim inigha men atrivim…®n oto.
\p 
\v 25 Atrivim Emon amizir bizir igharazibar eghaghaniba, da ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, Judabar Atrivibar Eghaghaniba.
\v 26 Ez…® me Emon…®n kuam isa Usan Azenim…®n itir mozim…®n anefa. Ez…® an otarim Josaia, an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto.
\c 22
\s1 Josaia Judabar atrivim…®n oto
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 34:1-2)
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 22:1 \xt Jeremaia 3:6\x*Josaia 8plan azeniba ikia, egha Judan atrivim…®n oto, egha 31plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n ike. An amebam…®n ziam Jedida, an Adaian guivim, a Boskat…®n nguibar ekiam…®n amizim.
\v 2 Atrivim Josaia uan ovavim, Atrivim Devit fom…®ra amiz…® mogh…®n, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir aghuibagh ami. Egha a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akaba bar dar g…®n mangasa bar gavgafi.
\s1 Me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n God…®n Araziba Itir Ak…®nafarim…®n api
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 34:8-28)
\p 
\v 3 Atrivim Josaia 18plan azenibar atrivim…®n ikia, a uan gumazir an ak…®nafariba osirim Safan amadaz…®, an akam inigha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ghu. Safan, an Asalian otarim, egha uaghan Mesulam…®n igiavotarim. Josaia kamagh…®n Safan m…®gei,
\v 4 ‚ÄúN…® mang…® ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim Hilkian ganigh, egh a m…®kemeght…®, a dag…®ar gumazamiziba isa ofa gamir gumazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n tiar akam…®n garibagh an…®diba, a bar da mengegh.
\v 5 Egh n…® Hilkia m…®kemeght…®, a dag…®ar kaba inigh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim ak…®rir ingangarim gamir gumazir kabar an…®ngigh. Eght…® me D…®penir kam ak…®rir gumazibagh ives.
\v 6 Egh me d…®penibar ingarir gumaziba ko gumazir dag…®abar d…®penibar ingara fozibagh ives. Egh uaghan me ter arariba ko dag…®ar me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim ak…®rasa d…®ghoregha ar…®ghiziba sara ivesegh.
\v 7 \x - \xo 22:7 \xt 2 Atriviba 12:15\x*K…® fo, gumazir ingangaribar garir kaba, me gumazir ifarir puvat…®ziba, egha dag…®aba oker puvat…®. Ez…® ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim dag…®ar kaba bagh men azangan kogham, me manmagh…®n dag…®ar kabagh ami.‚Äù
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® Safan ghua atrivim m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ami. Ez…® Hilkia akam baregha, kamagh…®n Safan m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® ak…®nafarir r…®ghizir mam…®n gari, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven iti. Ak…®nafarir kam Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Arazibar Akaba an iti.‚Äù Egha Hilkia ak…®nafarir kam isa Safan gan…®ngi, ez…® an a d…®bori.
\p 
\v 9 An a d…®ponegha g…®vagha, ak…®nafarim inigha ghua Atrivim Josaia bagha ghugha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…®n ingangarir gumaziba dag…®aba bar ada inigha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n gara anek…®rir ingangarir gumazibagh an…®ngi.‚Äù
\p 
\v 10 Egha Safan ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAtrivim, ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim Hilkia ak…®nafarir kam na gan…®ngi.‚Äù Egha an ak…®nafarim onegha atrivim bagh a d…®bori.
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® atrivim God…®n Ak…®nafarir kam…®n aven itir Arazibar Akaba baregha, bar osemegha uan korotiam ab…®ki.
\v 12 Egha an ofa gamir gumazim Hilkia, ko Safan…®n otarim Ahikam, ko Mikaian otarim Akbor, ko atrivim bagha ak…®nafariba osirir gumazim Safan, ko atrivim…®n ingangarir gumazim Asaia, a bar men dia. Ez…® me izegha g…®vaz…®, a kamagh…®n me m…®gei,
\v 13 ‚ÄúGod…®n Arazibar Akaba itir Ak…®nafarir k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n inizir kam, a bizir Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n g…®n mangasa ifongezibar gun e m…®gei. Ez…® en inazir afeziaba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar kaba batuegha g…®fa. Ez…® bizir kam bang…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar en an…®ngaghe. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n e God…®n Ak…®nafarir kam…®n apigha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® kamaghsua, ia mang…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azaragh fogh, k…® Jerusalemia ko, Judan gumazamiziba ko, e bizir manabar amuasa a ifonge.‚Äù
\p 
\v 14 Gumazir kaba atrivim…®n akam baregha, me God…®n akam inigha izir amizir mam ko m…®k…®masa nguibar igiar Jerusalem…®n borogh…®n itim…®n ghu. Amizir kam…®n ziam, Hulda. Hulda a Salum…®n amuim, a gumazir ofa gamir gumaziba azuir korotiaba itir danganim…®n garim. Salum a Tikvan otarim, egha Harhas…®n igiavotarim. Hulda gumazir kabar akam baregha g…®vagha,
\v 15 kamagh…®n men akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, a kamagh…®n m…®gei: Ia gumazir ia amadazir kam Josaia bagh uamategh mang…®, kamagh…®n a m…®kemegh,
\v 16 ‚ÄòK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® atrivim garir Ak…®nafarim…®n itir Akar kaba bar dar g…®n mang…®, egh k…® Jerusalem ko an itir gumazamiziba saram as…®ghasigham.
\v 17 Gumazamizir ak…®rim ragha na gasarazir kaba, me asebar marvir guabar ofabagh ami. Ez…® men arazir kurar kam na gamiz…®ma, k…® puv…®ram atari. K…® Jerusalemia bar men an…®ngaghe, ez…® nan an…®ngagharir kam, a g…®vaghan kogham.
\p 
\v 18 ‚Äú ‚ÄòEz…® dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, k…® ian atrivim kamagh…®n a m…®k…®masa. Me n…® bagha Ak…®nafarir kam d…®borima,
\v 19 n…® bizir k…® Jerusalem ko an itir gumazamizibar amuasa m…®kemeziba, n…® dagh fo. K…® kamagh…®n m…®gei, Jerusalem bar ikuvigh pura danganir k…®nim…®n ikiam. Eght…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba uan apaniba akar kurabar me m…®k…®ms…®, kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄúIa Jerusalemia ikuviz…® mogh…®n ia ikufigh.‚Äù Ez…® atrivim, n…® akar kam baregha navim giragha, nan damazim…®n uab…® ab…®ra. Egha n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n uan korotiam abigha, azia nan dei. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei, k…® n…®n d…®mdiam baraki.
\v 20 Egh k…® n…® ateght…®, n…® uab…® Jerusalem…®n otivamin as…®ghas…®zir kam…®n ganighan kogham. Puvat…®. N…® bar deraghv…®ra ikiam. Egh n…® g…®n uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremeght…®, me n…®n kuam afagh g…®vaght…®, k…® Jerusalem gas…®ghasigham.‚Äô ‚Äù God…®n akam inigha izir amizim Hulda, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam gumazir kabagh anigha g…®vaz…®, me akar kam inigha uam atrivim bagha uamategha ghue.
\c 23
\s1 Judaba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n apengan ikiasa akar d…®k…®r…®zim gami
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 34:3-7; 34:29-33)
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 23:1 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 34:29\x*Ez…® Atrivim Josaia Juda ko Jerusalem…®n gumazir dapanibar diaz…®, me iza uari akufa.
\v 2 Egha atrivim ko ofa gamir gumaziba ko, akam inigha izir gumaziba ko, Judan gumazamiziba ko Jerusalem…®n itir gumazamiziba, me ghua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n uari akufa. Me uari akuvagha g…®vaz…®, atrivim Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim itir Ak…®nafarir R…®ghizir me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n apizir kam inigha, an itir akaba bar me bagha dar bori.
\v 3 Atrivim Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n tiar akam…®n borogh…®n itir guarir ak…®nim…®n borogh…®n tughav ikia, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim gamua kamagh…®n m…®gei: A bar guizbang…®ra uan navir averiam ko, uan duam…®n aven, God…®n Akar Gavgaviba ko, akar a me gan…®ngiziba ko, arazir a ifongeziba, a bar dar amuam. Egh an Ak…®nafarir kam…®n aven itir Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n akaba bar dar g…®n mangam. Ez…® gumazamiziba uaghan bar Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam…®n akabar g…®n mangasa kamagh…®ra akar d…®k…®r…®zir mam gami.
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 23:4-6 \xt 2 Atriviba 21:3; 2 Eghaghaniba 33:3\x*Ez…® g…®n Atrivim Josaia, ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim Hilkia ko, ofa gamir gumazir an apengan ingariba ko, ofa gamir gumazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n tiar akam…®n gariba, me inigha akar gavgavim me m…®kemegha ghaze, Me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven mang…®, asem Bal ko, aser amizim Asera ko overiam…®n itir bizibar ziaba fer biziba, me bar ada inigh azenan iz…®. Me bizir kaba bar ada inigha azenan izez…®, atrivim bizir kaba bar ada inigha, nguibar ekiam…®n azenan ghua, Kidron…®n Fanem…®n danganir konim…®n da tue. Ez…® biziba bar isigha g…®vaz…®, me dar averenim inigha, Betel…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghu.
\v 5 Egha Atrivim Josaia, aseba bagha ofa gamir dakozibar ofabagh amir ofa gamir gumaziba batoke. Judabar atriviba, fom…®ra ofa gamir gumazir kabav sevez…®, me m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itir danganir asebar ziaba febar ofabagh ami. Ez…® asebar ziaba fer danganir kaba, da Judan nguibabar ikia egha Jerusalem…®n borogh…®n iti. Atrivim Josaia uaghan asem Bal ko, aruem ko, iak…®nim ko, m…®koveziba ko overiam…®n itir bizir igharaziba sara, dar ofa gamir gumaziba batoke.
\v 6 Egha a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven itir aser amizim Aseran marvir guam batuegha, a inigha Jerusalem…®n azenan ghua Kidron…®n Fanem…®n danganir konim…®n uaghira a tuaz…® a isi. Egha g…®n an averenim inigha a m…®sozi a pauran m…®raram oto. Ez…® me ghua pura tintinibar Jerusalem…®n gumazamizir k…®nir oveaghuezibar mozibar danganibar a inge.
\v 7 Ez…® Josaia m…®geima, me ghua gumazir poroghamiba uari bak…®a uari koma akuir arazim gamibar danganiba, da Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n borogh…®n iti, egha me dat…®r…®gh…®n bar ada akaraghar…®ki. D…®penir kaba, da nguazir otevir amiziba aser amizim Aseran marvir guam bagha inibar ingari nagh…®n iti.
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® Atrivim Josaia, Judan kantrin aven itir m…®ghs…®ar orazibar ghua, ofa gamir gumaziba ofa gamir danganiba bar dagh as…®ghas…®ki. A not…®n amadaghan Geban nguibar ekiam…®n ikegha ghua, saut…®n amadaghan Berseban nguibar ekiam…®n tuziba, a bar dagh as…®ghas…®ki. Atrivim Josaian arazir kam bang…®n, danganir asebar ziaba fer kaba, da dat…®r…®gh…®n gumazamizibar damazibar bar m…®ze. Ez…® Josaia nguibar kabar ofa gamir gumaziba bar me inigha Jerusalem…®n ize. Egha uaghan ofa gamir dakozir Josuan tiar akam…®n borogh…®ra itibagh as…®ghas…®ki. Gumazir kam Josua, a Jerusalem…®n gavman…®n gumazir dapanir faragha zuim, a faragha Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n aven zuir tiar akar ekiar agharir k…®riam…®n itim…®n, ofa gamir dakozir kabar ingari.
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® m…®ghs…®abar p…®n ingarir ofa gamir gumazir kaba, kar ofa gamir gumazir atrivim inigha Jerusalem…®n izeziba, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa gamir dakozir Jerusalem…®n aven itim…®n ofa damuan kogham. Bar puvat…®. Me pura uan adarazi ko ikia yis puvat…®zir bret api.
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 23:10 \xt Ofa Gami 18:21; Jeremaia 7:31; 19:1-6; 32:35\x*Faragha zuir dughiam…®n, danganir asebar ziaba fer mam iti, me a d…®bora ghaze, Tofet, a Hinom…®n danganir zarim…®n iti. Ez…® Josaia danganir kam gamiz…® a gumazibar damazibar bar m…®ze. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumaziba faragha amiz…® mogh…®n me ua danganir kam…®n mangan kogh, uan boriba is…® asem Molek bagh ofan m…®n ua da tuan kogham.
\v 11 Fom…®ra Judabar atrivir maba ghaze, aruem an aser mam. Egha me an ziam fe. Me hoziabar nedazir maba ko m…®dorozir karisba isa, aruem bagha da am…®sevegha da isa nguazir otevir mam, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n tiar akam…®n borogh…®n iti, me da ar…®ki. Nguazir otevir kam a d…®vazim…®n borogh…®n ikia, atrivim…®n ingangarir gumazim Natanmelek…®n d…®penim…®n borogh…®ra iti. Ez…® Atrivim Josaia hoziar kaba ko karis…®n nedazir kaba tuez…®, da bar isi.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 23:12 \xt 2 Atriviba 21:5; 2 Eghaghaniba 33:5\x*Ez…® atrivim…®n d…®penim gis…®n danganir mam iti, me a d…®bora ghaze, Atrivim Ahas…®n Danganim. Fom…®ra Judabar atrivir maba, ofa gamir dakozir maba danganir p…®n itir kam…®n dar ingari. Ez…® uaghan Atrivim Manase, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aven uari akuvir danganir pumuning…®n, ofa gamir dakozir mabar ingari. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Atrivim Josaia ofa gamir dakozir kaba bar dagh as…®ghas…®ki. Egha g…®n me ofa gamir dakozir as…®ghas…®ghizir kabar m…®neziba ko dar oteviba inigha ghua, Kidron…®n Fanem…®n danganir konim…®n da makuni.
\v 13 \x - \xo 23:13 \xt 1 Atriviba 11:7\x*Josaia, Atrivim Solomon fom…®ra ofa gamir dakozir Jerusalem…®n amadaghan aruem anadi nagh…®n, Oliv…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n saut…®n amadaghan itibagh as…®ghas…®ki.\f + \fr 23:13 \ft Gumazir ak…®nafarir kam osirizim, m…®ghs…®am…®n ikezir bizir kurar kabagh n…®ghn…®si. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, danganir kam, Hibrun akam, ziar igharazim Oliv…®n M…®ghs…®am gat…®, a ‚ÄúM…®ghs…®ar Ikuvim.‚Äù\f* Aser kaba, aser amizir kuram Astarte, ko Moapian aser kuram Kemos, ko Amonian aser kuram Molek, Solomon dar ziaba fasa ofa gamir dakozir kabar ingari. Aser kaba, kar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n bizir bar kurar a bar aghuaziba.
\v 14 Atrivim Josaia dag…®ar guarir d…®ghoriba itiba ap…®raghar…®gha, temer guarir aser amizim Aseran nedazim itiba okaghar…®ki. Egha a gumazir aremegha g…®vazibar aghariba inigha, tintinibar asebar ziaba fer danganibar da kuni, egha kamagh…®ra danganir kabagh amiz…®, da gumazamizibar damazibar m…®ze.\f + \fr 23:14 \ft Josua kamagh…®n n…®ghnigha gumazir oveaghuezibar aghariba pura tintinibar da akuni, eght…® gumaziba atiating…®va egh asebar ziaba fer danganibar saghon ikiam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Israelia kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim iti, gumazir oveaghuezibar aghariba, bizir kuraba.\f*
\p 
\v 15 \x - \xo 23:15 \xt 1 Atriviba 12:33\x*Bar fom…®ra, Nebat…®n otarim Jeroboam, Betel…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ofa gamir dakozir mam ko m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itir asebar ziaba fasa danganir mam…®n ingari. Jeroboam, an atrivir fom…®ra Israelia gekuiz…® me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kurabagh ami. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Atrivim Josaia, Betel…®n ghugha gumazibav kemez…®, me asebar ziaba fer danganir kabagh as…®ghas…®gha, ofa gamir dakoziba ap…®raghar…®ki. Me asebar ziaba fer danganibagh aboroz…® da isi, egha g…®n me avim…®n averenim inigha a m…®sogha zuima a pauran m…®n oto. Egha me uaghan aser amizim Aseran marvir guam inigha avim…®n a tuaz…® a isi.
\v 16 \x - \xo 23:16 \xt 1 Atriviba 13:1-2\x*Ez…® Atrivim Josaia m…®ghs…®ar kam…®n tughav ikia egha a ragh…®r…®gha, mozir mabar garima da iti. Ez…® a gumazibav kemez…®, me ghua gumazir ariaghirezibar aghariba asiz…®, ana da isa Jeroboam…®n ofa gamir dakozim gat…®gha avim…®n dagh aboroz…® da isi, ez…® bizir kam ofa gamir dakozim gamima, a gumazamizibar damazim…®n bar m…®ze. Egha arazir kam a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akar a fom…®ra uan akam inigha izir gumazir mam…®n akam garugha m…®kemezim gamiz…®, a guizbang…®ram oto.
\v 17 \x - \xo 23:17 \xt 1 Atriviba 13:30-32\x*Josaia aghariba tuegha g…®vagha, gumazir kuaba afir danganir igharazir mam…®n garima a iti. Ez…® a men azara, ‚ÄúKar tinan mozim?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Betel…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazamiziba Josaia ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúKar Judan kantrin akam inigha izir gumazir kam…®n mozim, a fom…®ra iza bizir n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ofa gamir dakozir kam gamizir bizibar gun m…®keme.‚Äù
\p 
\v 18 Ez…® Josaia kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa bizitam…®n a damuan mark…®. Ia an aghariba ateght…® da mar an mozim…®n ik…®.‚Äù Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me an aghariba inizir puvat…®. Egha uaghan me Samarian Distrigh…®n akam inigha izir gumazir igharazir kam…®n aghariba inizir puvat…®.
\v 19 Fom…®ra Israelian atriviba, Samarian Distrigh…®n itir nguibar ekiabar asebar ziaba fer danganir m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itibar ingari. Ez…® men arazir kam Ikiav…®ra Itir God gamiz…®, a men an…®ngaghe. Josaia faragha Betel…®n nguibar ekiam…®n amiz…® mogh…®n, dat…®r…®gh…®n a danganir kabagh as…®ghas…®ki.
\v 20 Egha an asebar ziaba fer danganir kabar ofa gamir gumaziba bar me inigha, men ofa gamir dakozibagh is…®n me m…®soghez…®, me ariaghire. Egha a gumazir ariaghirezir igharazir mabar aghariba dakozir kabar da tuegha, ingangarir kam ag…®vagha, uamategha Jerusalem…®n ghu.
\s1 Gumazamiziba, God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam G…®n…®ghn…®ghamin Isam gami
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 35:1-19)
\p 
\v 21 Egha g…®n Atrivim Josaia akam gumazamiziba bagha anemaga ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, en God, Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim Itir Ak…®nafarim…®n m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, E God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam G…®n…®ghn…®ghamin Isam damuam.‚Äù Ez…® gumazamiziba atrivim m…®kemez…® mogh…®ram ami.
\p 
\v 22 Gumazamiziba bar deraghav…®ra isar kam gami. Me fom…®ra gumazir dapanibar dughiam…®n tugha iza Israelia ko Judabar atrivibar dughiam…®n, gumazamiziba me Isar kam deragha a gamizir puvat…®. Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n me bar deragha a gami.
\v 23 Dughiar kam…®n, Josaia 18plan azenibar atrivim…®n itima, me God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n Akaba deraghav…®ra dar g…®n ghua, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha Jerusalem…®n Isar kam deraghv…®ram a gami.
\s1 Atrivim Josaia arazir kurar igharazir maba Judan kantrin, da batoke
\p 
\v 24 Atrivim Josaia uaghan gumazir ariaghirezir gumazibar duaba ko m…®geiba ko, nedazir muziarir gumaziba uan d…®penibagh ar…®ziba ko, asebar marvir guar gumaziba ingarizir igharaziba sara batoke. Kar Jerusalem ko Judan nguibaba bar men asebar ziaba fer bizir kurar God bar aghuaziba, a bar da batoke. A kamaghsua, gumazamiziba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Arazir Ak…®nafarir kam…®n aven itiba bar dar g…®n mangasa a ifonge. Ak…®nafarir kam, ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim Hilkia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n an api.
\v 25 Josaia an atrivir bar aghuim. An navir averiam ko an duam ko an gavgavim…®n aven, a ifongiar vam…®ra ko n…®ghn…®zir vam…®rara iti, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God baghav…®ra ikia, Moses Osirizir Araziba bar dar g…®n mangasa. Fom…®ra atrivitam Josaian m…®n derazir puvat…®, egha g…®n atrivitam an m…®n itir puvat…®. A bar me gafira.
\p 
\v 26 Josaia guizbang…®ra arazir aghuir av…®ribagh ami, ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Atrivim Manase amizir arazir kurabagh n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra iti, egha a Judaba bar men an…®ngaghegha, an an…®ngagharim g…®vazir puvat…®.
\v 27 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® fom…®ra Israelian kantri gamiz…® mogh…®n, k…® bar arazir magh garim…®n Judan kantri damigham. K…® Jerusalem ak…®rim ragh a gasaragham, kar nguibar ekiar k…® ua bagha m…®sevezim. Egh d…®penir k…® m…®sevez…® gumazamiziba an iz…® nan ziam famin kam, k…® ak…®rim ragh a gasaragham.‚Äù
\s1 Josaia areme
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 35:20--36:1)
\p 
\v 28 Atrivim Josaia amizir bizir igharazibar eghaghanir igharaziba, ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, Judan Atrivibar Eghaghaniba.
\v 29 Josaia atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, Isip…®n Atrivim Neko, Isip…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha Asirian atrivim ko m…®soghasa Yufretis…®n Fanem…®n ghu. Atrivim Josaia bizir kam…®n akam baregha, uan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha ghua Isipia ko m…®sosi. Me Megidon nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n m…®sozima, Isipian Atrivim Josaia m…®soghez…®, an areme.
\v 30 Ez…® Josaian apengan ingarir gumaziba an kuam inigha, m…®dorozir karis…®n mam gat…®gha, a inigha uamategha Jerusalem…®n ghu. Egha me Josaian kuam inigha an mozim…®n anefa. Ez…® Judaba, Josaian otarim Joahas inigha, borem…®n an dapanim gingegha anem…®sevez…®, a men atrivim…®n oto.
\s1 Joahas Judabar atrivim…®n oto
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 36:2-4)
\p 
\v 31 Joahas 23plan azeniba ikia Judabar atrivim…®n oto. Egha a Jerusalem…®n ikia iak…®nir 3plara atrivim…®n ike. An amebam, an ziam Hamutal, a Lipnan nguibam…®n gumazim Jeremaian guivim.
\v 32 Joahas uan inazir afeziabar arazibar g…®n ghua, egha arazir kuraba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh ami.
\p 
\v 33 Isip…®n Atrivim Neko, Joahas…®n atrivir ingangarim ag…®fa, egha a isa Riplan nguibar ekiam…®n kalabus gat…®, an Hamat…®n kantrin aven itir nguibam. Ez…® Joahas Jerusalem…®n aven uam atrivim…®n itir puvat…®. Ez…® Atrivim Neko Judan kantrin gumazamizibagh amima, me takis…®n m…®n dag…®aba a gan…®di, dar d…®bobonim, 3,400 kilogrem silva ko 34 kilogrem gol.
\v 34 \x - \xo 23:34 \xt Jeremaia 22:11-12\x*Ez…® Atrivim Neko, Josaian otarir mam Eliakim ini, egha a Eliakim gamiz…®, a Josaian danganim inigha Judabar atrivim…®n oto. Ez…® Atrivim Neko Eliakim…®n ziam adegha, ziam Jehoiakim a gat…®. Egha g…®n Atrivim Neko Joahas inigha Isip…®n kantrin ghu. Ez…® Joahas Isip…®n ikia ghuava areme.
\p 
\v 35 Ez…® Atrivim Jehoiakim, takis…®n m…®n dag…®aba is…® Atrivim Neko dan…®ngasa, gumazamiziba bar me da silvaba ko golba ini. Jehoiakim me m…®kemeght…®, me takis…®n dag…®aba manmagh…®n tught…®, me a dan…®ngam. Gumazir dag…®ar bar av…®riba itiba, me dag…®ar av…®riba an…®di. Ez…® gumazir dag…®ar av…®riba puvat…®ziba, me dag…®ar muziaribara an…®di. Ez…® Atrivim Jehoiakim silvaba ko golba inigha, Atrivim Neko bagha da amada.
\s1 Jehoiakim Judabar atrivim…®n oto
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 36:5-8)
\p 
\v 36 \x - \xo 23:36 \xt Jeremaia 22:18-19; 26:1-6; 35:1-19\x*Jehoiakim 25plan azeniba ikia, Judabar atrivim…®n oto. Egha a Jerusalem…®n ikia 11plan azenibar atrivim…®n ike. An amebam…®n ziam, Sebida, a Ruman nguibar ekiam…®n gumazim Pedaian guivim.
\v 37 Jehoiakim uan inazir afeziabar arazibar g…®n ghua, arazir kuraba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh ami.
\c 24
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 24:1 \xt Jeremaia 25:1-38; Daniel 1:1-2\x*Ez…® Jehoiakim Judabar atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, Babilonian Atrivim Nebukatnesar uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko iza Judan kantri m…®sosi. Egha a me ab…®ragha, Atrivim Jehoiakim gamiz…®, an an apengan iti. Ez…® 3plan azeniba g…®vaz…®, Atrivim Jehoiakim, Atrivim Nebukatnesar a gativaghan a bar aghua, egha a uam an apengan itir puvat…®.
\v 2 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Babilonian gumazir b…®zir maba ko, Siriabar gumazir b…®zir maba ko, Moapian gumazir b…®zir maba ko, Amonian gumazir b…®zir maba, me iz…®, Jehoiakim…®n adarazi ko m…®sogh Judan kantri gas…®ghas…®ghasa, a me amada. Ikiav…®ra Itir God fom…®ra uan akam inigha izir gumaziba, kar an ingangarir gumaziba, uan akaba isa me gan…®ngiz…®, me an gun m…®keme. Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, dat…®r…®gh…®n bizir kabagh amiz…®, da guizbang…®ram otifi.
\v 3 Bar guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…® n…®ghn…®zir kam gumazir kabagh an…®ngiz…®, me kamagh…®n ami. Ikiav…®ra Itir God Atrivim Manase amizir arazir kurar kabagh n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra iti. Bizir kam bang…®n, a Judabar atari, egh a me batueght…® me an damazim…®n saghon mangasa, a ifonge.
\v 4 Atrivim Manase uaghan, fom…®ra Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n aven itir gumazamizir aghuir arazir kuratam gamizir puvat…®zir av…®ribav soghez…® me ariaghire. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra ikia, egha Atrivim Manasen arazir kuraba g…®n amangan aghua.
\p 
\v 5 Atrivim Jehoiakim amizir bizir igharazibar eghaghaniba, da ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, Judabar Atrivibar Eghaghaniba.
\v 6 Atrivim Jehoiakim uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremez…®, an otarim, Jehoiakin an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto.\f + \fr 24:6 \ft Jehoiakim ko Jehoiakin aning gumazir igharazir pumuning, aning…®n ziamning mong uaghara ghu.\f*
\p 
\v 7 Isip…®n atrivim fom…®ra ativazir danganiba, Isip…®n kantrin m…®taghniam…®n fanem…®n ikegha ghua Yufretis…®n Fanem…®n tu. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Babilon…®n atrivim dagh atifa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Isip…®n atrivim uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko ua ghua kantrin igharaziba ko m…®sozir puvat…®.
\s1 Jehoiakin Judabar atrivim…®n oto
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 36:9-10)
\p 
\v 8 Jehoiakin 18plan azeniba ikia, egha Judan atrivim…®n oto. Egha a Jerusalem…®n ikia 3plan iak…®nibara atrivim…®n ike. An amebam…®n ziam, Nehusta, a Jerusalem…®n gumazim Elnatan…®n guivim.
\v 9 Jehoiakin uan afeziam…®n arazir kurabar g…®n ghua, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kurabagh ami.
\p 
\v 10 Egha Jehoiakin atrivim…®n ikiav…®ra itima, Babilonian Atrivim Nebukatnesar uan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha iza, Jerusalem korogha a iniasa m…®sosi.
\v 11 Babilonian m…®dorozir gumaziba Jerusalem korogha iti, ez…® Atrivim Nebukatnesar uab…® iza uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko iti.
\v 12 \x - \xo 24:12 \xt Jeremaia 22:24-30; 24:1-10; 29:1-2\x*Ez…® Atrivim Jehoiakin garima, Nebukatnesar izegha g…®vaz…®, a uab…® uan amebam ko, an apengan ingangarir gumaziba ko, an gumazir dapaniba ko atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n garir gumaziba, a bar me isa Atrivim Nebukatnesar dan…®ngasa, me bar nguibam ategha azenan ghua, Nebukatnesar batogha a m…®g…®a ghaze, e ua m…®soghan kogham. Ez…® Atrivim Nebukatnesar, Atrivim Jehoiakin isa kalabus gat…®. Bizir kam Nebukatnesar atrivim…®n itir azenir namba 8…®n aven oto.
\v 13 Dughiar kam…®n, Atrivim Nebukatnesar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven ghua, Atrivim Solomon fom…®ra ingarizir bizir golba itiba, a bar ada inigha da b…®aghar…®ki. Egha a uaghan bizir bar aghuir Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n itiba ko, bizir aghuir atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n itiba, a bar da atera Babilon…®n ghu. Arazir kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God fom…®ra an gun m…®keme, ez…® a guizbang…®ram oto.
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® Atrivim Nebukatnesar Jerusalem…®n gumazamiziba bar ko, gumazir dapaniba bar ko, m…®dorozir gumazir gavgaviba, a bar men suiragha kalabuziar gumazamizibar m…®n me inigha ghu, men d…®bobonim 10,000…®n tu. Egha a uaghan gumazir bizir igharagha garibar ingaramin fofozim itiba ko, gumazir ain…®n bizibar ingaramin fofozim itiba sara bar me ini. A me inigha Jerusalem ategha ghua Babilon…®n kantrin otoz…®, me kalabuziar gumazibar m…®n otifi. An onganarazibagh amir gumazamizir varazira ataghiz…®, me Judan kantrin ikiav…®ra iti. Gumazamizir igharaziba bar, me ua Judan kantrin aven itir puvat…®.
\v 15 \x - \xo 24:15 \xt Esekiel 17:12\x*Atrivim Nebukatnesar, Jehoiakin ko an amebam ko, an amuiba ko, an gumazir dapaniba ko, Judan gumazir aruaba, a bar me inigha Jerusalem ategha kalabuziar gumazamizibar m…®n Babilon…®n ghu.
\v 16 Egha Atrivim Nebukatnesar m…®dorozir gumazir gavgaviba bar me inigha ghu, men d…®bobonim 7,000. Egha a uaghan gumazir av…®rir bizir igharagha garibar ingarir fofozim itiba ko gumazir ain…®n bizibar ingariba sara ini, men d…®bobonim 1,000…®n tu. Gumazir kaba bar gumazir gavgaviba, ez…® me m…®dorozir gumazibar ingangarim damuan tughat…®.
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 24:17 \xt Jeremaia 37:1; Esekiel 17:13\x*Atrivim Nebukatnesar, Jehoiakin…®n afeziar dozim Matania gamiz…®, a Jehoiakin…®n danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto. Nebukatnesar ziam Matania adegha ziar kam, Sedekaia a gat…®.
\s1 Babilonia Jerusalem m…®sogha a ini
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 36:11-21; Jeremaia 52:1-11)
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 24:18 \xt Jeremaia 27:1-22; 28:1-17\x*Sedekaia 21plan azeniba ikia, Judan atrivim…®n oto. Egha 11plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n ike. An amebam, Hamutal, a Jeremaian igharazim…®n guivim, a Lipnan nguibar ekiam…®n gumazir mam.
\v 19 Sedekaia, Jehoiakim…®n arazibar g…®n ghua, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kurabagh ami.
\v 20 \x - \xo 24:20 \xt Esekiel 17:15\x*Judaba ko Jerusalemian arazir kuraba Ikiav…®ra Itir God gamiz…®, a bar men an…®ngaghe. Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God gumazamizir kaba bar me batoghez…®, me an guam…®n saghon ghue.
\p Ez…® g…®n Sedekaia, Babilon…®n atrivim a gativagh an ganan a bar aghua, egha a uam an apengan itir puvat…®.
\c 25
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 25:1 \xt Jeremaia 21:1-10; 34:1-5; Esekiel 24:2\x*Egha namba 9…®n azenim…®n Sedekaia atrivim…®n ikia ghua, an namba 10…®n iak…®nim…®n, namba 10…®n iak…®nir kam…®n aruem…®n oto. Ez…® Babilon…®n Atrivim Nebukatnesar uan m…®dorozir gumaziba bar dar akua iza Jerusalem av…®nigha, nguibam iniasa m…®sosi. Me Jerusalem korogha, ghua temeba okegha iza nguibar ekiam…®n d…®vazir gavgavim…®n borogh…®ra dar pozim m…®k…®ni. Egh me nguazim dav k…®night…®, da f…®gh ghuanaboght…®, me mang…® dagh is…®n m…®tivigh, nguibar ekiam ko m…®sogham.
\v 2-3 Me azenir vam…®ra ko akuam…®n Jerusalem av…®nigha iti. Ez…® Sedekaia 11plan azenibar atrivim…®n iti, ez…® an namba 4…®n iak…®nim…®n otogha\f + \fr 25:2-3 \ft Hibrun akam…®n danganir kam, iak…®nim…®n d…®bobonim itir puvat…®. Ez…® Jeremaia 52:6 kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, bizir kam namba 4…®n iak…®nim…®n oto.\f* ghua, namba 9…®n aruem otoz…®, men dagheba bar g…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Jerusalem…®n gumazamiziba m…®tiriam bar puv men azi.
\v 4 \x - \xo 25:4 \xt Esekiel 33:21\x*Dughiar kam…®n Babilonia d…®vazim…®n vuer mam akarigha Jerusalem…®n aven ghue. Ez…® Atrivim Sedekaia Jerusalem…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba koma are. Me d…®magarim…®n suebar ghuava atrivim…®n dagher azenim…®n otivigha ghua, danganir d…®vazir pumuning uaning isasuiragha itir tiar akar kam…®n ghua, Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n otivigha ghue. Egha me Jordan…®n Fanem…®n danganir zarim…®n ghuaghirir tuavim…®n zui.
\v 5 Ez…® Babilon…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba Atrivim Sedekaian ag…®ragha ghua, Jerikon nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n itir danganir zarim…®n a bato. Ez…® Sedekaian m…®dorozir gumaziba anetegha, ara tintinibar ghue.
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® Babilonia Sedekaian suiragha a inigha Babilon…®n atrivim bagha ghu. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Atrivim Nebukatnesar Riplan nguibam…®n iti, an Hamat…®n nguazim…®n aven itir nguibam. Ez…® Nebukatnesar uan kot…®n aven Sedekaian gara ghaze, Sedekaia uan arazir kurar an amizim…®n ivezim iniam.
\v 7 \x - \xo 25:7 \xt Esekiel 12:13\x*Ez…® Babilonian m…®dorozir gumaziba uaghan Sedekaian otariba ini, egha me inigha Riplan ize. Ez…® nguibar kam…®n Nebukatnesar m…®kemez…®, me Sedekaian otariba inigha, Sedekaian damazim…®n bar me m…®suaghar…®ki. Egha atrivim m…®kemez…®, me Sedekaian damazimning asi, egha an suemning ko dafarimning sen…®n ada ikegha, a inigha Babilon…®n ghu. Egha a isa Babilon…®n kalabus gat…®.
\s1 Babilon…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba, Jerusalem gas…®ghas…®ki
\r (Jeremaia 52:12-23)
\p 
\v 8 Nebukatnesar Babilon…®n atrivim…®n itima, an namba 19…®n azenim otogha ghua an namba 5…®n iak…®nim…®n, an namba 7…®n aruem oto. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, Nebusaradan, an atrivim…®n garir m…®dorozir gumazibar gumazir dapanir faragha zuim, a d…®kavigha Babilon…®n atrivim…®n ingangarim gativagh an ganasa Jerusalem…®n ize.
\v 9 \x - \xo 25:9 \xt 1 Atriviba 9:8\x*Egha a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim ko Judan atrivim…®n d…®penim ko, Jerusalem…®n gumazir aruabar d…®peniba sara, a bar dagh aponge. Babilonian d…®peniba bar, a vaghvagha dagh aponge.
\v 10 Babilonian m…®dorozir gumazir Nebusaradan…®n g…®n zuiba, me bar mogh…®ra Jerusalem av…®nizir d…®vazim gas…®ghas…®gha bar anekaraghar…®ki.
\v 11 Nebusaradan gumazamizir Jerusalem…®n ikiav…®ra itiba inigha ghua, Babilon…®n kalabus gat…®. Egha a uaghan Judan faragha Jerusalem ategha ara ghua an gara, a ko ikezibar akua, Babilon…®n kalabuziabar m…®n me inigha ghue.
\v 12 Egha Nebusaradan, gumazamizir onganarazibagh amir marazi ataghiz…®, merara Judan nguazim…®n ikiav…®ra iti. Egha a me m…®g…®a ghaze, ia wain…®n azeniba ko, azenir igharazibar gan ik…®.
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 25:13 \xt 1 Atriviba 7:15-26; 2 Eghaghaniba 3:15-17; 4:2-5\x*Egha Babilonia ghua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ghuegha, bras…®n guarir ak…®niba ko, teng…®n doziba p…®n da afasa bras…®n ingarizir osazariba ap…®raghar…®ki. Egha me uaghan teng…®n d…®par ekiar me bras…®n ingarizim ab…®ki. Israelia fom…®ra kamagh…®n a d…®bori, ‚ÄúOngarim.‚Äù Egha me bras…®n kaba bar da inigha Babilon…®n ghue.
\v 14 \x - \xo 25:14 \xt 1 Atriviba 7:45; 2 Eghaghaniba 4:16\x*Babilonia uaghan averenim iniamin itariba ko, savol…®n muziariba ko, lamba munger biziba ko, itarir ofan ghuzibar ar…®ghamiba ko, pauran mughuriar aghuim zuiba tuer itariba ko, Judaba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven ingarasa amizir bras…®n biziba sara me da ini.
\v 15 Egha Nebusaradan uaghan bizir gumaziba gol ko silvan ingariziba, kar itarir avim ateriba ko ofan ghuziba ar…®zir itarir ekiaba, a uaghan ada ini.
\p 
\v 16 Atrivim Solomon fom…®ra bras inigha guarir ak…®nir kamning ko, teng…®n ekiar me kamagh…®n d…®borim, ‚ÄúOngarim,‚Äù an adar ingari. Egha wilkar…®n itarir ekiar dagh is…®n dar…®ghamibar ingari. Ez…® Solomon m…®kemez…®, me bizir kaba isa Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ada ar…®ki. Ez…® bras…®n kabar os…®mt…®zim bar ekefe, eght…® gumazitam dar os…®mt…®zim g…®fofoghs…®, da is…® skel…®n tam dar…®ghan iburagham.
\v 17 Gumaziba fom…®ra ababanir vam…®ran bras…®n guarir ak…®nir kamning…®n ingari. Aning…®n ruarimning 8 mitan tu. Ez…® me bras…®n guarir ak…®nimning…®n dapanimning…®n ingariz…®, aning mong ekefe. Egha aning…®n dapanimning ghuanaga 1 mita ko 30 sentimitan tu. Ez…® me bras inigha iver nuzim…®n, mati temer pomigranet…®n ov…®ziba. Me pomigranet…®n kaba tintinibar iver nuzim…®n m…®n ada ike. Egha me guarir ak…®nir kamning…®n dapanimning gighuigha, aning as…®ngi.
\s1 Judaba ghua Babilon…®n kalabus…®n iti
\r (Jeremaia 52:24-27)
\p 
\v 18 Babilonian gumazir dapanir faragha zuir kam Nebusaradan, an ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim Seraia, ko Seraian apengan itir gumazim Sefanaia, ko God…®n D…®penim…®n tiar akam…®n garir gumazir 3plan igharaziba sara ini.
\v 19 Egha Jerusalem…®n, a gumazir dapanir Jerusalem…®n m…®dorozir gumazibar garim ini. Egha n…®ghn…®ziba Judan atrivim gan…®dir gumazir 5pla ini. Egha a Judan m…®dorozir gumazibar gumazir dapanibar ak…®nafariba osirir gumazim ini, kar gumazir gumaziba isima, me m…®dorozir gumazibar otivim. Egha a 60plan gumazamizibar garima, me Jerusalem…®n ikiav…®ra iti, ez…® a uaghan me ini.
\v 20 Egha Nebusaradan gumazamizir kaba, bar me inigha Babilon…®n atrivim bagha Riplan nguibam…®n ghu.
\v 21 Kar Hamat…®n nguazim. Ez…® atrivim m…®kemez…®, me gumazir kabav soghez…® me ariaghire.
\p Babilonia kamagh…®n amigha, me g…®n Judan igharaziba inigha ghua Babilon…®n kalabus gat…®.\f + \fr 25:21 \ft N…® ak…®nafarir kam…®n ak…®rang…®n itir Akar M…®ngaribar gan. A Judabar kalabus…®n itir dughiam m…®gei.\f*
\s1 Gedalia Judan nguazim gatifa
\r (Jeremaia 40:7-9; 41:1-3)
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 25:22-24 \xt Jeremaia 40:7-9\x*Atrivim Nebukatnesar, a gumazamizir Babilonia ataghiz…® me Judan nguazim…®n itibagh ativagh men ganasa Gedalia am…®sefe. Gedalia a Ahikam…®n otarim, egha Safan…®n igiavotarim.
\v 23 Judan m…®dorozir gumazir maba uan gumazir dapaniba ko, me kantri Judan danganir mabar ikiav…®ra iti. Me kamagh…®n akam baraki, Babilon…®n atrivim, Gedalia, Judan nguazim…®n, gavman…®n gumazir dapanir faragha zuim…®n ikiasa anem…®sefe. Ez…® gumazir kaba bar d…®kavigha Gedalian ganasa Mispan ghue. Gumazir dapanir kabar ziabar kara: Netanian otarim Ismael, Karean otarim Johanan, Tanhumet…®n otarim Seraia, a Netofan nguibam…®n gumazim, ko Makan nguazim…®n gumazim Jesania.
\v 24 Ez…® Gedalia me ko akam ak…®ra ghaze, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra, ia Babilonia men apengan ik…®va, men atiatingan mark…®. Puvat…®. Ia nguazir kam…®n ik…®va, egh Babilon…®n atrivim…®n apengan ik…®, deraghv…®ra ikiam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 25 \x - \xo 25:25 \xt Jeremaia 41:1-3\x*Ismael a Netanian otarim, egha a Elisaman igiavotarim, egha a Judan atrivibar ik…®zir mam. Ez…® azenir kam…®n namba 7…®n iak…®nim, a 10plan gumaziba inigha me Mispan izegha Gedalia m…®soghez…® an areme. Egha me uaghan Judan gumaziba ko Babilonian m…®dorozir gumazir Gedalia ko Mispan itiba bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire.
\v 26 \x - \xo 25:26 \xt Jeremaia 43:5-7\x*Bizir kam…®n g…®n, danganir kam…®n ikiav…®ra itir Judaba, ko m…®dorozir gumazibar gumazir dapanir ikiav…®ra itiba, me bar Babilonian atiatingi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me ara ghua Isip…®n iti.
\s1 Babilon…®n atrivim kalabus…®n Jehoiakin f…®ri
\r (Jeremaia 52:31-34)
\p 
\v 27 Judan Atrivim Jehoiakin, Babilon…®n 37plan azenibar kalabus…®n itima, Evil Merodak, Babilon…®n atrivim…®n oto. Egha azenir kam…®n aven, an namba 12…®n iak…®nim otogha ghua, namba 27…®n aruem otoz…®, Evil Merodak, Jehoiakin…®n apangkuvigha, kalabus…®n aneg…®fa.
\v 28 Evil Merodak arazir aghuim…®n a gamua, ziar ekiam ko dabirabir aghuim a gan…®ngi, ez…® an dabirabir kam atrivir igharazir Jehoiakin ko Babilon…®n kalabus…®n ikezibar dabirabim gafira.
\v 29 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Jehoiakin ua kalabuziar korotiaba azuir puvat…®. Egha a zurara dughiabar Babilon…®n atrivim ko apiav ikia apa ghua, Jehoiakin aremezir dughiam…®n tu.
\v 30 Babilon…®n atrivim m…®kemez…®, me dughiabar dag…®aba isa Jehoiakin gan…®di, eght…® a deraghv…®ra ikiam. Me kamagh…®ram amua ghua, Jehoiakin aremezir dughiam…®n tu.
